NK113(e)001:1: // gu na ko sha rat+na pra mo da bri sh+ti n+aa ma bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK113(e)001:2: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK113(e)001:4: gu na ko sha rat+na pra mo da brish+ti n+aa ma /
NK113(e)001:6: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK113(e)001:7: rin chen rnam gsum grags pa'i spring yig gis //
NK113(e)001:8: mu tig 'khri shing rab tu dga' byas nas //
NK113(e)001:9: bdud kyi bu mo'i bzhi na ras kun+da'i tshal //
NK113(e)001:10: skal ngan bgyid la mngon phyogs sangs rgyas mthu //
NK113(e)001:11: blo mchog rnams kyi yon tan dag byed gter //
NK113(e)001:12: gcig tu barlinga la spyi brtol rlabs phreng gi //
NK113(e)001:13: ca co sgrog 'di mdzes pa mi ngom yang //
NK113(e)001:14: dam chos brjod la brten slad mnyam par 'os /
NK113(e)001:15: thog ma med nas skye rga na 'chi yi //
NK113(e)001:16: rims kyis btab pa'i sman chen bdud rtsi'i ro //
NK113(e)001:17: dam chos lag tu mchis pa spong byed pa'i //
NK113(e)001:18: skyes bu rnams la bdag gis ji ltar 'doms //
NK113(e)001:19: ring nas bshes pa 'khor ba'i 'brog dgon du //
NK113(e)001:20: mgo dang yan lag bcad pas gdungs byas shing //
NK113(e)001:21: phyin chad gdung 'gyur lkog tu gyur pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:22: da dung mtho ris bde la sred cing rmongs //
NK113(e)001:23: bsam brlag de ni 'di nas yang ltung la //
NK113(e)001:24: ngan song gsum dang 'du shes med pa'i lha //
NK113(e)001:25: mtha' 'khob dbang po ma tshang lta ba log /
NK113(e)001:26: sangs rgyas 'byung ba med pa dag tu 'khyam //
NK113(e)001:27: thang cig skabs btsal ma yin lcags bsregs gzhir //
NK113(e)001:28: mtshon gyi chad pa rtsub mos yang nas yang //
NK113(e)001:29: srog 'phrog 'chi bar mi nus dmyal ba pa //
NK113(e)001:30: da dung khong khro'i las ngan rnyi la 'thogs //
NK113(e)001:31: rnag khrag phyi sa sogs kyang mi rnyed pa'i //
NK113(e)001:32: yi dwags phongs pas nyam thag smos ci dgos //
NK113(e)001:33: chu klung ljon pa bltas pa'i mod la bskams //
NK113(e)001:34: nang 'khrol 'tshig pa'i sdug bsngal zad mi shes //
NK113(e)001:35: sgrib pa'i mthus byas tshe tshad nges pa med //
NK113(e)001:36: dud 'gro phan tshun gcig la gcig bza' zhing //
NK113(e)001:37: rngon pa'i dam bzhag rtsub mos srog 'phrog dang //
NK113(e)001:38: bkol phyir 'dul ba 'dzin pas nyam thag pa'i //
NK113(e)001:39: gnas su skye ba thob na ci byar yod //
NK113(e)001:40: 'tsho ba'i lam mtha' shin tu ring pos bsring //
NK113(e)001:41: skyo ba'i go skabs mi dbye gzugs med dang //
NK113(e)001:42: thos bsam rten 'gags 'du shes med pa'i lha //
NK113(e)001:43: 'chi khar log par lta bas khom ldan min //
NK113(e)001:44: rkang pa gnyis pa'i khyogs la rab brten yang //
NK113(e)001:45: de yi 'du shes bsod nams ma yin pas //
NK113(e)001:46: dam la bzhag cing gzhungs pa'i kla klo rnams //
NK113(e)001:47: blang dor shin tu 'chol ba'i nags na 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:48: dbang po'i dam bca' nyams pa'i lkugs pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:49: 'phags pa'i ded dpon dag dad phrad gyur kyang //
NK113(e)001:50: brag ca'i cho gas bzung ba'i ca co bzhin //
NK113(e)001:51: brda mi 'phrod pa'i 'brog dgon chen por gdung //
NK113(e)001:52: skye ba'i rgya mtsho brgal ba'i gru bo che //
NK113(e)001:53: rnam rig ba dan g.yo ba thob nas slar //
NK113(e)001:54: sangs rgyas 'byung la mnyes par mi bgyid cing //
NK113(e)001:55: log par lta ba 'dzin de bdud kyis gtses //
NK113(e)001:56: thub pa rnams kyis spangs pa'i bskal pa yi //
NK113(e)001:57: gcong rong mun nag 'thibs por lhung de slar //
NK113(e)001:58: ldang bar brtson kyang lam min rgyun ldan de //
NK113(e)001:59: nyam nga'i ltung bar 'og nas 'og tu 'gro //
NK113(e)001:60: sdig sdug 'thor rlung 'khrugs pa'i gnas rigs su //
NK113(e)001:61: ngal zhing skrag bcas bsod nams rnyog pa can //
NK113(e)001:62: chos la phrag pa dog pa'i mi khom brgyad //
NK113(e)001:63: bsams nas rang gi dal ba don yod mdzod //
NK113(e)001:64: yul dbus sa gzi gtsang mar dbang po dang //
NK113(e)001:65: yan lag rab rdzogs dad pa'i gnas la dad //
NK113(e)001:66: las matha'i me tog sdig tos ma bcom pa'i //
NK113(e)001:67: mir gyur dpag bsam ljon pa shin tu dkon //
NK113(e)001:68: rgyal ba u dum wa ra 'jig rten byon //
NK113(e)001:69: chos kyi me tog kha bye bstan pa'i tshal //
NK113(e)001:70: nub pa med par gnas la yang dag zhugs //
NK113(e)001:71: dam pa'i grib bsil la brten de bas nyung //
NK113(e)001:72: gang phyir rang nyid 'byor pa'i ljon pa dang //
NK113(e)001:73: gzhan dbang rkyen gyis 'byor pa'i u dum war /
NK113(e)001:74: gnyis ka'i yon tan 'byor pa rnam pa bcus //
NK113(e)001:75: dal ba brgyad la 'khyud 'di slar mi rnyed //
NK113(e)001:76: ci phyir rus sbal mgrin dang gnya' shing dpe //
NK113(e)001:77: grangs ni mi dang dud 'gro nyin mtshan gyi //
NK113(e)001:78: skar mas phye ba de snyed yi dwags dang //
NK113(e)001:79: dmyal ba rnams la rim pas shes par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:80: de phyir dal ba'i gru chen 'dzin pa'i dus //
NK113(e)001:81: sdug bsngal chu gter pha mtha' ma brgal na //
NK113(e)001:82: chos lam mgron pos gnyer zhing skabs btsal ba'i //
NK113(e)001:83: mnyam pa 'bras med bgyis la phyogs pa yin //
NK113(e)001:84: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:85: dal 'byor gyi rnam par dbye ba'i tshoms te le'u dang po'o ////
NK113(e)001:86: srid pa brtan g.yo chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhi'i //
NK113(e)001:87: ngo bos bskal pa'i tshad du btags pa yang //
NK113(e)001:88: 'jig pa'i rten gyur ming gis sma bab pa'i //
NK113(e)001:89: chad pa gcod la me bdun chu gcig 'ong //
NK113(e)001:90: lha mi'i ston pa rdo rje'i sku mchog kyang //
NK113(e)001:91: rtag par lta la gzigs pa yol ba yi //
NK113(e)001:92: gzhom gzhig bral ba'i sri zhu lhod gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:93: zhi ba'i dbyings la dgyes pa'i mngon rtogs ngom //
NK113(e)001:94: bsam gtan grub nas bskal bar gnas pa'i khur //
NK113(e)001:95: don med gyur te 'chi ba de mthong nas //
NK113(e)001:96: tshangs dbang bde 'byung 'khor los sgyur rnams kyang //
NK113(e)001:97: 'chi bdag bdud la gzur ba'i thabs mi bsam //
NK113(e)001:98: mtho ris sman ljongs nyams dgar 'khrigs pa yi //
NK113(e)001:99: skyes bu'i tshe srog yid la yang nas yang //
NK113(e)001:100: bgyid pa'i rngon pa lag na be con can //
NK113(e)001:101: don gnyer gcig pu nyid las gzhan mi sems //
NK113(e)001:102: so ka'i tshi bas gdungs pa'i skye bo dag /
NK113(e)001:103: ston zla gsal ba'i 'od la dga' gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:104: nyin zhags brgya yi rang gi tshe thal ba'i //
NK113(e)001:105: gnas la sems nas skrag par gyur pa med //
NK113(e)001:106: skyes bu'i rtsol bas byas la nyag phran myur //
NK113(e)001:107: de bas sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwags te //
NK113(e)001:108: de bas mkhar rgyu de bas nyi zla lha //
NK113(e)001:109: kun las mgyogs pa mi yi tshe 'gro yin //
NK113(e)001:110: dar la bab pa rga ba'i chad pas tshe //
NK113(e)001:111: 'du ba rnal mar gnas pa na bas dkrug /
NK113(e)001:112: phun tshogs rten cing 'brel 'byung rgud pas 'joms //
NK113(e)001:113: 'chi bas srog la rgol ba myur por 'ong //
NK113(e)001:114: gang tshe gshin rje'i g.yul ngor pham pa de //
NK113(e)001:115: skyabs dang dpung gnyen bral ba'i g.yang sar rgyug /'tsho ba'i mdangs dang dbang pos rnam par spang //
NK113(e)001:116: sman dang sman pa dag kyang de la 'bros //
NK113(e)001:117: bskyod la ngal ba thob pa'i yan lag dang //
NK113(e)001:118: dbugs ni dbang med mthu yis g.yob cing ngar //
NK113(e)001:119: nye du 'brel bas bskor zhing gdungs na yang //
NK113(e)001:120: bshol 'debs lcags kyu'i brtan pa bral bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:121: de yid dbugs kyi 'gyu ba rta rnga'i lce //
NK113(e)001:122: 'chi bdag dgra s+t+wa rnon pos bkas gyur pas //
NK113(e)001:123: mdzes pa spangs pa'i so zho ngom bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:124: las dbang srid pa'i mun nag stug por 'jug /
NK113(e)001:125: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:126: mi rtag pa'i tshoms te le'u gnyis pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:127: de ltar 'jig rten pha rol son pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:128: go 'phang gang gi tha gus 'dogs pa'i tshul //
NK113(e)001:129: dge spyad sdig goms kho nas nye bar len //
NK113(e)001:130: kun rdzob bden pa bslu ba med pa yin //
NK113(e)001:131: gang zhig sa bon rnam pa sna tshogs mthu //
NK113(e)001:132: zhing pa rnams kyi thog la gsal ba bzhin //
NK113(e)001:133: skye ba gzhan du 'dris shing goms byas pa'i //
NK113(e)001:134: las tshul mang pos 'gro 'di sna tshogs byas //
NK113(e)001:135: sa bla mthon por gshegs pa'i mkha' lding gi //
NK113(e)001:136: grib ma re zhig blta bar mi mngon yang //
NK113(e)001:137: gzugs can nyid dang 'du 'bral spangs pa bzhin //
NK113(e)001:138: tshogs shing dus la babs tshe lhag par mngon //
NK113(e)001:139: bsod nams ma yin bya ba rta gdong mes //
NK113(e)001:140: mtho ris rgya mtsho'i rlabs kyang skems nus shing //
NK113(e)001:141: rnam mkhyen gru rdzings bshig pa'i dpe dang don //
NK113(e)001:142: las brgya pa dang rgya cher rol pas bstan //
NK113(e)001:143: mnar la shin tu brtul phod ngan song gis //
NK113(e)001:144: dge bcu'i dpung pa btsan pa'i dpa' bo'i yul //
NK113(e)001:145: g.yul gyi phru mas btab pa ma mchis te //
NK113(e)001:146: dam bca' nyams pa mtha' dag khyod dbang song //
NK113(e)001:147: la la'i tshul khrims la la'i tshe dang srog /
NK113(e)001:148: la la'i dka' thub la la'i chos dang nor //
NK113(e)001:149: la la'i ngo tsha la la'i khrel yod rnams //
NK113(e)001:150: sdig pa'i ched du gtong ba shin tu mang //
NK113(e)001:151: gang phyin yon gnas nye du 'khor 'bangs dang //
NK113(e)001:152: yul khams bsrung ba'i slad du stobs chen gyi //
NK113(e)001:153: sdig pa'i gnyis 'thung dkris pa btang na'ang //
NK113(e)001:154: rnam smin bgo bsha' bya ru med pa yin //
NK113(e)001:155: rnyed la brkam zhing bde ba 'ba' zhig sred //
NK113(e)001:156: snyan pa lhur len bstod na khengs 'gyur la //
NK113(e)001:157: gang las gcig shos bzhi yi sma bab pa'i //
NK113(e)001:158: byis pa 'di dag 'jig rten chos kyis bslus //
NK113(e)001:159: ris gzugs dbang thang la sogs 'phang gtod cing //
NK113(e)001:160: snyom las 'phye ba'i phag tu yib pa dang //
NK113(e)001:161: mngon pa'i nga rgyal ma rungs slong ba rnams //
NK113(e)001:162: dka' thub dpal la sdang ba'i srin por 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:163: brkam chags sems kyi nus pa brtan po yi //
NK113(e)001:164: zil gyis non pa'i g.yo sgyu'i 'khri shing gis //
NK113(e)001:165: gzhan dag rmongs byas bdag nyid bsrung na'ang //
NK113(e)001:166: gnod chen de ni rang gi khong du zhugs //
NK113(e)001:167: 'khor bar 'du byed dkar nag las 'bras gnyis //
NK113(e)001:168: sa bon nyung ngu las kyang 'bras bu'i gzugs //
NK113(e)001:169: sbom por bskyed la mi dbang nga las nus //
NK113(e)001:170: sran rdog bdun las 'khor los sgyur ba bzhin //
NK113(e)001:171: gang zhig sa bon yung 'bru tsam pa'i shing //
NK113(e)001:172: a sho ta yi 'bras bu lo dus su //
NK113(e)001:173: yal ga re la'ang dpag tshad tsam 'phel bas //
NK113(e)001:174: dge sdig gzugs brnyan 'phel ba'i dper mi phod //
NK113(e)001:175: gang la byed po ma mchis rang bzhin min //
NK113(e)001:176: dkar nag chos kyis bcos pa'i kun slong gis //
NK113(e)001:177: las dang de yi 'bras bu thu chen byas //
NK113(e)001:178: sbyor rjes gnyis dang mi ldan nus pa chung //
NK113(e)001:179: rtsa ba sman du mchis na myu gu'ang sman //
NK113(e)001:180: rtsa ba dug yin myu gu smos cig dgos //
NK113(e)001:181: bsam pa dge dang mi dge'i 'phen byed las //
NK113(e)001:182: dge sdi gzugs brnyan che chung rjes mi 'gro //
NK113(e)001:183: 'di ltar rtag dang mngon zhes gnyen po med //
NK113(e)001:184: yon tan gtso ldan gzhi las byung ba'i las //
NK113(e)001:185: rnam pa lnga po dge sdig lci yang gi //
NK113(e)001:186: nye bar len pa'i rnam rig lags par gsungs //
NK113(e)001:187: kun gyi rten byed kun gzhi lung ma bstan //
NK113(e)001:188: de las yid dang yul lnga'i shes pa la'ang //
NK113(e)001:189: kun la khyab byed ma rig gdon chen gyis //
NK113(e)001:190: nyon mongs gsum bzung 'khor bar mtho dman byas //
NK113(e)001:191: ji ltar me ni 'bar zhing bsreg pa yi //
NK113(e)001:192: gnyen por chas pa cu las gzhan med na //
NK113(e)001:193: dkon mchog gsum po bslus shing spangs pa yi //
NK113(e)001:194: sdig chen de la do zla rnyed pa min //
NK113(e)001:195: de las gzhan du 'gro ba'i kun rtog la //
NK113(e)001:196: rang bzhin 'brel gyur sems dang sems byung las //
NK113(e)001:197: mtha' dag blo yi thug pa ma mchis kyang /
NK113(e)001:198: lus ngag yid la rten dang brten pa can //
NK113(e)001:199: spang bya'i rgyu 'bras rnam pa bcur gnas pa'i //
NK113(e)001:200: lus kyi gsum ni srog gcod ma byin blang //
NK113(e)001:201: log par g.yem las dang po srog gcod ni //
NK113(e)001:202: 'du shes ma 'khrul gzhan srog bsam bzhin gcod //
NK113(e)001:203: phyogs mthun brdeg btsog la sogs 'tshe ba bgyid //
NK113(e)001:204: ma byin blang ba gzhan nor shes bzhin brku //
NK113(e)001:205: phyogs mthun g.yo dang sgyu yis len pa dang //
NK113(e)001:206: 'dod log gla rngan thob la reg pa sprod //
NK113(e)001:207: phyogs mthun bgrod bya ma yin 'khrigs pa'i chos //
NK113(e)001:208: ngag gi bzhi ni rdzun smras gzhan dag 'khrul //
NK113(e)001:209: phyogs mthun 'du shes bslad nas gzhan sems bslu //
NK113(e)001:210: phra ma mthun nas btang snyoms gnas pa 'dral //
NK113(e)001:211: phyogs mthun skyon tshig gzhan bzlos 'khon du 'chos //
NK113(e)001:212: ngag 'khyal bre mo'i gtam las chags sdang skyed //
NK113(e)001:213: phyogs mthun dmag dang chom rkun 'brel med gtam //
NK113(e)001:214: tshig rtsub pha rol snying la 'bigs pa ste //
NK113(e)001:215: phyogs mthun gzhan yid mi bde'i rkyen dang sprod //
NK113(e)001:216: yid kyi gsum las dang po brnab sems ni //
NK113(e)001:217: gzhan 'byor dpal la rngam zhing bdag gir byed //
NK113(e)001:218: phyogs mthun pha rol rdzas la bskam zhing myang //
NK113(e)001:219: gnod sems gzhan la khong 'khrug 'tshe ba slong //
NK113(e)001:220: phyogs mthun phan pas 'brel la 'du bral sgom //
NK113(e)001:221: log lta rgyu 'bras med dang rtag chad blta //
NK113(e)001:222: phyogs mthun med la sgro 'dogs yod la skur //
NK113(e)001:223: kun la 'bras bu bzhi bzhir smin pa'i tshul //
NK113(e)001:224: rnam smin rgyu mthun dbang dang byed pa las //
NK113(e)001:225: rnam smin 'bras bu chos lnga ldan nam min //
NK113(e)001:226: kun slong gsum gyi chung ngus dud 'gro dang //
NK113(e)001:227: 'bring gi yi dwags chen pos dmyal bar 'phen //
NK113(e)001:228: rgyu mthun 'bras bu rnam pa gnyis grub ste //
NK113(e)001:229: byed pa rgyu mthun byed las mthun par skye //
NK113(e)001:230: myong ba rgyu mthun mtho ris thob gyur kyang //
NK113(e)001:231: rim bzhin mi dge bcu la gnyis gnyis ldan //
NK113(e)001:232: 'tsho ba thung la nad kyang rnam grangs mang //
NK113(e)001:233: yo byad nyung zhing dgra dang thun mong can //
NK113(e)001:234: khyim thab mi mdzes dgra zlar 'brel ba dang //
NK113(e)001:235: skur bas gdung zhing gzhan gyis bslu ba mang //
NK113(e)001:236: 'khor g.yog ngan zhing 'dum par dka' ba dang //
NK113(e)001:237: mi snyan mang thos 'thab mo'i tshig tu 'drul //
NK113(e)001:238: tshig bzung mi 'os yid ches zhan pa dang //
NK113(e)001:239: chog mi shes dang 'dod pas gdung ba dang //
NK113(e)001:240: gnod pa'i 'du zhing phan pa 'dral ba dang //
NK113(e)001:241: lta ba ngan dang g.yo sgyus 'khrugs pa'o //
NK113(e)001:242: dbang gi 'bras bu yul dang rten cing 'brel //
NK113(e)001:243: srog gcod sdig to'i khur gyis non pa de //
NK113(e)001:244: sa phyogs bag chung sman shing me tog nyung //
NK113(e)001:245: lo 'bras bza' btung mthu nyams 'ju dka' zhing //
NK113(e)001:246: srog la ya nga'i gnas su phyin par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:247: ma byin blangs par myu gu 'joms pa sla //
NK113(e)001:248: bza' shing yod kyang 'bras bus rnam par smad //
NK113(e)001:249: sad kyis gdung zhing ser bas rnam par 'thag /
NK113(e)001:250: mu ge'i sdug bsngal snying la 'pho bar skye //
NK113(e)001:251: log bar g.yem pas bshang gci'i 'dam rdzab khrod //
NK113(e)001:252: dri nga'i tshor ba rtsub mos dbugs mi phyin //
NK113(e)001:253: mi gtsang ljan ljin dog cing nyams mi dag'i //
NK113(e)001:254: yul du skye ba'i 'khri shing dbang med 'dzugs //
NK113(e)001:255: rdzun gyis 'byor pa g.yo zhing yul mi mthun //
NK113(e)001:256: gzhan gyis bslu dang 'jigs pas brtabs shing skrag /
NK113(e)001:257: phra mas sa phyogs ngam grog gcong rong can //
NK113(e)001:258: bgrod dka' mtho dman can gyi yul la gnas //
NK113(e)001:259: brjod pa rtsub mos rdo gseg tsher ma can //
NK113(e)001:260: sdong dum 'bras ngan rtsub dang nyams mi bde //
NK113(e)001:261: tsh+wa sgo can dang rdul mang nyal nyil khrod //
NK113(e)001:262: yid mi bde ba'i tshor ba nyams su myong //
NK113(e)001:263: bkyal kas so nam ngal pa 'bras med cing //
NK113(e)001:264: dus kyi rjes su mi 'gro mi brtan 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:265: brnab sems spun dang 'bras bu go ldog cing //
NK113(e)001:266: gnas dus gdug pas skabs btsal mthong bar skye //
NK113(e)001:267: gnod sems sdig spyod rgyal po dang 'brel zhing //
NK113(e)001:268: chom rkun sbrul gdug mi rgod gcan gzan rtsub //
NK113(e)001:269: lo tog 'bras bu'i ro yang tsha zhing kha //
NK113(e)001:270: rang bzhin gnod pas bkab pa'i yul du skye //
NK113(e)001:271: log ltas rin po che sogs phun tshogs kyi //
NK113(e)001:272: 'byor pas kun nas spong zhing sman shing nyung //
NK113(e)001:273: me tog 'bras bu dag kyang mthu chung la //
NK113(e)001:274: skyabs dang skyob pa dpung gnyen med par skye //
NK113(e)001:275: skyes bu byed pa'i 'bras bu gang byas las //
NK113(e)001:276: mang por 'phel bas sdug bsngal mtha' dag bskyed //
NK113(e)001:277: 'di ltar mun pa las kyang mun nag can //
NK113(e)001:278: 'khor ba'i btson ra shin tu brnag dka' bar //
NK113(e)001:279: nyer len phung po'i steng du sdug bsngal dbal //
NK113(e)001:280: bzod daka'i tshor ba thob 'di sdig par byas //
NK113(e)001:281: de phyir ma dag gzhan dbang gnas skabs na //
NK113(e)001:282: mtho ris 'phen byed dge ba'i las lam bcu //
NK113(e)001:283: mi dge bcu las phyi rol phyogs pa yi //
NK113(e)001:284: dge ba'i las bcu yang dag bsnyen par mdzod //
NK113(e)001:285: de bsnyen pa las bsod nams cha mthun bcus //
NK113(e)001:286: bde 'gror 'phen cing mi dge rnam pa bcus //
NK113(e)001:287: ngan 'gror 'phen pa'i dkar nag rgyu 'bras la //
NK113(e)001:288: blang dor bgyid pa skyes bu chung ngu'i lam //
NK113(e)001:289: thar pa'i cha mthun zag med dam pa'i rgyu //
NK113(e)001:290: dge bcu bsam gtan gzugs med sbyin sogs drug /
NK113(e)001:291: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi slob lam lngas bsdus //
NK113(e)001:292: de'ang bdag med gnyis kyi don rtogs nas //
NK113(e)001:293: thabs shes zung 'brel dge ba gser 'gyur rtsis //
NK113(e)001:294: srid dang zhi bar 'gal ba'i lcags khams la //
NK113(e)001:295: thebs pas mi gnas ye shes rgyal ba'i khams //
NK113(e)001:296: grub pa 'jig rten 'das pa'i dge ba yin //
NK113(e)001:297: lam dus dmigs par bcas pa bsod nams tshogs //
NK113(e)001:298: dmigs med ye shes tshogs te zung 'jug gis //
NK113(e)001:299: sgrib pa gnyis sbyang sku gnyis mngon du 'thob //
NK113(e)001:300: dag pa'i rgyu 'bras zab mo'i rten 'brel lags //
NK113(e)001:301: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:302: las rgyu 'bras kyi tshoms te le'u gsum pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:303: mngon mtho'i gru bo mchog la bsten pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:304: re zhig ngan song chu srin gdug pa'i lces //
NK113(e)001:305: btang yang thar pa'i skam sar ma phyin pas //
NK113(e)001:306: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi yis ded dpon bsten //
NK113(e)001:307: de la sdug bsngal shes par bya ba ni //
NK113(e)001:308: gnas rigs drug po dma' 'am mtho yang rung //
NK113(e)001:309: sdug bsngal 'gyu dang khyab pa 'du byed kyis //
NK113(e)001:310: dam la ma bzhag 'khor ba yod ma yin //
NK113(e)001:311: phung dkrol bskyed la mgo 'phang bstod pa yi //
NK113(e)001:312: ma rungs 'dod pa'i gdon dang yul gyi dug /
NK113(e)001:313: phan tshun 'dzings shing gtugs pa'i btson ra nas //
NK113(e)001:314: thar pa'i skabs med nyam thag skyo ba 'phel //
NK113(e)001:315: bde ba 'dod la mngon sbyor brtson pa dag /
NK113(e)001:316: gti mug mthus non sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyis //
NK113(e)001:317: mtshon cha rnon po'i dbal la brten byas pas //
NK113(e)001:318: gnod pa'i gnas su rang nyid yang dag sbyar //
NK113(e)001:319: mar me'i gzugs dang phye ma leb bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:320: sgra dang dri ro reg byas bslu ba ni //
NK113(e)001:321: ri dwags bung ba nya dang glang po che //
NK113(e)001:322: 'dod pa'i yul lnga dag dang rten cing 'brel //
NK113(e)001:323: srid pa'i yul la thu ba gtum po'i me //
NK113(e)001:324: khro bo'i mngon spyod rtsub pa gcan gzan dang //
NK113(e)001:325: mi rgod rgyal po'i chad pa las myur ba'i //
NK113(e)001:326: sdug bsngal snga phyi brgyud mas 'gro 'di mnar //
NK113(e)001:327: bdag la bshes sam mi mthun nye dang 'khon //
NK113(e)001:328: bsam par mi nus mtha' dag sems ldan gyis //
NK113(e)001:329: dgra dang mdza' bshes bar ma'i phyogs bzung nas //
NK113(e)001:330: phan dang gnod pa sbyin pa bsam las 'das //
NK113(e)001:331: rdul phran lta bu'i lus kyi bdag gcig pu'i //
NK113(e)001:332: srog rten gzugs su gyur dang 'dod pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:333: mgo dang yan lag bcad gtubs bgyis so cog /
NK113(e)001:334: spungs na lhun po'i che thang nyams par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:335: dmyal gnas zangs zhun khol ma 'thungs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:336: yi dwags lus gyur rnag khrag mi gtsang zos //
NK113(e)001:337: kun tu sdug bsngal rgyu las mchi ma zags //
NK113(e)001:338: phyogs mtha' gtugs pa'i chu klung dag las mang //
NK113(e)001:339: khyad par dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal tshad med de //
NK113(e)001:340: phan tshun gcig gis gcig gsod yang gsos la //
NK113(e)001:341: thig nag sog les gshog 'byar rgyun mi 'chad //
NK113(e)001:342: sdus 'joms mgo brnyan ri dang tho bas 'thag /
NK113(e)001:343: ngu 'bod lcags zhun bkol bar 'tshod cing dbang //
NK113(e)001:344: 'bod sgrog chen po lcags khyim 'bar bar bsreg /
NK113(e)001:345: tsha ba gsal shing 'bar bas lus la 'bigs //
NK113(e)001:346: rab tu tsha ba mdung thung rtse gsum las /
NK113(e)001:347: lus kyi gzhung 'bigs phyi nas lcags bsreg dkri //
NK113(e)001:348: khro chu khol mar 'tshod dang mnar med ni //
NK113(e)001:349: lcags khyim 'bar bar me dang gnyis med bsreg /
NK113(e)001:350: sdug bsngal nyid las dbugs 'byin kun rtog gis //
NK113(e)001:351: nye 'khor sgo 'phar bye ba mdag me'i 'obs //
NK113(e)001:352: ro myags 'dam rdzab stug dang ral gri'i nags //
NK113(e)001:353: chu bo rabs med gshin rje'i khabs thu //
NK113(e)001:354: mdza' bcugs dam bca' dran nas bsnyegs pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:355: tsher ma rnon pos tshabs chen phug pa'i lus //
NK113(e)001:356: 'bar zhing rtsub pa'i lcags kyi bud med kyis //
NK113(e)001:357: 'khyud mthar khwa dang bya rgod mig la 'dru //
NK113(e)001:358: bu yug sprebs pa 'dar ba'i thag pa yin //
NK113(e)001:359: bcings te bskyod par mi nus bzhin gson yang //
NK113(e)001:360: rlung gi mtshon chas rus ba'i gting phug pa'i //
NK113(e)001:361: grang reg so yi bar du 'tshir ltar gdungs //
NK113(e)001:362: chu bur can dang chu bur brdol ba dang //
NK113(e)001:363: a chu'i smre sngags kyi hud so 'tham can //
NK113(e)001:364: ut+pala ltar pags pa drug tshal 'gas //
NK113(e)001:365: pad+ma dang ni pad+ma chen po ltar //
NK113(e)001:366: brgyad dang bcu drug grangs med gas pa'i rma //
NK113(e)001:367: srog chags mchu rnon can gyis 'bigs shing bza' //
NK113(e)001:368: mgal rdum bcad dang sgo 'phar med la 'thums //
NK113(e)001:369: sgo dang ka ba thab dang thag pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:370: sna tshogs las kyi sprul pa'i rang gzugs la //
NK113(e)001:371: nye bar len pa'i sdug bsngal zad mi shes //
NK113(e)001:372: de phyir skye ba'i shwa 'od sdug bsngal gyi /
NK113(e)001:373: rba rlabs ca co sgrog 'di ma bzlog na //
NK113(e)001:374: lha bas lhag pa'i lus rten chu lon yang //
NK113(e)001:375: bstan pa bral ba'i mya ngam thang du 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:376: gzugs med ting 'dzin lung ma bstan pa'i las //
NK113(e)001:377: zad nas srid pa phyi mar 'du byed dang //
NK113(e)001:378: gzugs khams bsam gtan snga ma'i las zad de //
NK113(e)001:379: 'og mar lhung ba 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal myong //
NK113(e)001:380: tshangs dang lha dbang 'khor los sgyur ba yang //
NK113(e)001:381: sprin bar nyi bzhin dkar po'i rnam smin gyi //
NK113(e)001:382: skabs btsal spangs pa'i mod la mar me'i lces //
NK113(e)001:383: 'thungs pa'i zhun mar bzhin du nyams par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:384: mnan na nem pa'i reg pa 'jam po dang //
NK113(e)001:385: lha klu mi'am ci yi la thod kyi //
NK113(e)001:386: rkang pa'i chu skyes dmar byas dbang po'ang //
NK113(e)001:387: lcags kyi gsal shing 'bar ba'i rtse mor gdungs //
NK113(e)001:388: mtho ris bu mo'i nu ma gsar ba la //
NK113(e)001:389: reg pa'i 'khri shing bsten de dga' tshal dang //
NK113(e)001:390: gzhal med khang mdzes mu tig d+r+wa phyed can //
NK113(e)001:391: spangs nas me mur 'obs nang spyi'u tshugs ltung //
NK113(e)001:392: gos bstan me tog rnyings pa'i lha mo dag /
NK113(e)001:393: rdul gyis gdong pa bkru ba'i zol zhig nas //
NK113(e)001:394: nye du rnams la blta zhing ngu ba yi //
NK113(e)001:395: 'chi 'pho'i sdug bsngal lta bu mi la med //
NK113(e)001:396: gnya' shing 'dzin ri'i sa bla 'gegs pa la //
NK113(e)001:397: gdugs gyur snang byed chen po nyi zla gnyis //
NK113(e)001:398: slan chad mun pa'i smag gi btson ra ru //
NK113(e)001:399: long ba chen po'i gnas skabs 'thob bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:400: lha yi dpal la sdang ba'i phrag dog gi /
NK113(e)001:401: dgra s+t+was rang snying tshal par bkas nas slar //
NK113(e)001:402: dpung pa gtum po'i g.yul ngor bdag nyid kyi //
NK113(e)001:403: mgo dang yan lag gtubs pas lha min mnar //
NK113(e)001:404: 'tsho ba chu bur lta bur g.yo ba yi //
NK113(e)001:405: mi dag yid mi bde dang 'khrugs pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:406: sdug bsngal snga mas phyi ma nye bar len //
NK113(e)001:407: mdze can phol gyi thog tu rmas gtugs bzhin //
NK113(e)001:408: mngon mtho'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i skyed tshal du //
NK113(e)001:409: 'dod pa'i ro la gdung ba dug can gyi //
NK113(e)001:410: bza' bas rnam par sma bab dka' thub lus //
NK113(e)001:411: mig 'phrul lta bur thob 'di 'gyur ba can //
NK113(e)001:412: rkang pa'i reg pa khur du mi bzod pa'i //
NK113(e)001:413: ngal bcas sems kyi glang po'i gnyar 'dzegs kyang //
NK113(e)001:414: de yi bsam pa rtse dgas rgod gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:415: g.yas sar smad pas 'du byed sdug bsngal mtshon //
NK113(e)001:416: de ltar sdug bsngal nyid gsum 'brog dgon na //
NK113(e)001:417: skye rga na 'chi'i tshor ba rnam par 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:418: smon pa med pa'i mi sdug dgra dang phrad //
NK113(e)001:419: sdug pa yid la goms byas gnas min phyogs //
NK113(e)001:420: 'dod pa'i yul la 'byor pas ngo tshar byas //
NK113(e)001:421: nyer len phung po'i steng du dka' thub 'dus //
NK113(e)001:422: rnam pa brgyad kyi sdug bsngal rtul phod pas //
NK113(e)001:423: mi yi skye ba'i 'khri shing rtag tu gtser //
NK113(e)001:424: shin tu dri nga mi gtsang rnyog ma can //
NK113(e)001:425: kun nas dog pa mun nag 'thibs po'i khrod //
NK113(e)001:426: mngal gnas lcags khyim sgo 'phar spangs lta'i nang //
NK113(e)001:427: ma rig rnam shes khu khrag dbus na brten //
NK113(e)001:428: mer mer nur nur ltar ltar mkhrang gor nya //
NK113(e)001:429: rus sbal bzhin te bdun phrag bdun rtsa drug /
NK113(e)001:430: gnas 'gyur yid mi 'ong ba'i rnam pa la //
NK113(e)001:431: dbang po yan lag ba spu la sogs 'grub //
NK113(e)001:432: bdun phrag sum cu rtsa bdun grangs snyed tshe //
NK113(e)001:433: brtas dang cher bskyed g.yo zhing chor bas gdung //
NK113(e)001:434: ma yi spyod lam bkres skom tsha grang gi //
NK113(e)001:435: rnam 'gyur las byung sdug bsngal dpag tu med //
NK113(e)001:436: btsa' ba'i dus kyi rjes 'gro de yi lus //
NK113(e)001:437: bzod daka'i sdus 'joms khur du 'phos pa lta'i //
NK113(e)001:438: sdug bsngal nye bar spyad pas mtho btsams nas //
NK113(e)001:439: ma bu gnyis ka mod la srog 'dor ram //
NK113(e)001:440: cig shos gnod pa bdo ba'i khur gyis btsa' //
NK113(e)001:441: mngal gnas rlon pas dkris shing dri nga ba //
NK113(e)001:442: sran mi bzod pa sha rmen zhig pa ltas //
NK113(e)001:443: sngon gyi dran pa'i stobs rnams nyams byas shing //
NK113(e)001:444: reg pa'i rnam pas gzir ba'i sdug bsngal myong //
NK113(e)001:445: rga ba'i chad pas non pa'i lang tsho la //
NK113(e)001:446: nyams dang yid mi bde ba'i khur babs pas //
NK113(e)001:447: bskyod pa'i mthu nyams 'khar ba'i gzhan dbang can //
NK113(e)001:448: 'gro ldog g.yo ba'i lhu tshigs rnam par 'khur //
NK113(e)001:449: dbang po rgud nas 'dod pa'i yon tan dang //
NK113(e)001:450: yul gyi longs spyod sprin gyis bkab pa yi //
NK113(e)001:451: tsha zer bzhin du rmongs dang mthu nyams pa'i //
NK113(e)001:452: 'du shes 'khrugs pa'i mal du shin tu 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:453: rang bzhin snyoms ldan 'du ba'i rdzing bu ni //
NK113(e)001:454: rnyog pa can bgyid na ba'i tshor ba yis //
NK113(e)001:455: phung po lnga yi nyer len dub byas te //
NK113(e)001:456: 'tsho ba'i brtan pa bral ba'i dogs pas skrag /
NK113(e)001:457: srid pa 'di na srog gi rin thang la //
NK113(e)001:458: thug pa med pas 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal gyis //
NK113(e)001:459: rnam par gtugs pa'i skyes bu gnyen 'dun dang //
NK113(e)001:460: longs spyod las thal sa tshugs med par 'gro //
NK113(e)001:461: mi sdug yul dang phrad pa'i sdug bsngal gyi //
NK113(e)001:462: pho nyas rnam par gzir zhing smad pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:463: bde ba'i 'bab stegs zhig pa'i ngal gso ltar //
NK113(e)001:464: dbugs 'byin thob pa med pas lhag par nyen //
NK113(e)001:465: byams sdug 'du 'bral gsar par bkod pa yi //
NK113(e)001:466: gdung bas nyams pa'i dka' thub gzugs gyur na //
NK113(e)001:467: nor bzang dri za mo yi dbang gyur pa'i //
NK113(e)001:468: lam phrang 'tshe bas bkab las las mtha' ring //
NK113(e)001:469: 'dod pas phongs dang dbul ba'i skyes bu rnams //
NK113(e)001:470: bkres skom don ma grub pa'i re dogs kyi //
NK113(e)001:471: gzhan dbang kho nar lus ngag chud gson pa'i //
NK113(e)001:472: sdug bsngal sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwags dngos //
NK113(e)001:473: gzugs la rten bcas tshor bas rang bzhin shes //
NK113(e)001:474: 'du shes las de rgyun chags 'du byed kyi //
NK113(e)001:475: phyin chad sa bon bskrun dang rnam shes kyi //
NK113(e)001:476: sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba'i nye bar len //
NK113(e)001:477: phung po lnga po 'di dag sdug bsngal rnams //
NK113(e)001:478: kun gyis 'byung gnas kun gyi rten dang snod //
NK113(e)001:479: kun gyi rgyu 'bras bdag por mkhyen 'tshal nas //
NK113(e)001:480: kun 'byung las dang nyon mongs spang 'tshal lo //
NK113(e)001:481: de ltar spangs nas skyes bu 'bring gi lam //
NK113(e)001:482: bden pa bzhi yi shing rta la zhon rnams //
NK113(e)001:483: 'gog pa mngon gyur mya ngan 'das pa'i khams //
NK113(e)001:484: thar pa mchog gi go 'phang nyid du 'gro //
NK113(e)001:485: rten 'chos kun gyi rtsa ba ma rig pa //
NK113(e)001:486: de las 'du byed rnam shes ming dang gzugs //
NK113(e)001:487: de las skye zhing mched pa rnam pa drug /
NK113(e)001:488: de las reg pa reg las tshor ba ste //
NK113(e)001:489: de las sred pa sred las len pa dang //
NK113(e)001:490: de las srid pa srid las skye ba ste //
NK113(e)001:491: skye ba yod na 'dod pas phongs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:492: mya ngan na rga 'chi sogs sdug bsngal gyi //
NK113(e)001:493: phung po shin tu che ba grub pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:494: skye ba 'gags pas thams cad 'gag 'gyur ba'i //
NK113(e)001:495: rten cing 'brel 'byung rgyu 'bras zab mo ni //
NK113(e)001:496: rgyal ba bden par smra ba'i gsung gi mdzod //
NK113(e)001:497: de lta mod kyi srid par 'du byed pa'i //
NK113(e)001:498: mtho dman las dang dkar nag rgyu 'bras chos //
NK113(e)001:499: kun las 'das pa zhi ba dam pa'i dngos //
NK113(e)001:500: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid rtogs las 'byung //
NK113(e)001:501: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:502: 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi tshoms te le'u bzhi pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:503: yul ni mthun par gyur pa dag la bsten //
NK113(e)001:504: skyes bu dam pa bsten las yon tan 'thob //
NK113(e)001:505: legs par smon dang bsod nams skyabs 'dun la //
NK113(e)001:506: 'khor lo chen po bzhi zhes klu dbang bzhed //
NK113(e)001:507: tshogs kyi dbus na dug can zas lta bu'o //
NK113(e)001:508: yul dang rkyen gyi rnam 'gyur shin tu rgod //
NK113(e)001:509: de las bsrings nas gcig pur zhi la mos //
NK113(e)001:510: rnyed la ma chags rlung dang mkha' lding bzhin //
NK113(e)001:511: ri dwags bzhin du dben par gnas pa de //
NK113(e)001:512: bab col spyod pas 'khrugs par mi 'gyur la //
NK113(e)001:513: gzhi la brten na gzhan ngo bsrung ba dang //
NK113(e)001:514: phrag dog bzod pa'i snying stobs bri bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:515: yid ni shin tu reng sa pa'i byi la yang //
NK113(e)001:516: 'gro 'dug zhi zhing spyod lam des pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:517: sdig pa'i grogs kyis bag phebs bsten pa'i yul //
NK113(e)001:518: phun sum tshogs kyang chos las phral du nyams //
NK113(e)001:519: bskyod pa yang ba'i nyi zla kun dang mdza' //
NK113(e)001:520: 'dris shing gnyug mar gnas pa khro bas gdung //
NK113(e)001:521: gsar pa gsar par gyur pa'i yul 'jam zhing //
NK113(e)001:522: skye bo kun kyang bshes par 'gyur ba mthong //
NK113(e)001:523: sems ldan lta bur ca co sgrog gyur yang //
NK113(e)001:524: brjod pa bzang ngan rjes su de yi sems //
NK113(e)001:525: 'gro ba ma yin brag cha lta bu yi //
NK113(e)001:526: kun spyod can la yul gyi dam bca' bral //
NK113(e)001:527: skyes bu tshangs par mtshungs pa spyod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:528: bsam gtan don la gcig tu sems pa yi //
NK113(e)001:529: brtul zhugs brtan par ma son gang dang gang //
NK113(e)001:530: yul dang grogs la brten nas mtho dman byed //
NK113(e)001:531: ston pas gnang bas gzhan la bsod nams bskyed //
NK113(e)001:532: bdag kyang dka' thub nyams par mi 'gyur la //
NK113(e)001:533: slong ba rnams kyis yid bzhin nor bu ltar //
NK113(e)001:534: mthun par gyur pa'i bsod snyoms kho na yin //
NK113(e)001:535: 'tsho ba shin tu ma dag thabs kyis brku //
NK113(e)001:536: rnyed pas rnyed 'tshol kha gsag tshul 'chos dang //
NK113(e)001:537: thob kyis 'jal ba'i log 'tsho rnam pa lngas //
NK113(e)001:538: drang srong rnams kyi brtul zhugs sma bab 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:539: de phyir gnas mal bzang dang 'tsho ba bzang //
NK113(e)001:540: grogs dang sbyor ba bzang pos snying stobs slong //
NK113(e)001:541: bslab pa kun gyi yon tan rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:542: skyes bu dam pa dag la bsten par bgyid //
NK113(e)001:543: ji ltar ma la ya yi nags klung du //
NK113(e)001:544: rnam par 'khyams pa'i sdong dum phal pa'ang //
NK113(e)001:545: yal 'dab brlan pa'i tsan+dana dris bsung ltar //
NK113(e)001:546: gang la bsten pa de yi rjes su 'gro //
NK113(e)001:547: dam pa'i chos tshul mtha' dag rdzogs pa ni //
NK113(e)001:548: snyigs ma'i mthus byas rnyed par dka' na'ang //
NK113(e)001:549: sdom gsum gnang bkag gtsang ma'i sa gzhi la //
NK113(e)001:550: thos dang snying rje chen pos thugs rgyud brlan //
NK113(e)001:551: sde snod sngags rgyud rgya mtsho'i cho ga mkhas //
NK113(e)001:552: spangs rtogs ye shes dri med 'bras bus phyug /
NK113(e)001:553: bsdu dngos bzhi yi me tog rnam bkra bas //
NK113(e)001:554: skal bzang slob ma'i bung ba sdud la bsten //
NK113(e)001:555: khyad par man ngag ston pa'i bla ma ni //
NK113(e)001:556: dbang thob dam tshig la gnas shin tu zhi //
NK113(e)001:557: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud don khong du chud //
NK113(e)001:558: bsnyen bsgrub rtags rdzogs rtogs par rang rgyud grol //
NK113(e)001:559: snying rje tshad med gzhan don 'ba' zhig gnyer //
NK113(e)001:560: bya ba nyung zhing nan tan chos la sems //
NK113(e)001:561: skyo shas cher ldan gzhan yang de la bskul //
NK113(e)001:562: thabs la mkhas shing brgyud pa'i byin rlabs ldan //
NK113(e)001:563: de lta bu la bsten na dngos grub myur //
NK113(e)001:564: bram ze bzhin du cho rigs srung ba'am //
NK113(e)001:565: bsti gnas nyams par dogs pa'i rdzing bu ru //
NK113(e)001:566: thos bsam 'bras bu gnas min khrus la zhugs //
NK113(e)001:567: shing gi rang thag lta bu'i lam ston dang //
NK113(e)001:568: so so skye bo'i rang bzhin ma 'gal yang //
NK113(e)001:569: blun po'i dad pas bab col gnas la sbyang //
NK113(e)001:570: rnyed dang bkur sti'i mchod pas khengs gyur pa //
NK113(e)001:571: khron pa'i lag 'gro lta bu'i bshes gnyen dang //
NK113(e)001:572: thos pa nyung zhing sdom dang dam tshig 'chal //
NK113(e)001:573: rgyud tshod dma' la kun spyod sa blar gshegs //
NK113(e)001:574: byams dang snying rje'i dpyang thag chad pa yi //
NK113(e)001:575: smyon pa'i lam mkhan rnams las sdig pa 'phel //
NK113(e)001:576: khyad par rang las yon tan lhag bcas min //
NK113(e)001:577: byang chub sems bral grags pa'i mthus bsten na //
NK113(e)001:578: long ba'i ded dpon nor ba chen po ste //
NK113(e)001:579: zol 'grogs mun pa'i smag tu 'khyam par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:580: de phyir dam pa shin tu ma brtags na //
NK113(e)001:581: dad pa can gyi dge tshogs chud gson cing //
NK113(e)001:582: dal ba skabs gcig rnyed pa sbrul gdug dang /
NK113(e)001:583: shing gi grib ma nor bzhin bslu bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:584: mtha' dag yon tan 'byor pa'i bla ma ni //
NK113(e)001:585: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes thugs rje'i khams //
NK113(e)001:586: gdul bya'i yul la skyes bu'i gzugs kyis byon //
NK113(e)001:587: dngos grub kun gyi rtsa ba bla na med //
NK113(e)001:588: drang ba'i don du kun dang phyogs mthun la //
NK113(e)001:589: nges pa'i don du kun dang rnam gzhag 'gal //
NK113(e)001:590: dgongs pa can phyir kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK113(e)001:591: the tshom gcod mkhas log bsgrub skyo ngal bzod //
NK113(e)001:592: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol ba'i gru bo che //
NK113(e)001:593: lam mchog 'khrul par mi 'gyur ded dpon dngos //
NK113(e)001:594: las nyon me tshogs 'joms pas bdud rtsi'i char //
NK113(e)001:595: ma rig mun pa sel bas nyi zlar mtshungs //
NK113(e)001:596: theg pa shin tu che bas sa gzhi 'dra //
NK113(e)001:597: phan dang bde ba'i 'byung gnas dpag bsam shing //
NK113(e)001:598: chos kyi mdzod ldan bum pa bzang po ste //
NK113(e)001:599: kun 'byung yid bzhin nor bu las kyang lhag /
NK113(e)001:600: kun la snyoms par byams pas pha ma yin //
NK113(e)001:601: che zhing myur ba'i snying rje chu klung mtshungs //
NK113(e)001:602: 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dga' ba ri dbang 'dra //
NK113(e)001:603: 'khrugs pa med pa'i btang snyoms char sprin bzhin //
NK113(e)001:604: de 'dra'i bla ma sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK113(e)001:605: gnod pa byas kyang bde ba'i lam 'brel na //
NK113(e)001:606: zol med dad pas bsten pa'i skyes bu la //
NK113(e)001:607: mngon mtho nges legs yon tan char bzhin 'bab //
NK113(e)001:608: nad pas sman pa mgron pos skyes ma dang //
NK113(e)001:609: 'jigs pas ram zla tshong bas ded dpon dang //
NK113(e)001:610: gru pas mnyam pa bzhin du skye shi dang //
NK113(e)001:611: nyon mongs dgra yi 'jigs pas bsten par bya //
NK113(e)001:612: de la nye bar len pa slob ma ste //
NK113(e)001:613: snod dang bral la bcud kyi phan mi thogs //
NK113(e)001:614: zang zing tsam gyi tshim pa thob gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:615: bcos ma'i dad pas dus bzhi'i 'gyur ldog dngos //
NK113(e)001:616: dang po chos lam mi tshud g.yag rgod bzhin //
NK113(e)001:617: bar du thob bsam la sdang tshe 'di gnyer //
NK113(e)001:618: tha mar sdig pa'i grogs kyi phyogs bzung nas //
NK113(e)001:619: las mtha' log pa nags matha'i mi rgod 'dra //
NK113(e)001:620: dam pa'i drung na gnas tshe 'bros la rings //
NK113(e)001:621: yul gang bgrod par phyogs na sdig pas 'dzin //
NK113(e)001:622: dben par ched du bskul na chos tshugs gzhi /
NK113(e)001:623: rlung gi rjes 'gro ku sha'i rtse mo bzhin //
NK113(e)001:624: mi gzhi ngan pa'i zol sbyor tha gu'i lces //
NK113(e)001:625: bla ma spos kyi glang po ltar bsnyen nas //
NK113(e)001:626: dam chos gla rtsi'i rnyed pa thob nas slar //
NK113(e)001:627: rngon la yang dag spro bas dam tshig 'phen //
NK113(e)001:628: blo sna nyams 'og ma chud mtha' dag ni //
NK113(e)001:629: gdams pa'i gnad 'gag thob pa slar btang nas //
NK113(e)001:630: sna tshogs yig sna 'tshol ba'i dub pa'i mthar //
NK113(e)001:631: gsar pa ma mthong sngon ma mtha' dag nyams //
NK113(e)001:632: yang dag don la sbyong ba'i dad pa dang //
NK113(e)001:633: ltar snang tshe 'di bsgrub pa'i 'dod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:634: gnyis kar lung du ma bstan gzu lum can //
NK113(e)001:635: gsum du gnas pa'i mtshan nyid brtag pa gces //
NK113(e)001:636: go cha che la blo gros shin tu brtan //
NK113(e)001:637: lus dang srog la mi blta rim gro bgyid //
NK113(e)001:638: ci gsung bkar dkri bdag nyid mi bsrung ba'i //
NK113(e)001:639: skyes bu de ni mos gus kho nas grol //
NK113(e)001:640: dad dang shes rab thos dang snying rje che //
NK113(e)001:641: sdom dang dam tshig la gus sgo gsum dul //
NK113(e)001:642: khong yangs gtong phod dag snang khrel yod ldan //
NK113(e)001:643: bla ma shin tu bsrung bas mdzangs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:644: bka' bkyon dag la mi khro rta mchog bzhin //
NK113(e)001:645: gru ltar 'gro 'ong gnas la skyo ba spangs //
NK113(e)001:646: zam pa lta bur bzang ngan thams cad theg /
NK113(e)001:647: bzo stegs bzhin du tsha grang gang yang bzod //
NK113(e)001:648: bka' bzhin nyan pa bran khol lta bu dang //
NK113(e)001:649: nga rgyal spangs pa phyag dar lta bu dang //
NK113(e)001:650: dreg pa spangs pa khyu mchog rwa chad ltas //
NK113(e)001:651: bla ma bsten zhes sde snod dag las gsungs //
NK113(e)001:652: 'byor pa yod na dkon mchog bzhi pa mchod //
NK113(e)001:653: zhabs tog sri zhu lus ngag bkol ba'i las //
NK113(e)001:654: mtha' dag nam yang chud zos gyur pa med //
NK113(e)001:655: mnyes pa gsum gyi nang nas sgrub pa mchog /
NK113(e)001:656: mdzad spyod gang yang log par mi blta ste //
NK113(e)001:657: 'phags pa'i yul gyi dbang phyug phal mo che //
NK113(e)001:658: gdol ba g.yung po sdig spyod phal pa'i tshul //
NK113(e)001:659: nyams pa las kyang shin tu nyams par yod //
NK113(e)001:660: rang gi nyer len dbang du ma gyur bar //
NK113(e)001:661: 'khrul pa brtan pa'i nyes pa tshad med de //
NK113(e)001:662: sde snod bcu gnyis blo la chub pa yi //
NK113(e)001:663: dge slong skrar bzang sdig pa'i mthus btab nas //
NK113(e)001:664: ston pa'i mdzad pa g.yo sgyur mthong ba'i tshul //
NK113(e)001:665: legs par bsam nas rang gi rang nyid 'chos //
NK113(e)001:666: gal te bla ma sdang bar mngon gyur na //
NK113(e)001:667: bdag skyon gzigs nas spyo bas gdul ba yi //
NK113(e)001:668: dus la babs par rig nas bshags sdom bya //
NK113(e)001:669: cang shes skyes bu bdud kyi dbang mi 'gro //
NK113(e)001:670: bla ma bzhengs tshe stan la 'dug pa min //
NK113(e)001:671: bzhugs pa'i dus na bsnyun 'dri nyer spyad dbul //
NK113(e)001:672: gshegs na zhabs 'bring sngon rjes g.yas nas min //
NK113(e)001:673: stan dang bzhon pa smad sogs bsod nams nyams //
NK113(e)001:674: sgo 'phar brdeg dang sgeg chos ngo 'dzum gnag /
NK113(e)001:675: rdzun dang bab col bzhad gad 'brel med gtam //
NK113(e)001:676: gus dang 'jigs bcas ma yin ji mi snyam //
NK113(e)001:677: spangs la sgo gsum nye bar zhi bas bsten //
NK113(e)001:678: bla ma dmod cing sdang ba'i gang zag dang //
NK113(e)001:679: bshes par mi bya nus pas de bzlog cing //
NK113(e)001:680: bag phebs smra na sdig pa'i gzhan dbang ni //
NK113(e)001:681: lhag par mthu che dam tshig skyon can byed //
NK113(e)001:682: 'grogs par bde ba ska rags lta bu dang //
NK113(e)001:683: 'jug pa bde ba lan tsh+wa lta bu dang //
NK113(e)001:684: bzod sran che ba ka ba lta bu yis //
NK113(e)001:685: bla ma'i 'khor dang rdo rje'i spun la gnyen //
NK113(e)001:686: rdzing bu mchog la bsten pa'i ngang pa dang //
NK113(e)001:687: bung bas me tog bcud la ro myang bzhin //
NK113(e)001:688: rtag tu 'grogs pa'i spyod pa ngo mtshar can //
NK113(e)001:689: skyo ngal med pas bla ma'i thugs bzung nas //
NK113(e)001:690: dad pa'i nye bar len pas yon tan myang //
NK113(e)001:691: 'jug pa'i spyod la nges par zhugs pa yi //
NK113(e)001:692: dam pa mchog gi bsod nams ye shes tshogs //
NK113(e)001:693: gang gi khrod du'ang don mthun spyod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:694: mngag gzhug bang phyin phyag dar tshun chod kyang //
NK113(e)001:695: ngal ba 'bras bcas tshogs kyi lam mchog yin //
NK113(e)001:696: ci phyir skabs su 'gro dang tshogs kyi zhing //
NK113(e)001:697: bla ma bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor phyi nang gnyis //
NK113(e)001:698: bskyed rdzogs bsgrub bya'i ngo bo 'dir 'dus pas //
NK113(e)001:699: mdo rgyud kun nas sangs rgyas nyid du bstan //
NK113(e)001:700: rmongs pa phal cher gzugs brnyan 'dri zhing sgom //
NK113(e)001:701: dngos su bzhugs la rim gro bgyi ba med //
NK113(e)001:702: gnas lugs sgom zer bla ma'i thugs mi shes //
NK113(e)001:703: sgrub dang bsgrub bya 'gal ba nyon re mongs //
NK113(e)001:704: mos gus med bzhin bar dor mjal ba mtshar //
NK113(e)001:705: dang po bla ma brtag la mkhas pa dang //
NK113(e)001:706: bar du bla ma bsten la mkhas pa dang //
NK113(e)001:707: tha mar dgongs spyod bslab la mkhas pa yi //
NK113(e)001:708: skyes bu de ni yang dag lam la 'gro //
NK113(e)001:709: gang tshe zhi la sdang ba'i 'byung po yi //
NK113(e)001:710: bsam pa skyes bu'i gzugs su 'ongs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:711: g.yo dang sgyus spyod nag po'i chos la bsten //
NK113(e)001:712: dam pa dmod sogs dkar po'i chos la sdang //
NK113(e)001:713: ji tsam 'grogs bzhin sdig spyod 'thor rlung 'tshub //
NK113(e)001:714: dge ba'i lo tog 'joms pa'i sdig grogs la //
NK113(e)001:715: bsten pa'i blo gros blun po bdud sdes bcom //
NK113(e)001:716: de phyir dge ba'i bshes dang grogs bsten pas //
NK113(e)001:717: bde legs yon tan mthong ba'i chos la zin //
NK113(e)001:718: rgyal dang rgyal sras rnams kyis rtag tu dgongs //
NK113(e)001:719: mngon mtho nges legs yon tan kun gyis 'byor //
NK113(e)001:720: tshogs rdzogs grib dag dngos grub rnam gnyis 'thob //
NK113(e)001:721: sa lam yon tan bla nas blar 'gro bas //
NK113(e)001:722: rnal 'byor sgom zhing bsgrub pa bsod nams tshogs //
NK113(e)001:723: thugs rgyud gcig tu bsre ba ye shes te //
NK113(e)001:724: tshogs gnyis 'bras bu'i thus ka yin pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:725: bskal par rgyal dang rgyal sras bsnyen bkur zhing //
NK113(e)001:726: bskyed rim brgya phrag bsgom las bla ma ni //
NK113(e)001:727: skad cig dran pa mchog ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK113(e)001:728: dam chos bdud rtsi'i chu klung dpag med mdzod //
NK113(e)001:729: rgyud la 'drongs pa'i dmigs pa bzang po rnams //
NK113(e)001:730: ston pa'i bla ma bzang por rten cing 'brel //
NK113(e)001:731: thabs bzang ba las man ngag 'khyam mi 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:732: nges 'byung bzang po'i rig sngags nus pa can //
NK113(e)001:733: 'khor bar skyo ba med pa'i gdon la thebs //
NK113(e)001:734: bzang po bzhi dang ldan pa'i legs smon yin //
NK113(e)001:735: chos sgor zhugs kyang mod la sun pa dang //
NK113(e)001:736: kun slong dug can 'dres pa'i thos bsam sgom //
NK113(e)001:737: chos las blo nyams srung sdom khur du song //
NK113(e)001:738: chos brgyad dmod pas theg chen brtul zhugs 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:739: legs smon dka' thub bshig pa'i rnyog pa yin //
NK113(e)001:740: thad ka thad ka'i nyon mongs dug chen lnga'i //
NK113(e)001:741: gnyen por che ba skyes bu rnam gsum gyi //
NK113(e)001:742: shing rtar 'dzegs la dus bzhir skyo ba med //
NK113(e)001:743: snang ba mtha' dag chos dang bla mar shar //
NK113(e)001:744: rnam mkhyen rgyur song legs smon grub pa yin //
NK113(e)001:745: mtho ris yon tan bdun po'i dga' ba dang //
NK113(e)001:746: dal bas yang dag mtho la nad med cing //
NK113(e)001:747: ting nge 'dzin dang rnam 'byed shes rab lnga //
NK113(e)001:748: sngon chad bsod nams la gus mngon rtags yin //
NK113(e)001:749: ma bsgom pas ni rig pa 'joms shing 'ong //
NK113(e)001:750: rgyags pa rgyas pas dpal 'byor 'joms shing 'ong //
NK113(e)001:751: rnam par sdang bas legs tshogs 'joms shing 'ong //
NK113(e)001:752: chags pas yang dag mtho ba 'joms shing 'ong //
NK113(e)001:753: gang phyir las dang nyon mongs sdig pa yis //
NK113(e)001:754: rnam par dkrugs pa ma yin blo gros ni //
NK113(e)001:755: shes rab mthu dang skal bas bkol thub pa //
NK113(e)001:756: bsod nams bsags pa'i rtags su rgyan las bshad //
NK113(e)001:757: chos la sems pa'i go cha rnam par sra //
NK113(e)001:758: zab rgyas chos khams rgya mtsho dbang po'i mtshon //
NK113(e)001:759: bdung ba'i blo yi spobs sam mi spobs kun //
NK113(e)001:760: snying stobs gnyen po'i dbang du gtor ba rnams //
NK113(e)001:761: lam mi 'chug par phyin drug steng du 'gro //
NK113(e)001:762: de yi mthun phyogs yan lag bdun pa dang //
NK113(e)001:763: chu gtor la sogs bsags sbyangs mtha' dag yin //
NK113(e)001:764: mi mthun phyogs kyis de la mi bardzi zhing //
NK113(e)001:765: lam du 'gro ba bsod nams dag la bsten //
NK113(e)001:766: 'di ni skyes bu chen po'i lam stegs yin //
NK113(e)001:767: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las //
NK113(e)001:768: 'khor lo chen po bzhi'i tshoms te le'u lnga pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:769: 'jigs pa gsum gyi chu gter 'khrugs pa la //
NK113(e)001:770: skyabs su 'os par yid ches srog brtan pa'i //
NK113(e)001:771: dkon cog gsum gyi grags pa'i gdugs dkar ni //
NK113(e)001:772: bstan la 'jug pa'i thog ma nyid du 'dzin //
NK113(e)001:773: thar par 'gro ba'i lam dang yon tan gyi //
NK113(e)001:774: rten dang snod du dam bca' mi bslu ba //
NK113(e)001:775: skyabs su 'gro ba nyid de de'i sngon du //
NK113(e)001:776: ston dang bstan pa'i yon tan shes pa gces //
NK113(e)001:777: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba dad pa ni //
NK113(e)001:778: skyes bu'i sems la lung du ma bstan pa //
NK113(e)001:779: ston pa mthong dang sde snod bklags pa yi //
NK113(e)001:780: mod la ba spu'i 'khri shing slong bzhin ldang //
NK113(e)001:781: de la dang ba'i dad pa dang po ste //
NK113(e)001:782: de bzhin 'dod dang yid ches phyir mi ldog /
NK113(e)001:783: rnam pa bzhi las skyabs 'gro'i gnas skabs 'dir //
NK113(e)001:784: srog la bab kyang phyir mi ldog pa dgos //
NK113(e)001:785: dad pa skye ba'i rgyu ni bzhi yin te //
NK113(e)001:786: dam pa bsten dang dam pa'i grogs dang 'grogs //
NK113(e)001:787: dkon mchog rjes su dran dang 'khor ba la //
NK113(e)001:788: snying po med pa'i nyes dmigs bsam las skyes //
NK113(e)001:789: thub pa rnams kyi yon tan mtha' yas te //
NK113(e)001:790: spangs pa gnyis kyi nyon shes sgrib pa bcom //
NK113(e)001:791: spyan dang mngon shes dbang bcu gzungs kyi sgo //
NK113(e)001:792: stobs bcu mi 'jigs bzhi dang so so rig /
NK113(e)001:793: ma 'dres bco brgyad rdzogs pa sangs rgyas te //
NK113(e)001:794: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan chos kyi sku //
NK113(e)001:795: sa bcu'i 'khor la longs spyod rdzogs par ston //
NK113(e)001:796: chos ni bsod nams lam dang mya ngan 'da' //
NK113(e)001:797: brjod bya'i don de de la'ang 'bras bu dang //
NK113(e)001:798: bya ba'i rang bzhin gnyis su gnas pa la //
NK113(e)001:799: bden gnyis zhes bya 'gog lam rnams gnyis yin //
NK113(e)001:800: brjod bya rjod byed la ltos lung rtogs chos //
NK113(e)001:801: lung ni gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis dang //
NK113(e)001:802: gnyen po'i sgo nas sde snod gsum du shar //
NK113(e)001:803: thabs kyi che ba rig 'dzin sde snod yin //
NK113(e)001:804: glegs bam yi ger gnas pa dam tshig rten //
NK113(e)001:805: rtogs pa'i chos ni dran pa nyer bzhag nas //
NK113(e)001:806: rim bzhin lam lnga'i yon tan mtha' dag dang //
NK113(e)001:807: 'phags pa'i spang rtogs ye shes snying po can //
NK113(e)001:808: bskyed dang rdzogs pa gzugs dang zad par dang //
NK113(e)001:809: slob lam bzhi dang mi slob lam gyi dngos //
NK113(e)001:810: rgyu yi sa bcu 'bras bu'i bcu gsum sogs //
NK113(e)001:811: rdo rje theg pa'i rigs dbye dpag tu med //
NK113(e)001:812: gang gi ye shes rgyud la brtan pa'o //
NK113(e)001:813: dge 'dun ngo bo rig grol gnyis ldan te //
NK113(e)001:814: nyan rang zhugs gnas skyes bu zung bzhi'am //
NK113(e)001:815: ya brgyad rgyal sras sar gnas mtha' dag pa'i //
NK113(e)001:816: rang sa'i yon tan brjod kyi mi lang yang //
NK113(e)001:817: lam dang skyob pa'i ngo bo dam pa'i chos //
NK113(e)001:818: chos ni ston pa las byung de bsgrub pa'i //
NK113(e)001:819: grogs sam bslab pa'i brten gnas dge 'dun phyir //
NK113(e)001:820: dkon mchog gsum zhes skyabs kyi yul du grub //
NK113(e)001:821: de la rgyu dang 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro yi //
NK113(e)001:822: dam bca' gnyis las dus gzhan 'grub 'dod rgyu //
NK113(e)001:823: da ltar grub pa rang sems 'bras bu'i skyabs //
NK113(e)001:824: rdo rje theg pa dag gi khyad chos yin //
NK113(e)001:825: rgyu yi yul ni dkon mchog rnam pa gsum //
NK113(e)001:826: sngags su de yi ngo bo bla mar 'dus //
NK113(e)001:827: nyi tshe mchog dang bla na med pa yi //
NK113(e)001:828: kun slong gsum las skyes bu chung ngu ni //
NK113(e)001:829: ngan 'gro la 'jigs mngon mtho'i bar du 'gro //
NK113(e)001:830: 'bring gnyis srid pas 'jigs nas thar pa gnyer //
NK113(e)001:831: gnas skabs ji srid 'tsho dang mthar thug ni //
NK113(e)001:832: nyan rang 'bras bu thob pa'i bar du 'gro //
NK113(e)001:833: chen po gzhan don spangs pa'i zhi bdes 'jigs //
NK113(e)001:834: 'khor ba dbugs 'byin chen po la bsgral phyir //
NK113(e)001:835: byang chub bar 'gro de yang rang gi sems //
NK113(e)001:836: bral thob bslu ba spangs pa 'bras bu'i skyabs //
NK113(e)001:837: lam dus sangs rgyas rnams ni sems can gyi //
NK113(e)001:838: khams la thugs rje dus las yol ba med //
NK113(e)001:839: ba spu'i khung bu gcig gi yon tan kyang //
NK113(e)001:840: mtha' dag brjod pas ma thug nam mkha' lding //
NK113(e)001:841: bya lam grub mtha' ma gtugs slar 'bab 'dra //
NK113(e)001:842: 'di ni 'khor ba'i 'khor lor yang nas yang //
NK113(e)001:843: brgyud de las ngan bsags pa'i mtshang can rnams //
NK113(e)001:844: 'khor los sgyur dang dbang phug la sogs pa //
NK113(e)001:845: skyabs gzhan gang gis bslu bar mthong nas ni //
NK113(e)001:846: 'jigs dang dad dang snying rje rnam gsum gyi //
NK113(e)001:847: gzhan don sems pa skyes bu chen po'i blos //
NK113(e)001:848: dkon mchog rjes su dran pas skyabs su 'gro //
NK113(e)001:849: ji ltar nam mkha' tshad bzung med pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:850: dkon mchog la brten dkar nag las 'bras kyi //
NK113(e)001:851: pha mtha' mi dpogs skyabs song gzugs gyur na //
NK113(e)001:852: nam mkha'i snod kyis bsten par nus ma yin //
NK113(e)001:853: nang pa'i khyur 'gro sdom pa mtha' dag rten //
NK113(e)001:854: sdig sgrib 'dzad cing gnod pa'i phyogs kyis spong //
NK113(e)001:855: ngan 'gro'i g.yang bsrung dkon mchog gsum mi 'bral //
NK113(e)001:856: phun sum tshogs pa mthong ba'i chos la 'ong //
NK113(e)001:857: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs gzugs kyi sku gnyis 'grub //
NK113(e)001:858: 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro bslu ba med pa ni //
NK113(e)001:859: rnam thar sgo gsum smon pa med pa'i dbyings //
NK113(e)001:860: gnas lugs rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa yin //
NK113(e)001:861: ye shes tshogs rdzogs dag pa gnyis ldan 'thob //
NK113(e)001:862: bslab bya rgyu 'bras gnyis las dang po ni //
NK113(e)001:863: mnga' ris bya dag'i slad du smos ci dgos //
NK113(e)001:864: srog gi phyir yang dkon mchog gtong ba min //
NK113(e)001:865: de yi ngo bo bla mar skyabs song nas //
NK113(e)001:866: dam pa bslu dang mi snyan sgrog pa spang //
NK113(e)001:867: de bzhin sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK113(e)001:868: skyabs su song nas rim bzhin bdag nyid ni //
NK113(e)001:869: 'khor bar 'khor ba'i lha la phyag mi 'tshal //
NK113(e)001:870: gzhan la mi 'tshe mu stegs can mi 'grogs //
NK113(e)001:871: dkon mchog rten la dad pas bsnyen bkur zhing //
NK113(e)001:872: nyin mtshan brjed pa spangs nas skyabs su 'gro //
NK113(e)001:873: 'bras bu'i bslab bya thub pa chos kyi sku //
NK113(e)001:874: bral thob spangs pa'i dbyings la byang chub pas //
NK113(e)001:875: skyob dang bskyab byar mi 'dzin tha snyad las //
NK113(e)001:876: 'das phyir gtong rgyu'ang btags pa bla dwags yin //
NK113(e)001:877: rgyu yi gtong mtshams skyabs 'gro mtshan nyid pa //
NK113(e)001:878: 'gro ba'i yul la log lta skyes pas gtong //
NK113(e)001:879: bslab bya nyams na dman par ltung ba'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:880: rma yi bag bzhin sgrims te bsrung bar bya //
NK113(e)001:881: las kyi ce spyang gdug pas skabs btsal rnams //
NK113(e)001:882: tshig don 'dzol ba'i yid gnyis snod ngan du //
NK113(e)001:883: bslu ba med pa'i nges shes bri ba'i rtags //
NK113(e)001:884: yi dwags la bsten tshe 'di nyid la nyams //
NK113(e)001:885: 'di na sa dang nam mkha' ri rab rnams //
NK113(e)001:886: yan man gnas 'gyur nyi zla thang lhung srid //
NK113(e)001:887: dkon chog gsum gyis bslu ba mi srid pa'i //
NK113(e)001:888: nges shes brtan pa kun tu don yod yin //
NK113(e)001:889: rmi lam na'ang dkon cog mthong ba dang //
NK113(e)001:890: bag yod dran zhing yon tan kun gyis 'byor //
NK113(e)001:891: tshe rabs dran zhing bar do bsgrod par sla //
NK113(e)001:892: lus can kun gyi dpung dang gnyen du 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:893: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:894: skyabs su 'gro ba'i tshoms te le'u drug pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:895: theg dman rdzing bur byang chub sems kyi khams //
NK113(e)001:896: rigs lam nyams pa'i nyan rang skyes bu'i sems //
NK113(e)001:897: stong nyid snying rje'i ded dpon mthus sad nas //
NK113(e)001:898: theg chen rgya mtsho kun mkhyen gling du 'gro //
NK113(e)001:899: sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa rnam pa lnga'o //
NK113(e)001:900: ngo bo lung du ma bstan lcags khams su //
NK113(e)001:901: rnam par nyams pa thabs shes gser 'gyur rtsis //
NK113(e)001:902: thebs pa'i mod la rin thang chen por byed //
NK113(e)001:903: gang phyir snying rje'i thabs dang stong nyid kyi //
NK113(e)001:904: shes rab zung du 'jug pa'i byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:905: sbyor ba tshad med bzhi pa'i sa mkhan gyis //
NK113(e)001:906: smon 'jug gnyis dang bslab bya slob las skye //
NK113(e)001:907: byams pa'i ngo bo gzhan bde 'dod pa yin //
NK113(e)001:908: sdug pa'i ma yis bu la ji bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:909: lus dang longs spyod dge ba kun spungs nas //
NK113(e)001:910: gzhan la phan 'dogs gnod pa bzod la bslab //
NK113(e)001:911: snying rje'i ngo bo gzhan gyi sdug bsngal la //
NK113(e)001:912: bzod mi phod pa'i sems stobs drag po dang //
NK113(e)001:913: 'gro drug mtha' dag sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyi //
NK113(e)001:914: mtha' la gcur mthong mchi ma slong ba yin //
NK113(e)001:915: dga' ba'i ngo bo gzhan dag phun tshogs la //
NK113(e)001:916: spro ba'i sems 'jug kun la legs smon bsgom //
NK113(e)001:917: rang rang mthu yis thob la dga' byed cing //
NK113(e)001:918: phyin chad de dang mi 'bral smon pa yin //
NK113(e)001:919: btang snyoms ngo bo byams sdang 'bral ba ste //
NK113(e)001:920: phyogs dang ris chad mnyam pa nyid brdal nas //
NK113(e)001:921: dgra dang gnyen dang bar ma'i 'du shes gsum //
NK113(e)001:922: phan 'dogs yul la mnyam par rab tu spyad //
NK113(e)001:923: rnam pa'i dmigs bcas dmigs med rtsi yis sbyar //
NK113(e)001:924: 'dod pa'i byams pa ser sna'i snying rje dang //
NK113(e)001:925: nga rgyal dga' ba gti mug btang snyoms dang //
NK113(e)001:926: thar pa'i lam min tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhi'o //
NK113(e)001:927: phyogs dang nye ba dmigs bcas rnam par spangs //
NK113(e)001:928: 'di ni zhi ba'i lam dang 'brel ba yi //
NK113(e)001:929: dmigs pa'i yul ni sems can thams cad kyang //
NK113(e)001:930: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid kyi //
NK113(e)001:931: rnam pa'i sgom tshul stobs su gyur pa las //
NK113(e)001:932: byang chub sems gnyis skye ba'i rgyur 'gro bas //
NK113(e)001:933: khyad chos ldan pa'i tshad med bzhi ru 'dod //
NK113(e)001:934: sgom tshul go rim can dang nges pa med //
NK113(e)001:935: dmigs pa'i yul gang skye bar sla na gtad //
NK113(e)001:936: 'on kyang byams bsgoms chags pa'i rten gyur na //
NK113(e)001:937: nye ring bral ba'i btang snyoms sgom par spo //
NK113(e)001:938: de nyid rmongs nas lung ma bstan gyur na //
NK113(e)001:939: snying rjer spos pas sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras 'gog /
NK113(e)001:940: snying rje stobs zhan ris su chad pa na //
NK113(e)001:941: dga' bar spos bas dman sems skye ba 'gog /
NK113(e)001:942: dga' bas sems rgod spros pa'i yul gyur na //
NK113(e)001:943: byams sogs mtha' dbus barjesa nas spel mar bsgom //
NK113(e)001:944: de ltar bsgoms pas rnam smin mngon par mtho //
NK113(e)001:945: 'dod par lha mi'i lus dang nges legs gnyis //
NK113(e)001:946: rgyu mthun byed pa de 'dra myong bas ni //
NK113(e)001:947: mi mthun phyogs dang bral zhing bde ba 'thob //
NK113(e)001:948: dbang gis yid 'ong bde dag'i yul la spyod //
NK113(e)001:949: byed pa bzhi po stobs su gyur pa yi //
NK113(e)001:950: don gnyis 'byor pa'i yon tan 'thob 'gyur te //
NK113(e)001:951: byams pa 'byongs pas 'gro la bu ltar brtse //
NK113(e)001:952: zhe sdang med cing gzhan gyi yid du 'ong //
NK113(e)001:953: byams pa'i ngo bo stong la rang bzhin med //
NK113(e)001:954: me long ye shes longs spyod rdzogs pa 'thob //
NK113(e)001:955: snying rje 'byongs pas gzhan gyi sdug bsngal kyang //
NK113(e)001:956: bdag gi khur 'gro 'tshe ba bral ba'i sems //
NK113(e)001:957: 'dod chags dang bral stong nyid snying rjer 'brel //
NK113(e)001:958: sor rtog ye shes chos kyi sku ru 'grub //
NK113(e)001:959: dga' ba 'byongs pas phrag dog rtsa ba chod //
NK113(e)001:960: 'byor ba brtan cing zhi bde rgyun mi 'chad //
NK113(e)001:961: bsam tan dga' ba dmigs pa med pa dang //
NK113(e)001:962: bya grub ye shes sprul pa'i sku mchog 'thob //
NK113(e)001:963: btang snyoms 'byongs pas bdag gzhan dgra gnyen mnyam //
NK113(e)001:964: nga rgyal med cing za bzhi'i rtogs pa skye //
NK113(e)001:965: rmongs pa med cing chos dbyings ye shes dang //
NK113(e)001:966: ngo bo nyid sku mngon du 'thob par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:967: de lta'i tshad med bzhi yi yon tan ni //
NK113(e)001:968: rgyu 'bras shin tu mtha' yas bslu ba med //
NK113(e)001:969: lam ngan gzhan gyi grub mtha' srid pa'i rgyu //
NK113(e)001:970: stong nyid snying rjer 'gal la mi bsten par //
NK113(e)001:971: thar pa dri med rgyal sras dam pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:972: rnyog pa zhi ba'i dge la goms 'tshal lo //
NK113(e)001:973: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:974: tshad med bzhi'i tshoms te le'u bdun pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:975: rnyed pa gang gi don la yon gyi mchog /
NK113(e)001:976: tshad med rnam bzhis thob pa'i byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:977: smon 'jug shing rta'i sgyu thabs la drangs pas //
NK113(e)001:978: zhi bde'i lta ba ngan pa nyams par byed //
NK113(e)001:979: sdig sdug 'khor ba'i brtson rar bcings rnams kyang //
NK113(e)001:980: byang chub sems bskyed mod la rgyal sras kyi //
NK113(e)001:981: ming gi cod pan 'thob la rab dga' nas //
NK113(e)001:982: 'jig rten lha mir bcas kyang bsti stang byed //
NK113(e)001:983: las nyon mun nag 'khrigs pa'i sprin par nas //
NK113(e)001:984: gtum po'i glog 'od 'khrug lta'i dge ba la //
NK113(e)001:985: skabs 'gar goms pa'i bsod nams tsam po ba //
NK113(e)001:986: chu shing bzhin du 'bras bus rtsa ba smad //
NK113(e)001:987: sa gzhi bzang pos bsten pa'i zhing sa la //
NK113(e)001:988: dge ba'i lo tog phun sum tshogs pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:989: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing srid pa na //
NK113(e)001:990: 'bras bu mang zhing zhi ba'i bar du 'phel //
NK113(e)001:991: las nyon 'du byed sdug bsngal kun gyi snod //
NK113(e)001:992: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho rnam rtog rba rlabs can //
NK113(e)001:993: sems can rnams kyi khyim ltar rab bzung las //
NK113(e)001:994: gdon pa'i snying stobs chen po sems bskyed yin //
NK113(e)001:995: gang la rang don sems pa yod ma yin //
NK113(e)001:996: bkres pa zas dang skom pa chur gdung bzhin //
NK113(e)001:997: sems can 'ba' zhig don du rnam mkhyen gyi //
NK113(e)001:998: go 'phang gnyer la byang chub sems zhes grags //
NK113(e)001:999: de'ang 'bras bur dam 'cha' smon pa'i sems //
NK113(e)001:1000: bslab bya bdag gzhan mnyam dang barje ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1001: bdag pas gzhan gces gsum du bzhag pa'ang //
NK113(e)001:1002: bslab pa'i mdor bsdus yin gyi de'i ngo bo //
NK113(e)001:1003: byams sogs tshad med bzhi la yang dag gnas //
NK113(e)001:1004: rgyu la dam 'cha' 'jug pa'i sems yin te //
NK113(e)001:1005: de yi bslab bya pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK113(e)001:1006: spyod yul yongs su dag pa rnams la bsten //
NK113(e)001:1007: dbye ba'i sgo nas skye 'phags sems bskyed gnyis //
NK113(e)001:1008: bslab pa gsum la ltos pa'i sems bskyed gsum //
NK113(e)001:1009: khyad par tshogs sbyor lam na mos pas spyod //
NK113(e)001:1010: dang po'i sa nas bdun par lhag bsam dag /
NK113(e)001:1011: dag sa gsum na rnam par smin pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1012: sangs rgyas sa la sgrib pa spangs te bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1013: de bzhin lam lnga'i rjes 'gro sems bskyed lnga //
NK113(e)001:1014: pha rol phyin pa drug ltos de snyed grangs //
NK113(e)001:1015: sa mtshams dbye ba nyi shu rtsa gnyis so //
NK113(e)001:1016: bsam pas smon dang 'jug pas khyab la 'du //
NK113(e)001:1017: gang zhig rang nyid legs pa don gnyer nas //
NK113(e)001:1018: rtag tu gcod pa med pa'i sgo 'phar nang //
NK113(e)001:1019: slong ba'i yid la 'khrugs pa mi ster ba //
NK113(e)001:1020: de la gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin zhes //
NK113(e)001:1021: basngagasa par 'os na mtha' dag sems can don //
NK113(e)001:1022: phan pa'i smon sems thang gcig skyes pas kyang //
NK113(e)001:1023: ngan song sgo gcod lha mi'i gnas rigs su //
NK113(e)001:1024: bde ba bsten pa'i yon tan zad mi shes //
NK113(e)001:1025: khyad par 'jug pa'i yon tan mtha' yas te //
NK113(e)001:1026: dngos su sbyor bas khyab pa'i cho ga la /
NK113(e)001:1027: gang nas bzung ste ldog pa med pa'i sems //
NK113(e)001:1028: 'gro sgrol dam bcar shin tu yid brtan pa //
NK113(e)001:1029: de nas bzung ste bag med gnyid log kyang //
NK113(e)001:1030: bsod nams rgyun chags nyid du 'brel 'gyur ba //
NK113(e)001:1031: spyod pa'i sa las 'thad pa dang bcas bshad //
NK113(e)001:1032: bskal pa mang po'i tshogs kyang 'dums par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1033: phyugs dang glang po shing rta nyi zla sogs //
NK113(e)001:1034: bgrod pa'i brtul zhugs myur bul mtha' yas ltar //
NK113(e)001:1035: blo stobs chen po'i thabs brtson shes rab kyis //
NK113(e)001:1036: grangs med gsum gyi dam bzhag 'jig pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1037: ji ltar sa bon sa la lhung ba bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1038: sems mchog bskyed pa mi gtso skyes pa gtso //
NK113(e)001:1039: stobs gsum las ni byang chub sems skye bas //
NK113(e)001:1040: snying rje che dang tshogs bsags skyabs su 'gro //
NK113(e)001:1041: bsam dang sbyor ba rgyu yi stobs su bshad //
NK113(e)001:1042: rten gyi gang zag rnam pa gnyis bstan te //
NK113(e)001:1043: so thar rigs bdun gang rung sdom ldan nam //
NK113(e)001:1044: dkon mchog t+aa lar bsam pa'i rten gtso ba'i //
NK113(e)001:1045: rjes phyoogs dbu ma'i lam srol 'jug pa yangs //
NK113(e)001:1046: tshogs bsags pa ni lhag par skye ba'i thabs //
NK113(e)001:1047: rgyu ni kun kyang bde gshegs snying po can //
NK113(e)001:1048: rkyen ni dge ba'i bshegs la rab bsten pas //
NK113(e)001:1049: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i bla ma mchog /
NK113(e)001:1050: byang chub sems kyi thugs rgyud gang ba des //
NK113(e)001:1051: thog mtha' bar du dge ba'i chos rnams dang //
NK113(e)001:1052: rgyan dang sdong po bkod las legs gsungs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1053: byang chub sems kyi yon tan dpag yas brjod //
NK113(e)001:1054: skyang nul mdzes sdug ngom pa'i gnas khang yang //
NK113(e)001:1055: gur gum spos chus bran bcas gdong bkru zhing //
NK113(e)001:1056: dkon mchog 'ba' zhig yid la sems pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1057: mchod tshogs phru ma 'debs la dga' zhing dgos //
NK113(e)001:1058: dam tshig gzugs brnyan mtha' dag der bos nas //
NK113(e)001:1059: ye shes sems dpa' dgug gzhug cho ga ni //
NK113(e)001:1060: mdza' gcugs dam bca' dran pa las myur bas //
NK113(e)001:1061: rgyal rnams zhing khams gzhan du gzigs pa yol //
NK113(e)001:1062: gang zhig lus pa med pa'i sems can gyi //
NK113(e)001:1063: mgon dang dpung gnyen gyur kyang bdud sde'i dgra //
NK113(e)001:1064: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen cing gzigs pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1065: bcom ldan bdag gi sdum par mchis su gsol //
NK113(e)001:1066: las kyis sprul pa ma yin 'byon pa'i shul //
NK113(e)001:1067: khrus kyi khang bu brtsegs pa dri bsung can //
NK113(e)001:1068: shel dang nor bu'i sa gzhi ka bar ldan //
NK113(e)001:1069: g.yu dmar mu tig bla bre dpyangs pa der //
NK113(e)001:1070: bde gshegs rigs kyi bu mchog bcas pa la //
NK113(e)001:1071: spos chus gang ba'i nor bu'i bum pa nas //
NK113(e)001:1072: khrus kyi rim gro bgyid pa'i smin legs ma //
NK113(e)001:1073: glu gar rol mo'i 'gyur ba 'gran la brtson //
NK113(e)001:1074: nye reg cho ga mkhas pa'i ri dwags mig /
NK113(e)001:1075: dril phyis bku mnye'i sri zhus g.yeng ba'ang //
NK113(e)001:1076: kha dog gcig tu mi gnas dbang po'i mtshon //
NK113(e)001:1077: thags su btags pa med pa'i lha rdzas nyo //
NK113(e)001:1078: dpag bsam ljon pas btsod pa'i pany+tsa li //
NK113(e)001:1079: lcid kyis non spangs srab 'dzam yang ba'i gos //
NK113(e)001:1080: dri dang spos chus bgos shing byugs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1081: rin thang brjod la khrel ba'i rin chen rgyan /
NK113(e)001:1082: gdu bu dpung rgyan snyan cha cod pan sogs //
NK113(e)001:1083: 'dod pa'i yon tan spangs pa'i thub dbang kyang //
NK113(e)001:1084: bkren ldan bsod nams slad du bdag gir bzhes //
NK113(e)001:1085: 'jig rten dbang phyug la sogs nye ba'i sras //
NK113(e)001:1086: ngan song kun 'dren la sogs bskal bzang gi //
NK113(e)001:1087: sems dpa' bcu drug dang ni khyim pa'i tshul //
NK113(e)001:1088: chos 'phags rtag tu ngu dang li tsa b+ai //
NK113(e)001:1089: dri ma med par grags la'ang dbul bar bgyi //
NK113(e)001:1090: stong gsum cig car khyab pa'i dri'i bzhon par //
NK113(e)001:1091: 'khyud pa'i tsan+dana spos kyi bsung zhim dris //
NK113(e)001:1092: bsod nams bye ba'i 'byung gnas mtshan dpe'i byad //
NK113(e)001:1093: gser sbyangs brtan pa 'phrog la byug par bgyi //
NK113(e)001:1094: btang snyoms yangs pa'i shel gyi sa gzhi la //
NK113(e)001:1095: byams pa'i pad+mo ge sar stong brdal bar //
NK113(e)001:1096: snying rje'i nyi zla bkrag tu 'tsher ba bstar //
NK113(e)001:1097: dga' chen bcom ldan 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NK113(e)001:1098: bab col goms pa min pa'i lus btud kyi //
NK113(e)001:1099: snying gar gus bcas mngon rtogs ngom pa la //
NK113(e)001:1100: me tog dog pas rab bzung snyim pa'i snod //
NK113(e)001:1101: ga bu chung gi brtul zhugs 'dzin pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1102: rig dang zhabs su ldan sogs bde gshegs kyi //
NK113(e)001:1103: yon tan mtha' dag gnas kyis bskal ba bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1104: dad pa'i skyed mos tshal du 'ongs pa'i mod //
NK113(e)001:1105: skyo ba min pa'i ba spu gcig tu zing //
NK113(e)001:1106: zla gzhon khrus la 'jug pa'i rdzing bu'i nang //
NK113(e)001:1107: rma bya'i bu mo 'jo sgeg rol pa lta'i //
NK113(e)001:1108: lang tsho'i grangs snyed rdul gyi rnam grangs dang //
NK113(e)001:1109: shin tu 'khrul pa bskyed byed phyag gis brel //
NK113(e)001:1110: gtong ba'i yan lag rdzogs pa'i dngos 'byor dang /
NK113(e)001:1111: des kyang mtshon par dpe med yid kyis sprul //
NK113(e)001:1112: bla na mchis pa ma yin mchod pa'i sprin //
NK113(e)001:1113: kun tu bzang po'i yon la phrag dog bgyid //
NK113(e)001:1114: mu bcor smra ba'i las dang bag chags sdig /
NK113(e)001:1115: dge la 'jigs nas gzhan du bros pa'i gzugs //
NK113(e)001:1116: srid pa'i mun nag stug por 'chab pa kun //
NK113(e)001:1117: stobs bzhi'i nyin byed 'bar bas sbyang zhing bshags //
NK113(e)001:1118: sbyor ba gang gis bdag nyid ma 'khrugs bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1119: bsam pa'i khyad par gcig gis gzhan dag pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1120: rnam dkar yud la 'phrog pa'i chom rkun gyi //
NK113(e)001:1121: brtul zhugs rjes su yi rang kho nas byas //
NK113(e)001:1122: thar med 'khor ba'i spyod pa ma dul zhing //
NK113(e)001:1123: rnam par sra mkhregs tha ba gang gis kyang //
NK113(e)001:1124: gdul thabs brtan pa bral la chos 'khor gyi //
NK113(e)001:1125: rtsibs rnon mu khyud 'dzin de bskor bar bskul //
NK113(e)001:1126: rgyal dang de sras rnams kyis spangs gyur pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1127: 'gro 'dis sdug bsngal gnas skabs bsten mthong nas //
NK113(e)001:1128: mya ngan 'da' ba min pa'i gdan khri la //
NK113(e)001:1129: dngos po kun gyi rin thang gcig tu spungs //
NK113(e)001:1130: bdag tu blta bas 'dar ba'i rnam dkar yang //
NK113(e)001:1131: srid par lan gcig mtho ba'i cho nge ste //
NK113(e)001:1132: byang chub bsngo ba'i gser 'gyur rtsis thebs pa //
NK113(e)001:1133: 'di ni ston pa gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK113(e)001:1134: chog shes bdud rtsi'i btung bas ma ngoms na //
NK113(e)001:1135: skyes bu'i yid la ma bzung mchod sprin yang //
NK113(e)001:1136: tshig gi pha mthar 'khyams la skrag gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:1137: bdag lus stan du dbul la'ang do gal bgyid //
NK113(e)001:1138: dkon mchog gsum gyi 'bangs su dam bcas pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1139: grib bsil so ka'i me tog 'jo sgeg can //
NK113(e)001:1140: rnam kun 'khrugs pa'i gshin rje'i mdun sar yang //
NK113(e)001:1141: khro gnyer 'jig pa'i rin thang zad mi shes //
NK113(e)001:1142: des ni gti mug mthus non sdig ldan bdag /
NK113(e)001:1143: byi dor shin tu bsten pa'i dwangs shel ltar //
NK113(e)001:1144: bsod nams rnyog pa dwangs pa'i sems kyi nang //
NK113(e)001:1145: sems bskyed cho gas thob pa'i gzugs brnyan dngos //
NK113(e)001:1146: nyes pa brgya phrag g.yang sar ltung ba yi //
NK113(e)001:1147: rims kyis shin tu btab pa'i nad pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:1148: gso dpyad phal pa'i mdun sar dbugs mi phyin //
NK113(e)001:1149: sman pa mchog la skyabs su lhag par dang //
NK113(e)001:1150: mos pa gang gi slad du 'dir gshegs nas //
NK113(e)001:1151: sems can khams la dgongs pa'i ston mchog ni //
NK113(e)001:1152: theg pa chen po'i skyes bu 'ba' zhig pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1153: tshogs kyi dbus na lham mer mdzes pa la //
NK113(e)001:1154: skyabs su 'gro ba gsum gyis gzhi bcas la //
NK113(e)001:1155: dgongs su gsol ba gsum gyis sad byas nas //
NK113(e)001:1156: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i thugs bskyed dang //
NK113(e)001:1157: bslab pa'i brtul zhugs mtha' dag blang ba yin //
NK113(e)001:1158: nyon sgrib zug rngu'i dum bu bcad gyur kyang //
NK113(e)001:1159: shes sgrib yul gyi ro la gcags pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1160: nyan rang dgra bcom ma bsgral ba las bsgral //
NK113(e)001:1161: gnyis ka'i 'ching bas kun nas dkris pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1162: tshangs pa la sogs so so skye bo nas //
NK113(e)001:1163: slob pa 'phags pa'i bar la gnas pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1164: sems can ma grol ba rnams dgrol ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1165: shin tu sdug bsngal drag po'i shugs ring las //
NK113(e)001:1166: dbugs 'byin thob pa med pa'i ngan song gsum //
NK113(e)001:1167: dbugs 'byin chen po'i gnas la sbyar ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1168: mdor na rten cing 'brel 'byung bcu gnyis kyi //
NK113(e)001:1169: 'khor lo'i rgyar chud sems can yod do cog /
NK113(e)001:1170: mi gnas ye shes mya ngan 'das pa'i grong //
NK113(e)001:1171: dgod byed cho gas bzung ba'i brjod pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1172: sngon byon drang srong rnams kyi lugs la brten //
NK113(e)001:1173: rtag tu nyid dang mtshan mo lan gsum du //
NK113(e)001:1174: byang chub sems gnyis bskyed la nan tan bya //
NK113(e)001:1175: 'dun pa'i rtse la chos rnams rkyen chags pas //
NK113(e)001:1176: brjod pa dang pos smon dang gnyis pas 'jug /
NK113(e)001:1177: gsum kas gnyi ga brtan par thob pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1178: rgya mtsho sprin gyi bzhed pa bla na med //
NK113(e)001:1179: sngon chad gzhan gyi don la lta ci smos //
NK113(e)001:1180: rang don nyid du rmi ba'ang ma myong ba'i //
NK113(e)001:1181: rin chen sems kyi khyad par gsang ba 'dis //
NK113(e)001:1182: bdag gi srid pa rin thang med pa byas //
NK113(e)001:1183: rigs las nyams pa gang zhig cho rigs kyi //
NK113(e)001:1184: lhag par btsun pa'i gnas thob ji bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:1185: rgyal ba kun gyi sras su deng gyur pas //
NK113(e)001:1186: byang chub sems dpa'i ming gi cod pan thob //
NK113(e)001:1187: srid gsum bdag po byas dang de nyid kyis //
NK113(e)001:1188: rmongs pa'i bla dwags dpyangs la'ang dga' byed na //
NK113(e)001:1189: byang chub sems dpa'i gnas thob de ring tsam //
NK113(e)001:1190: dga' ba'i 'khri shing slong la lha yang phyogs //
NK113(e)001:1191: 'chi bdag 'joms pa'i bdud rtsi mi zad gter //
NK113(e)001:1192: dbul ba sel ba'i nor dang nad zhi'i sman //
NK113(e)001:1193: srid lam dub pa'i mgron po'i nga la stegs phyir //
NK113(e)001:1194: bdag ni deng nas 'gro ba'i nyer 'tshor gyur //
NK113(e)001:1195: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las //
NK113(e)001:1196: byang chub kyi sems yongs su bzung ba'i tshoms te le'u brgyad pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:1197: sngon chad legs par ma brtags bab bcol gyi //
NK113(e)001:1198: dam bca' gtong la'ang yid gnyis gnas mchi na //
NK113(e)001:1199: rgyal dang de sras rnams kyi shes rab mthus //
NK113(e)001:1200: gdon mi za bar brtags pa'i blang dor gnas //
NK113(e)001:1201: btang na bdag gi sems can kun bslus pas //
NK113(e)001:1202: mu mtha' med pa'i ngan 'gror 'khyams par 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1203: de phyir sems can gcig gi bde ba'ang //
NK113(e)001:1204: bshig nas bdag nyid nyams pa'i las mi bgyid //
NK113(e)001:1205: ltung dang byang chub sems stobs gnyis kar ldan //
NK113(e)001:1206: 'khor bar res kyi 'gre byed gang yin pa //
NK113(e)001:1207: sa thob pa la yun ring 'thogs 'gyur na //
NK113(e)001:1208: bslab bya gtong ba'i skyes bu smyon pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1209: gang zhig gnod pa'i rgyu 'bras chung ngu la'ang //
NK113(e)001:1210: khros pa'i nga rgyal shin tu bdo ba rnams //
NK113(e)001:1211: mda' mdung mtshon gyi chad pa bzod byas nas //
NK113(e)001:1212: don ma grub par phyir phyogs mi byed na //
NK113(e)001:1213: rnam pa kun tu dag la dgrar gyur pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1214: nyon mongs stobs chen 'di dang g.yul sprad nas //
NK113(e)001:1215: 'khon du bzung ba'i cho ga ma zhig bar //
NK113(e)001:1216: bslab pa bsrung ba'i brtul zhugs su zhig gtong //
NK113(e)001:1217: 'di na nyon mongs btson rar bsdams pa yis //
NK113(e)001:1218: bdag gi tshod kyang rig par mi 'gyur na //
NK113(e)001:1219: mtha' dag 'gro ba de las dbugs 'byin zhing /
NK113(e)001:1220: sgrol ba'i brtan pa mi nyams ga la zhig /
NK113(e)001:1221: bag yod shes bzhin ldan pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK113(e)001:1222: byang chub sems kyi myu gu bskyed sla bas //
NK113(e)001:1223: mi nyams bzung zhing dri ma sbyong ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1224: spel ba'i thabs la nan tan bgyid 'tshal lo //
NK113(e)001:1225: de la ltung ba'i rab dbye nyi shu ni //
NK113(e)001:1226: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog la sogs rgyal po'i lnga //
NK113(e)001:1227: grong dang grong rdal 'joms sogs blon po'i lnga //
NK113(e)001:1228: blo ma sbyangs la stong nyid ston pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:1229: phal pa'i brgyad dang smon 'jug gtong rnams spang //
NK113(e)001:1230: mdor na rmi lam sdig pa mthong na yang //
NK113(e)001:1231: de ma thag tu phung po gsum pas bshags //
NK113(e)001:1232: rten gzhi smon sems shor dang 'gal zla byung //
NK113(e)001:1233: spong rkyen bslab pa phul ba gsum dag las //
NK113(e)001:1234: thun tshod las nyams shor na 'gyod sems kyis //
NK113(e)001:1235: skya rengs mdun du nam mkha'i snying po la //
NK113(e)001:1236: bos nas yan lag bdun pas ltung ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1237: bdag bde gzhan la yang dag spo ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1238: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal bdag gi khur bzod pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1239: gtong len snying stobs rmad byung 'du byed cing //
NK113(e)001:1240: byang chub bar du mi 'bral phyi phyir smon //
NK113(e)001:1241: smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med bzhi po'ang //
NK113(e)001:1242: byas pa drin du gzo las byams pa skye //
NK113(e)001:1243: byams las snying rje de las byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:1244: skye ba tshad ma'i lung gis yang dag 'grub //
NK113(e)001:1245: btsas ma thag pa'i skyes bu bzhin ngan de //
NK113(e)001:1246: ma yis pang pas khrus khang ltar byas nas //
NK113(e)001:1247: mi gtsang mtha' dag lag pas nye reg byas //
NK113(e)001:1248: nu zhos bsnyen bkur lus kyi reg byas g.yogs //
NK113(e)001:1249: bu chung na las bdag nyid 'chi bar 'dams //
NK113(e)001:1250: sdig sdug gtam ngan mtha' dag sran nus pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1251: drin dang rim gro khyad du gsod byed na //
NK113(e)001:1252: de las cho ga 'khrugs pa su zhig yod //
NK113(e)001:1253: sa 'di rir bcas bdag gi khur ma yin //
NK113(e)001:1254: byas pa mi gzo'i khur chen dug ldan gyi //
NK113(e)001:1255: bza' ba khong du chud pa'i skye bo bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1256: de phyir pha mtha' yas pa'i sems can kun //
NK113(e)001:1257: ma ru gyur nas phan btags dam pa'i drin //
NK113(e)001:1258: dran pas byams sogs bzhi po gong 'phel zhing //
NK113(e)001:1259: byas pa shes dang drin du gzo ba yi //
NK113(e)001:1260: skyes bu gang la 'phags pa'i nor gyis bsnyen //
NK113(e)001:1261: smon sems ston ka'i zla ba gsar pa la //
NK113(e)001:1262: sgra gcan gdong bas thu ba'i mi mthun phyogs //
NK113(e)001:1263: nag po'i chos bzhi ring du bskrad par bya //
NK113(e)001:1264: mchod 'os bslu dang gzhan gyis bsod nams la //
NK113(e)001:1265: the tshom bskyed nas 'gyod pa'i gnas la sbyar //
NK113(e)001:1266: dam pa rnams la bskur zhing mi snyan sgrog /
NK113(e)001:1267: g.yo dang sgyus spyod gzhan dag mgo bo bskor //
NK113(e)001:1268: chos bzhi gang rung nyams myong smon sems shor //
NK113(e)001:1269: 'gyod dang gnyen pos ma slebs thun tshod 'das //
