NK113(e)001:1270: de yi mod la sems bskyed 'chor ba yin //
NK113(e)001:1271: gnyen por che ba dkar po'i chos bzhi ni //
NK113(e)001:1272: srog la babs kyang bsam bzhin rdzun mi smra //
NK113(e)001:1273: rgyal sras rnams la ston par gus shing basngagasa //
NK113(e)001:1274: g.yo sgyu med pas sems can thams cad gnyer //
NK113(e)001:1275: mtha' dag byang chub lam la dkri ba'o //
NK113(e)001:1276: brtan bya'i sgo nas bsrung ba'i 'du shes bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1277: dge ba'i bshes la sangs rgyas 'du shes dang //
NK113(e)001:1278: des bstan chos la lam gyi 'du shes dang //
NK113(e)001:1279: de sgrub rnams la grogs kyi 'du shes dang //
NK113(e)001:1280: sems can kun la bu gcig 'du shes te //
NK113(e)001:1281: 'di dag smon pa'i bslab bya yang dag go //
NK113(e)001:1282: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug las //
NK113(e)001:1283: dang po lnga ni bsod nams dam pa'i tshogs //
NK113(e)001:1284: phyi ma gcig ni ye shes tshogs chen te //
NK113(e)001:1285: gnyis la ma bsten sangs rgyas yod ma yin //
NK113(e)001:1286: thabs stobs smon lam ye shes bsnan pas bcu //
NK113(e)001:1287: blo stobs mthu yis sgrub byed rgyal sras gsum //
NK113(e)001:1288: rang don sngon byas 'gro ba sgrol 'dod pa //
NK113(e)001:1289: rgyal po lta bu'i 'dod chen sems bskyed dang //
NK113(e)001:1290: rang dang 'gro ba stabs gcig sgrol 'dod pa //
NK113(e)001:1291: gru pa lta bu ye shes dam pa'i sems //
NK113(e)001:1292: 'gro ba sngon bsgral rjes la zhi 'dod pa //
NK113(e)001:1293: skyong byed lta bu'i dpe med sems bskyed de //
NK113(e)001:1294: rtul pos grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum dang //
NK113(e)001:1295: 'bring pos bdun dang rnon pos gsum na grol //
NK113(e)001:1296: sbyin pa'i ngo bo chags pa med pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1297: dbye na chos dang zang zing mi 'jigs gsum //
NK113(e)001:1298: zang zing la'ang rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK113(e)001:1299: gtong dang gtong ba che dang shin tu gtong //
NK113(e)001:1300: gtong ba zhes bya zas gos shing rta dang //
NK113(e)001:1301: glang po yul khams gzhan la byin pa'o //
NK113(e)001:1302: gtong ba chen po bu dang bu mo dang //
NK113(e)001:1303: khyim thab gtong yin shin tu gtong ba ni //
NK113(e)001:1304: bya daka'i gnas te mgo dang yan lag gtang //
NK113(e)001:1305: 'di na thog mar goms su 'jug pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:1306: ser snas bsdams pa'i skyes bu'i lag pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1307: gcig nas cig shos sbyin par bsam pa'i sems //
NK113(e)001:1308: yang yang spos pas tshod ma la sogs la //
NK113(e)001:1309: brkam chags 'jig pa stobs su gyur la bslab //
NK113(e)001:1310: mi 'jigs sbyin pa gzhan gyi srog bsrung dang //
NK113(e)001:1311: 'jigs pa'i yul bsgral dbugs 'byin gnas la dgod //
NK113(e)001:1312: mi nus bzhin du bab col cho ga yis //
NK113(e)001:1313: rnam par sbyar ba'i sbyin pa'ang smad pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1314: snying rje'i bsam pa shin tu ma dag par //
NK113(e)001:1315: lus dang srog gtong bslab btus nyin las bkag /
NK113(e)001:1316: kha na ma thos bskrun pa'i sbyin pa yang //
NK113(e)001:1317: gnas min smad pa'i gnas te bdog pa la //
NK113(e)001:1318: zhen pa btang ba sbyin pa'i tshad du bzhed //
NK113(e)001:1319: chos kyi sbyin pa rnam pa gsum las dngos //
NK113(e)001:1320: mos pas spyod la ji bzhin 'doms par dka' //
NK113(e)001:1321: rang gi nyon mongs bsal ba'i cho ga dang //
NK113(e)001:1322: byams dang snying rjes gsung rab bklags pa yis //
NK113(e)001:1323: dkar po'i phyogs kyi rgyud gro la smon lam gdab //
NK113(e)001:1324: rang rgyud grol nas 'gro ba'i skal ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1325: rang bzhin 'tshams pas gzhan don gtso bor bya //
NK113(e)001:1326: tshul khrims ngo bo mi mthun sdom pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1327: dbye na nyes spyod sdom dang dge chos sdud //
NK113(e)001:1328: sems can don byed rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NK113(e)001:1329: sgo gsum mi dge sdom pa nyes spyod sdom //
NK113(e)001:1330: pha rol phyin pa drug ldan dge chos sdud //
NK113(e)001:1331: gzhan la phan gdags sems can don byed yin //
NK113(e)001:1332: nang gses so so thar las byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:1333: khyad par bzhi yi sgo nas 'phags pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1334: so thar gzhan gnod gzhi bcas ldog pa tsam //
NK113(e)001:1335: byang sems de yi steng du phan 'dogs bsnon //
NK113(e)001:1336: sa thar spangs pa bdun bsdus lus ngag gtso //
NK113(e)001:1337: byang sems spangs pa bcu ka gtso bor byed //
NK113(e)001:1338: khyad par bslab pa'i gnas ni so thar skabs //
NK113(e)001:1339: gzhan gyi don du bcas pa mi 'bral la //
NK113(e)001:1340: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan gyi don 'gyur na //
NK113(e)001:1341: lus ngag gnyis kyi mi dge rnam pa bdun //
NK113(e)001:1342: gzhan don 'gyur dang 'gyur bar shes pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1343: rang gi dge tshogs mi sgrib 'phel ba yi //
NK113(e)001:1344: gnas skabs gsum brtags gnang ba'i skabs yod de //
NK113(e)001:1345: sems stobs chen pos mi nag mdung thung can //
NK113(e)001:1346: bram ze'i khye'u skar ma dper mtshon nas //
NK113(e)001:1347: rnam pa'i nyes pa'ang don la dge ba yin //
NK113(e)001:1348: rgyu 'bras mthu can bsam pas byas pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:1349: yid kyi gsum la gnang ba'i skabs med do //
NK113(e)001:1350: de lta na'ang rgyal sras sdom pa la //
NK113(e)001:1351: rang don zhi bde gnyer dang bya dka' spang //
NK113(e)001:1352: gzhan phyir phan pa mi bsgrub gang dad gang //
NK113(e)001:1353: ltung ba'i rgyu ru gcig par gsungs pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1354: dang po'i las can byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK113(e)001:1355: blo ni gong nas gong du spyod gtso bas //
NK113(e)001:1356: thog mar sdom pa'i tshul khrims ma dag par //
NK113(e)001:1357: gzhan gnyis gtso bor gnyer na bar chad mang //
NK113(e)001:1358: rab tu byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' ni //
NK113(e)001:1359: khyad par can du mdo sde rgyan las bshad //
NK113(e)001:1360: byang chub sems dpa' rang sa'i sdom pa la //
NK113(e)001:1361: so thar mtshan nyid cho gas gsal ba med //
NK113(e)001:1362: sbyangs pa sngon song sems stobs chen po ni //
NK113(e)001:1363: bsam pa'i rten gtso in+d+ra b+h+au ti bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1364: gang zhig khyim pa'i phyogs la brten pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:1365: dge bsnyen dang ni bsnyen gnas sdom pa'i steng //
NK113(e)001:1366: smon 'jug byang chub sems gnyis rtag tu bsrung //
NK113(e)001:1367: rab tu byung rnams dge slong dge tshul dang //
NK113(e)001:1368: dge slong ma yi sdom pa gang ldan steng //
NK113(e)001:1369: smon 'jug gnyis bsrung rang sa'i tshul khrims yin //
NK113(e)001:1370: dbye na dge bsnyen rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK113(e)001:1371: sna gcig bsrung ba srog gcod lta bu spang //
NK113(e)001:1372: de steng ma byin len spong phyogs gcig ldan //
NK113(e)001:1373: de steng rdzun smra spang ba phal cher bsrung //
NK113(e)001:1374: de steng 'dod log cha dang bcas spangs na //
NK113(e)001:1375: yongs rdzogs bsrung ba'i dge bsnyen dag tu 'dod //
NK113(e)001:1376: rtsa bzhi chang dang lnga ka spang ba la /
NK113(e)001:1377: tshangs par spyod pa'i dge bsnyen zhes su grags //
NK113(e)001:1378: rab tu byung ba'i bslab pa'i gnas bcu las //
NK113(e)001:1379: gser dngul len pa bu smad gso phyir gnang //
NK113(e)001:1380: gar phreng gnyis po mtshang chung gcig tu bgrang //
NK113(e)001:1381: yan lag brgyad pa'i khrims zhes grags pa gang //
NK113(e)001:1382: bsrung mtshams med par rtag tu bsrung ba de //
NK113(e)001:1383: tsan+d+ra go mi lta bu'i dge bsnyen yin //
NK113(e)001:1384: dge tshul srog gcod gzhan gyi nor 'phrog dang //
NK113(e)001:1385: mi tshangs spyod rdzun bcos pa'i chang la sogs //
NK113(e)001:1386: gar sogs phreng sogs mal chen mtho ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1387: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul len pa spong //
NK113(e)001:1388: bslab pa'i gnas bcu 'dzin pa khyad par yin //
NK113(e)001:1389: dge slob ma ni de steng skyes pa la //
NK113(e)001:1390: reg pa la sogs spong byed bcu gnyis kyi //
NK113(e)001:1391: gnyen po dang bcas bud med nyon mongs pas //
NK113(e)001:1392: lo gnyis la sogs thub bam mi thub brtag /
NK113(e)001:1393: dge slong rtsa ba'i pham pa bzhin dag dang //
NK113(e)001:1394: lhag ma bcu gsum spang ltung sum cu dang //
NK113(e)001:1395: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1396: sor bshags sde bzhi nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis //
NK113(e)001:1397: nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa gsum rnam grangs dang /
NK113(e)001:1398: dge slong ma la sum brgya drug cu bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1399: so so'i rtsa ba bzhi brgyad pham pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1400: nyes byas sbom po phyogs mthun khyad par yod //
NK113(e)001:1401: pham pas sdom pa rtsa nas gtong ba yin //
NK113(e)001:1402: phyin chad sor chud rung dang mi rung mtshams //
NK113(e)001:1403: 'chab sems skyes dang ma skyes dag la rag /
NK113(e)001:1404: bsrung bya mi shes bsrung bar rlom pa mtshar //
NK113(e)001:1405: ltung ba shes pa tsam gyis gso sbyong sla //
NK113(e)001:1406: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi'i dang po yang //
NK113(e)001:1407: mi shes pa zhes thogs med bzhed pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1408: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya gzhi gsum cho ga dang //
NK113(e)001:1409: bcu bdun bslab bya 'jug pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK113(e)001:1410: 'di na pham lhag bcu bdun ma gtogs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1411: mi rung longs spyod byin gyis brlab pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1412: dus ma yin par kha zas spyod dgos na //
NK113(e)001:1413: sgra mi snyan pa'i gling du mos pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1414: de bzhin khrus la nad pa gos lhag gam //
NK113(e)001:1415: rung ba ma yin bgo ba dkar po dang //
NK113(e)001:1416: ko pags sogs la phongs pas nyam thag par //
NK113(e)001:1417: srog bsrung slad du gnang ba yin snyam dang /
NK113(e)001:1418: rin po cher reg dkon cog mchod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1419: sems can gso ba'i slad du gnang bar bsgom //
NK113(e)001:1420: gnang med bkag pa med pa rjes mthun brtsi //
NK113(e)001:1421: thams cad yod smra phal chen sde pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1422: gnas brtan pa dang mang pos bkur ba ste //
NK113(e)001:1423: sde pa bzhi ka'i bslab pa thams cad la //
NK113(e)001:1424: ston pa'i bcas pas ma khyab mi srid pas //
NK113(e)001:1425: bslab pa kun la dbang thob byed pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1426: mya ngan 'das bar bsngo bas lhag pa'i khrims //
NK113(e)001:1427: gzhan la phan pa bsgrub pas byang sdom la //
NK113(e)001:1428: dbang bskur rnal ma thob na sngags sdom te //
NK113(e)001:1429: gsum rdzogs bslab bya yon tan mtha' dag mang //
NK113(e)001:1430: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du //
NK113(e)001:1431: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la gnas pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1432: nang 'gal byung na gong ma gtsor bton pa //
NK113(e)001:1433: sngon byon mkhas grub rnams kyi lugs la grags //
NK113(e)001:1434: 'og ma'i rnam pa 'gal ba ltar snang yang //
NK113(e)001:1435: gnod pa spong dang phan 'dogs dgos pa mthun //
NK113(e)001:1436: gang zhig 'gal na gnang bar mi srid la //
NK113(e)001:1437: gnang na 'gal bar mi srid de chos can //
NK113(e)001:1438: 'di lta nyan thos pa la ltung ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1439: byang chub sems dpar phyogs mthun nyes byas su //
NK113(e)001:1440: 'gyur ba'i myos byed sngags kyi dam rdzas su //
NK113(e)001:1441: spyod pa'i skyes bu'i rtog tshogs lhar shar bas //
NK113(e)001:1442: gzhi dang bsam pa gnyis ka gzhan du 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1443: dge slong ma yin byang chub sems dapa'ang min //
NK113(e)001:1444: thabs bral chags sred nyon mongs mthus non min //
NK113(e)001:1445: snang ba mtha' dag lha dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK113(e)001:1446: spyad bya'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i rang bzhi du //
NK113(e)001:1447: 'du shes gnas 'gyur gang la gnang ba yin //
NK113(e)001:1448: soo so thar dang byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK113(e)001:1449: dge slong dang ni dge 'dun la byin las //
NK113(e)001:1450: yi dam la phul tshogs kyang yar ldan 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1451: bslab pa'i cha shas gzhan la'ang de yis 'gre //
NK113(e)001:1452: 'on kyang rang ldog ma 'dres dgag dgos tshang //
NK113(e)001:1453: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yon tan yar ldan pas //
NK113(e)001:1454: gnad kyis mi 'gal dus skabs gtsor spyad do //
NK113(e)001:1455: grub pa'i mtha' la dpyad pa zhugs pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:1456: gnas 'gyur ngo bo gcig tu 'dod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1457: gcig la gzhi mi mthun du 'dod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1458: gsum ka rdzas 'gal gong 'phel 'dod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1459: gtong thob mtshams nas rnam par dbye ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1460: dong rtse brtsegs bzhin ma 'dres 'dod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1461: nyi zla skar gsum rim can tshoms pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:1462: rang 'od ma nyams nus pa'i khyad zhugs 'dod //
NK113(e)001:1463: de sogs rnam pa'i khas blang mtha' dag kyang //
NK113(e)001:1464: cho ga'i dus ltar rang ldog ma 'dres dang //
NK113(e)001:1465: bsrung mtshams dus na dgag dgos tshang ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1466: gnas 'gyur ngo bo ye shes mthus byed pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1467: spyir btang dmigs bsal phyed pa khyad par yin //
NK113(e)001:1468: gleng gzhi gnas 'gyur 'dod la phyir bcos med //
NK113(e)001:1469: so thar ngos nas byung ba'i ltung ba gcig /
NK113(e)001:1470: rang ngos 'chos na gnas 'gyur zin pas 'gal //
NK113(e)001:1471: gong ma'i ngos nas 'chos na de nyid la //
NK113(e)001:1472: lta ba ma byung phyir bcos mi dgos bsnyon //
NK113(e)001:1473: lus ngag las skyes sdom pa gzugs can nam //
NK113(e)001:1474: spong sems rgyun chags sa bon bden zhen ldan //
NK113(e)001:1475: bsgyur dang lam 'khyer thabs kyis ma zin par //
NK113(e)001:1476: theg chen lam zhugs dbang bskur nod na'ang //
NK113(e)001:1477: gnas 'gyur thob pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa min //
NK113(e)001:1478: sdom pa dag par byed pa 'du shes te //
NK113(e)001:1479: 'du shes dag byed lha yi rnal 'byor yin //
NK113(e)001:1480: de nyid dag byed ye shes la goms na //
NK113(e)001:1481: bcas pa'i ltung ba chos can skye 'jig can //
NK113(e)001:1482: rang mtshan mi 'dzin thob dang shor ba med //
NK113(e)001:1483: thog mtha' bar du 'gal bar mi gnas pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1484: ngo bo kun rdzob yin pas gnas 'gyur grub //
NK113(e)001:1485: gzhi dang bsam pa gnyis ka mngon gyur ldan //
NK113(e)001:1486: mos pas spyod pa'i sdom pa gsum ldan la //
NK113(e)001:1487: gnas na bye brag bsrung na 'chol bar bsrung //
NK113(e)001:1488: ldan na yang ldan 'chos na rang sa nas //
NK113(e)001:1489: nyams pa khol bur phyung ba'i phyir bcos 'grub //
NK113(e)001:1490: ci phyir nyes pa bskyed na gang yang 'gog /
NK113(e)001:1491: dge dang yon tan bskyed na gnang ba'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:1492: gnang bkag tshig gi lam na gnas pa min //
NK113(e)001:1493: gang zag rgyud dang 'brel nas grub pa'o //
NK113(e)001:1494: pha rol phyin pa drug dang tshogs gnyis kyi //
NK113(e)001:1495: yon tan ma skyes bskyed par byed pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1496: skyes pa spel la dge ba chos sdud kyi //
NK113(e)001:1497: tshul khrims zhes bya sems kyi bslab pas bsdus //
NK113(e)001:1498: byams dang snying rjes zin pa'i dge ba ni //
NK113(e)001:1499: gang du sems can don byed sbyin pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1500: de la rang 'dod med pa tshul khrims la //
NK113(e)001:1501: gzhan don skyo ngal med pa bzod pa'o //
NK113(e)001:1502: lhag par spro bzhin 'jug pa brtson 'grus te //
NK113(e)001:1503: sems can don la rtse gcig bsam gtan dang //
NK113(e)001:1504: dngos mtshan zhen pa spangs pa shes rab ste //
NK113(e)001:1505: pha rol phyin drug nam yang 'du 'bral med //
NK113(e)001:1506: spyod lam rnam bzhi kun la dran shes ldan //
NK113(e)001:1507: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i dge tshogs kyi //
NK113(e)001:1508: gom pa'i 'degs 'jog dag kyang phyin drug lam //
NK113(e)001:1509: rtsol med 'jug pas tshogs rjogs shin tu myur //
NK113(e)001:1510: thabs la mkhas pas dngos sam rgyud ma nas //
NK113(e)001:1511: sems can kun la phan pa lhur byed cing //
NK113(e)001:1512: sbyin dang snyan smra don spyod don mthun dang //
NK113(e)001:1513: dge ba chos sdud tshul khrims sgo 'phar yangs //
NK113(e)001:1514: gang la brtag pa drug tu gsungs pa'ang //
NK113(e)001:1515: rang gi chos la 'byor rgud brtag par 'du //
NK113(e)001:1516: rang nyid chos lam ma nyams gzhan don bya //
NK113(e)001:1517: rang don nyams pa'i so skyes 'khrul pa brtag /
NK113(e)001:1518: gzhan la phan pa rlabs chen 'grub srid na //
NK113(e)001:1519: bcas pa chung ngu bag yangs gnang ba'i skabs //
NK113(e)001:1520: yod de grong khyer phyir na grong rdal dang //
NK113(e)001:1521: bdag phyir sa gtong chos phyir bdag kyang gtong //
NK113(e)001:1522: 'di na mi mjed bzod pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK113(e)001:1523: chos kyi dri bzang rgyas pa rab bsrung ba'i //
NK113(e)001:1524: dka' ba dang len bzod pa ji mi snyam //
NK113(e)001:1525: zab mo'i don la mi skrag rnam pa gsum //
NK113(e)001:1526: yid ni shin tu rengs byas zhe sdang gi //
NK113(e)001:1527: sdig pa'i mngon rtogs mun pa'i 'khri shing can //
NK113(e)001:1528: thar med dmyal bar 'dzul la skrag pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:1529: nam yang khro ba'i go skabs dbye mi bgyid //
NK113(e)001:1530: gnod pa'i yul ni nags kyi tsher ma bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1531: gdul gyi mi lang kun nas 'phel ba can //
NK113(e)001:1532: 'khon dang khro ba'i byed po gcig btul na //
NK113(e)001:1533: bzod pa'i dka' thub bdag la mdza' bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1534: reg pa shin tu rtsub pa'i tshig gi mdas //
NK113(e)001:1535: skyes bu'i snying la zug pa cang mchi'am //
NK113(e)001:1536: de nyid dang du blang ba'i nyer len gyis //
NK113(e)001:1537: phan tshun rten dang brten par 'khrugs bzhin mnar //
NK113(e)001:1538: 'di na gnod pa'i rgyu 'bras mtha' yas su //
NK113(e)001:1539: bdag nyid las byung sgra dang brag ca bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1540: bdag nyid ma byung gnod pa'i yul med pas //
NK113(e)001:1541: rang gi sngon byas rkyen gyis bos la ltos //
NK113(e)001:1542: brtags na gnod chen ma yin phan chen te //
NK113(e)001:1543: gang la brten nas bzod pa'i gru gzings dang //
NK113(e)001:1544: byang chub sems kyi nor bu 'thob 'gyur bas //
NK113(e)001:1545: de 'dra'i gnod pa dam pa'i chos ltar mchod //
NK113(e)001:1546: shin tu brtags na gnod pa'i ngo bo la //
NK113(e)001:1547: mtshan nyid med de chu yi ri mo bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1548: rnam rtog khro gnyer rtsub mo zhig pa'i mod //
NK113(e)001:1549: mkha' bzhin rnam par stong la thob shor med //
NK113(e)001:1550: gang phyir bzod pa'i dka' thub gsum nyams na //
NK113(e)001:1551: sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa gzhan lnga yang //
NK113(e)001:1552: phyi mtha' dgra yis bskor ba'i bshul lam bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1553: 'dod pa'i gnas su phyin dka' blo stobs bskyed //
NK113(e)001:1554: dus las yol ba med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis //
NK113(e)001:1555: rang dbang nyid du dge ba'i chos mtha' dag /
NK113(e)001:1556: skyed mos tshal du ngang pa 'gro ba bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1557: le lo'i g.yang la bskyud pa med par 'jug /
NK113(e)001:1558: bya ba ngan zhen 'du 'dzi'i thag pas dkris //
NK113(e)001:1559: sgyid lug mthus non sbyor bas nus pa'ang btang //
NK113(e)001:1560: bdag nyid brnyan nas sems zhum brtul zhugs blangs //
NK113(e)001:1561: de 'dra'i gang zag nyes ba'i gzings la zhon //
NK113(e)001:1562: bdud bzhi 'joms pa go cha'i brtson 'grus dang //
NK113(e)001:1563: sa bcu'i lam 'gro sbyor ba'i brtson 'grus dang //
NK113(e)001:1564: mi 'gong mi ldog chog shes med pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1565: brtson 'grus can gyi smos pa'i don kun 'grub //
NK113(e)001:1566: bdag gi tshe ni nyin mo'i mthar gyur te //
NK113(e)001:1567: myur ba myur bar 'chi ba'i mun nag gis //
NK113(e)001:1568: gtugs na 'khor ba'i spyod pa rgyu skar las //
NK113(e)001:1569: rnam grangs mang ba de yis dbugs mi phyin //
NK113(e)001:1570: le lo'i rnyog pa dwangs pa'i rtson 'grus kyi //
NK113(e)001:1571: dal 'bab phyogs lhung ston pa ma yin par //
NK113(e)001:1572: rnam pa kun mkhyen rgya mtshor phyin de srid //
NK113(e)001:1573: g.yo zhing myur ba'i brtul zhugs nyams mi bgyid //
NK113(e)001:1574: nags tshal me tog 'khrigs pa'i sman ljongs ni //
NK113(e)001:1575: ngang pa shin tu zhi bas brten byas shing //
NK113(e)001:1576: lta na sdug pa brag ri'i pha gu dang //
NK113(e)001:1577: rta babs ri dwags gzhon nus mdzes pa yod //
NK113(e)001:1578: dga' ba'i nags tshal lha mo'i sked chings ni //
NK113(e)001:1579: shing bal gzhon nu'i d+r+wa phyed g.yo ba na //
NK113(e)001:1580: dogs pas skrag pa min pa'i khu byug rnams //
NK113(e)001:1581: 'khor bar skyo ba'i gtam gyi spring yig 'grem //
NK113(e)001:1582: de ru gshegs shig bsam gtan 'dod pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:1583: longs spyod sprin gyi bla re'i nang shed na //
NK113(e)001:1584: tshe srog rol pa'i glog ni g.yo zhing 'dar //
NK113(e)001:1585: 'gyu dang sdug bsngal 'du byed chom rkun dkyu //
NK113(e)001:1586: phung krol bskyed pa'i chu klung ca co can //
NK113(e)001:1587: gsog dang bsrung dang spel ba'i 'dod pas 'khrugs //
NK113(e)001:1588: khengs dang 'jungs dang ser snas tshe gtugs nas //
NK113(e)001:1589: ngan 'gro'i chu gter mu mtha' med par 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:1590: g.yo sgyu'i char sprin brnags pa'i rin thang can //
NK113(e)001:1591: nor ni ji tsam 'byor bzhin sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK113(e)001:1592: yo byad bsnyungs rnams dgra rkun 'tshe bas spong //
NK113(e)001:1593: chog shes thob pa 'byor pa'i rtse mor 'gro //
NK113(e)001:1594: so so skye bo'i rang bzhin byis pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1595: byis pa rnams ni nyes pa'i sprin gyis 'khrigs //
NK113(e)001:1596: bdag nyid bstod cing gzhan la mi snyan sgrog /
NK113(e)001:1597: nyon mongs sbrul lce rtsub mo'i nyams bag bsten //
NK113(e)001:1598: dpal 'byor g.yo ba gang la'ang rtag par sems //
NK113(e)001:1599: byas pa mi gzo mgu ba'i gzugs brnyan 'khyog /
NK113(e)001:1600: mkhon gyi me lce phra ma'i rlung gis bskyod //
NK113(e)001:1601: spre'u bzhin du gnod pa sna tshogs ster //
NK113(e)001:1602: chu srin bzhin du sdig pa'i lto ba yangs /
NK113(e)001:1603: sbrul gdug bzhin du su dang phrad pa 'joms //
NK113(e)001:1604: me bzhin dge ba'i ljon shing bsreg 'gyur ba'i //
NK113(e)001:1605: byis pa'i grogs las ring du bsring bar bya //
NK113(e)001:1606: yul ni dug las thu ste rnam smin rtsub //
NK113(e)001:1607: spyad pa'i mod la 'da' ba'i ro bro yang //
NK113(e)001:1608: tshe rabs gcig min skye ba thams cad du //
NK113(e)001:1609: gsang sngags mchog dang sman gyi gsor mi rung //
NK113(e)001:1610: gang zhig sems kyi glang po ma dul bar //
NK113(e)001:1611: bslu ba'i rdzu 'phrul yul las che ba med //
NK113(e)001:1612: phung po'i 'du byed phyogs la bzhag de srid //
NK113(e)001:1613: zhi ba'i nags mthongs dag la bsnyen par mdzod //
NK113(e)001:1614: bas mtha' 'brog ni yid 'ong skyo shas 'phel //
NK113(e)001:1615: tshong dang so nam sdig pa'i grogs kyis spangs //
NK113(e)001:1616: dpya dang khral dang zho shas 'tshos mi gdung //
NK113(e)001:1617: bya dang ri dwags mi snyan sgrog pa med //
NK113(e)001:1618: chu gtsang 'bras bu'i nyer spyod rgya che la //
NK113(e)001:1619: brag ri'i phung dang lo ma'i khang bzang yangs //
NK113(e)001:1620: ljon pa'i grib bsil 'grogs na bde ba dang /
NK113(e)001:1621: nam zhig bdag ni lhan cig gnas 'gyur bas //
NK113(e)001:1622: de na dus bzhi'i mgron po gsar pa yis //
NK113(e)001:1623: 'pho 'gyur mngon rtogs ngom pa'i nags tshal rnams //
NK113(e)001:1624: rang nyid nyon mongs ma yin gtan tshigs su //
NK113(e)001:1625: gom bdun phyogs pa'i bsod nams sgrog la ltos //
NK113(e)001:1626: gang du bsam gtan shin tu brten pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1627: lhag pa sems kyi bslab pa'i mtshan nyid de //
NK113(e)001:1628: rten cing 'brel 'byung lus kyi cho ga ni //
NK113(e)001:1629: rnam snang chos bdun sems kyi srog shing can //
NK113(e)001:1630: gcig las gnyis pa ma yin mnyam gzhag brtson //
NK113(e)001:1631: dmigs pa gang yang rung ba'i 'dzin dpyad kyis //
NK113(e)001:1632: yid ni dge ba'i don la rnam par bcing //
NK113(e)001:1633: spros pa'i snang ba chos nyin gcig tu nub //
NK113(e)001:1634: snang yul ma 'gags der 'dzin med pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1635: shes pa yul la mi rtog mnyam bzhag la //
NK113(e)001:1636: ngo bo gcig ba'i rjes thob lhag mthong ste //
NK113(e)001:1637: dbye na byis pa nyer spyod don rab 'byed //
NK113(e)001:1638: de bzhin gshegs dge'i bsam gtan rnam gsum dang //
NK113(e)001:1639: rtog dpyod yod med mu bzhi'i bsam gtan bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1640: de bzhin gzugs med bzhi ste rnam pa'i grangs //
NK113(e)001:1641: lam ma zhugs pa'i rgyud kyi ting 'dzin ni //
NK113(e)001:1642: bsam gtan gzugs med byis pa nyer spyod yin //
NK113(e)001:1643: lam zhugs tshogs dang sbyor ba'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK113(e)001:1644: thar lam mngon byed don rab 'byed par grags //
NK113(e)001:1645: dang po'i sa yan 'phags pa'i ting 'dzin te //
NK113(e)001:1646: zag pa med pas de bzhin gshegs dge yin //
NK113(e)001:1647: kun kyang ngo bo nang du sems 'dzin la //
NK113(e)001:1648: rgyu ni dran pa rgyun chags brtson 'grus can //
NK113(e)001:1649: rnam par g.yeng na slar yang de la bslan //
NK113(e)001:1650: byed las bde ba bskyed cing rdzu 'phrul 'grub //
NK113(e)001:1651: 'bras bu mngon shes la sogs thob pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1652: bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdogs rtog cing dpyod //
NK113(e)001:1653: dngos gzhi rtog pa med la spyod pa tsam //
NK113(e)001:1654: lhag ma gsum por rtog dpyod gnyis ka med //
NK113(e)001:1655: snga ma snga mas phyi ma'i nyer bsdoms byed //
NK113(e)001:1656: 'phags pa'i lam gyi rten gzhi zhes su grags //
NK113(e)001:1657: yon tan thams cad byed pa'i bsam gtan ni //
NK113(e)001:1658: snying rje dang ni ye shes dam pas zin //
NK113(e)001:1659: ting 'dzin mang ldan rnam pa thams cad bsgrub //
NK113(e)001:1660: blo rdzas gcig pa'i mnyam rjes gzung 'dzin spong //
NK113(e)001:1661: mnyam gzhag las la'ang rjes thob rgya yan pa //
NK113(e)001:1662: sa bdun tshun chad kun na yod pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1663: lhag pa shes rab bslab pa'i nges 'byed ni //
NK113(e)001:1664: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor ba las skyes zhing //
NK113(e)001:1665: dngos dang rjes la byung ba'i shes rab bam //
NK113(e)001:1666: thos dang bsam pa sgom pa las byung ba'i //
NK113(e)001:1667: shes rab gsum gyi lhag mthong yang dag 'grub //
NK113(e)001:1668: nyon mongs tshogs 'joms chos dang chos can shes //
NK113(e)001:1669: srid pa'i grong las mya ngan med par 'da' //
NK113(e)001:1670: sbyin sogs rnam pa drug po'ang gong nas gong //
NK113(e)001:1671: khyad zhugs shes rab pha rol phyin la bsten //
NK113(e)001:1672: de'ang 'di na so so'i skye bo'i sar //
NK113(e)001:1673: thos pa las byung shes rab ma bsten na //
NK113(e)001:1674: bsam dang sgom pa'i yon tan gnas min 'khyams //
NK113(e)001:1675: thos pa'i shes rab kun gyi rgyu ru gsungs //
NK113(e)001:1676: gzhal bya'i chos la 'jal byed shes rab kyis //
NK113(e)001:1677: drang nges gnyis dang ldem dgongs rnam bzhir gzhal //
NK113(e)001:1678: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bo de bzhin nyid //
NK113(e)001:1679: rnam thar gsum du gnas pa nges don yin //
NK113(e)001:1680: chos can snang tshod lam la 'jug pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:1681: rig pas gzhal nas sgro btags drang ba'i lam //
NK113(e)001:1682: gnyis pos drang nges gang la rton mi rton //
NK113(e)001:1683: shes de gsung rab blta ba'i lde mig yin //
NK113(e)001:1684: de dag rang bzhin gsal bar bya ba dang //
NK113(e)001:1685: don gyi dgongs pa rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:1686: dgongs ldem gnyis bshad dang po dgongs pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1687: cung zad sgro btags bshad du yang yod la //
NK113(e)001:1688: gdul bya'i yul rnams re shig kha drang ba //
NK113(e)001:1689: gcig pu'i slad du ma yin dgos ched dang //
NK113(e)001:1690: bcas nas dgongs pa rnam bzhir ston pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1691: mnyam pa nyid dgongs 'gal ba'ang gcig tu bstan //
NK113(e)001:1692: don gzhan la dgongs dpyad na ma grub bstan //
NK113(e)001:1693: dus gzhan la dgongs 'bad med 'tshang rgya bstan //
NK113(e)001:1694: gang zag la dgongs de de'i mchog 'dzin smad //
NK113(e)001:1695: ldem por dgongs pa gdul bya gang zhig gi //
NK113(e)001:1696: blo la mi chud yid gnyis gnas thob rnams //
NK113(e)001:1697: de nyid dga' ba'i ming dang cha ldan gyi //
NK113(e)001:1698: rnam par kyogs nas yang dag lam gzud phyir //
NK113(e)001:1699: tshig mthun don mi mthun par bshad pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1700: dbye na zhugs pa mtshan nyid gnyen po bsgyur //
NK113(e)001:1701: zhugs pa ldem dgongs gang zhig nyan thos dag /
NK113(e)001:1702: stong pas skrag nas theg chen spong ba la //
NK113(e)001:1703: gzugs yod smos pas grub par go nas 'jug /
NK113(e)001:1704: snang tshod rmi lam lta bur dgongs pa'o //
NK113(e)001:1705: mtshan nyid ldem dgongs ngo bo nyid med don //
NK113(e)001:1706: shes pa'i don du rim bzhin kun btags dang //
NK113(e)001:1707: gzhan dbang yongs grub rnam pa gsum dag las //
NK113(e)001:1708: dang por mtshan nyid ngo bo nyid med dang //
NK113(e)001:1709: gnyis par skye ba ngo bo nyid med dang //
NK113(e)001:1710: gsum par don dam ngo bo nyid med pas //
NK113(e)001:1711: chos rnams brjod pa zab pa dag tu ston //
NK113(e)001:1712: gnyen po ldem dgongs gzhan gyi log rtog ldog /
NK113(e)001:1713: sku tshe rigs dang sku bongs tshad kyis min //
NK113(e)001:1714: sangs rgyas thams cad gzugs sku chos skur mnyam //
NK113(e)001:1715: tshogs kyi yul la'ang mnyam pa lta bur dgongs //
NK113(e)001:1716: bsgyur ba ldem dgongs bsad bya ma yin pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1717: pha ma gsod dang de bzhin bcom bya min //
NK113(e)001:1718: rgyal po dang ni gtsang sbra can gnyis bcom //
NK113(e)001:1719: sred len kun gzhi sogs la btags pa'i don //
NK113(e)001:1720: rnal mar bzung na nor pa chen po'o //
NK113(e)001:1721: mdor na dgongs dang ldem po'i khyad par ni //
NK113(e)001:1722: dgongs pa yid la rnam par bzhag pa tsam //
NK113(e)001:1723: yin gyi pha rol bzung la ltos pa min //
NK113(e)001:1724: ldem por dgongs pa pha rol bzung ba la //
NK113(e)001:1725: ltos pa'i rnam 'byed gsung rab lta ba'i mig /
NK113(e)001:1726: gzhal bya'i ngos nas rgyal bas chos kyi sgo //
NK113(e)001:1727: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa mtha' dag don //
NK113(e)001:1728: 'jig rten kun rdzob pa dang don dam ste //
NK113(e)001:1729: bden pa gnyis las gsum pa ma mchis so //
NK113(e)001:1730: kun rdzob pa la snang lugs rnam pa gnyis //
NK113(e)001:1731: 'khrul shes ngo la snang ba ji snyed kyi //
NK113(e)001:1732: snang tshod nyid dang mthun par don byed rnams //
NK113(e)001:1733: yang dag kun rdzob nyid de snang na'ang //
NK113(e)001:1734: don mi byed la log pa'i kun rdzob grags //
NK113(e)001:1735: don dam bden pa gshis kyi bzhugs tshul te //
NK113(e)001:1736: 'khor ba dang ni mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK113(e)001:1737: ngo bo gnyis med gdod nas bsam brjod 'das //
NK113(e)001:1738: rtogs dang ma rtogs blo yi ma bzhag go //
NK113(e)001:1739: bden gnyis 'dres pa'i snang stong zung 'jug ni //
NK113(e)001:1740: rdzing bur zhugs pa'i zla ba'i skye mched bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1741: snang ba'i cha nas kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1742: rang bzhin ma grub don dam bden pa'o //
NK113(e)001:1743: yul lnga'i shes pa tshon ris ma 'dres ltas //
NK113(e)001:1744: gzugs sogs 'dod pa'i longs spyod cha bzung ba //
NK113(e)001:1745: de la der 'dzin dgag bsgrub blo rtog gi //
NK113(e)001:1746: 'khrul snang sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad nyid du brtag /
NK113(e)001:1747: mthar thug blo yis rnam par dpyad bzod na //
NK113(e)001:1748: don dam ma yin blo ni kun rdzob phyir //
NK113(e)001:1749: gcig dang du mar 'gal ba'i mtshan nyid rnams //
NK113(e)001:1750: blo yi yul la nam yang gnas ma myong //
NK113(e)001:1751: re zhig grub pa'i mtha' yi rnam bzhag ni //
NK113(e)001:1752: shes pa'i don dam blo yis dpyad pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1753: dngos po'i don dam tho bas bcom pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1754: rdul phran cha med nyan thos sde ba'i lugs //
NK113(e)001:1755: don byed nus pa gang yin de 'dir ni //
NK113(e)001:1756: don dam yod min gzhan ni kun rdzob yod //
NK113(e)001:1757: de la rang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyis bshad pa //
NK113(e)001:1758: mdo sde pa'i lugs ngo bo rtog ger mthun //
NK113(e)001:1759: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i yul yul can //
NK113(e)001:1760: kun rdzob bden pa nyid de gang las gzhan //
NK113(e)001:1761: gnyis med shes pa don dam bden pa ru //
NK113(e)001:1762: 'dod pa sems tsam pa yi grub pa'i mtha' //
NK113(e)001:1763: ji ltar snang ba thams cad kun rdzob tu //
NK113(e)001:1764: grub pa sgyu ma lta bu'i mtshan nyid de //
NK113(e)001:1765: don dam grub pa med pa nam mkha' ltar //
NK113(e)001:1766: 'dod pa dbu ma rang rgyud pa yi lugs //
NK113(e)001:1767: 'di ltar snang ba nyid ni kun rdzob dang //
NK113(e)001:1768: stong pa don dam shes bya tha snyad kyis //
NK113(e)001:1769: btags pa gang yang spros pa'i matha dang bral //
NK113(e)001:1770: snang dus nyid nas skye 'gag 'gro 'ong med //
NK113(e)001:1771: gzhan dbang dngos por 'dod pa'i kun rdzob kyang //
NK113(e)001:1772: de yi grub pa'i mtha' ru khas ma blangs //
NK113(e)001:1773: de ni thal 'gyur shing rta'i srol 'byed che //
NK113(e)001:1774: klu dbang zla ba grags pa'i khyad chos yin //
NK113(e)001:1775: 'dir ni 'og ma'i rnam pa thams cad la //
NK113(e)001:1776: brtsad cing brtags pas gong ma nor mi 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1777: rang rang 'dod zhen gyis sbyar ltos grub kyi //
NK113(e)001:1778: grub pa'i mtha' yi mtshan nyid nyams 'og chud //
NK113(e)001:1779: de las dngos dang dngos 'dra dngos min gyi //
NK113(e)001:1780: mtshan nyid legs par phyed pa'i shes rab kyang //
NK113(e)001:1781: thos la brten 'byung de yis nyon mongs bcil //
NK113(e)001:1782: nyon mongs med la bdud kyis glags mi rnyed //
NK113(e)001:1783: 'dir gang bzung na gshis kyi bzhugs tshul la //
NK113(e)001:1784: smra bsam brjod med don dam bden pa yin //
NK113(e)001:1785: blo yi cha nas smra bsam brjod pa ru //
NK113(e)001:1786: btags shing snang ba kun rdzob bden pa'i char //
NK113(e)001:1787: bzhag nas bden gnyis rtogs bya rtogs byed las //
NK113(e)001:1788: 'das pa sus kyang mngon du byar med la //
NK113(e)001:1789: bltar med thob dang ma thob gnyis ka med //
NK113(e)001:1790: stong pa nyid dang nges par rjes mthun pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1791: blo skyes pa la rtogs pa'i bla dwags btags //
NK113(e)001:1793: chos rnams ma lus kun gyi mdzod //
NK113(e)001:1794: gang la bsam pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK113(e)001:1795: yang dag 'jug pa lde mig yin //
NK113(e)001:1797: gang nas kyang ni ma 'ongs la //
NK113(e)001:1798: gang du'ang ma song mi gnas pa //
NK113(e)001:1799: gshis la gnas pa'i rten cing 'brel //
NK113(e)001:1800: chos can nyid kyang skye 'gag ltar //
NK113(e)001:1801: snang dus nyid nas stong par shar //
NK113(e)001:1802: spros pa'i mtha' la mi gnas pa //
NK113(e)001:1803: dbu ma'i rang bzhin nyid du bstan //
NK113(e)001:1804: dag dang ma dag glo bur ba //
NK113(e)001:1805: don la med kyang med bzhin snang //
NK113(e)001:1806: kun tu btags pas nye bar len //
NK113(e)001:1807: rtog cing dpyad pas mtha' bzhi byung //
NK113(e)001:1808: yod dang med dang rtag dang chad //
NK113(e)001:1809: dbus la gnas pa'ang mkhas pa min //
NK113(e)001:1810: ji ltar dar gyi srid bu bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1811: 'dod pa'i grub mthas rang nyid bcings //
NK113(e)001:1812: 'di na blo yis btags pa'i chos //
NK113(e)001:1814: don gcig ma yin tha dad min //
NK113(e)001:1815: rtag pa ma yin chad pa'ang min //
NK113(e)001:1816: spros pa mtha' dag nyer zhi ba'i //
NK113(e)001:1817: rang bzhin nyid du shes pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1818: bsam byung shes rab ngo bo yin //
NK113(e)001:1819: snang yul sa chu me rlung mkha' //
NK113(e)001:1820: ri dang nags tshal khang bu brtsegs //
NK113(e)001:1821: 'du byed rgyu las thams cad skyes //
NK113(e)001:1823: ma rig pa las 'du byed de //
NK113(e)001:1824: debazhina gcig la gcig rten gyis //
NK113(e)001:1825: rga shi'i bar du 'brel ba ni //
NK113(e)001:1828: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis su gnas //
NK113(e)001:1830: lugs su 'jug pa bcu gnyis kyi //
NK113(e)001:1831: rtsa ba ma rig chen po ni //
NK113(e)001:1832: rig pa'i ye shes kyis ldog pas //
NK113(e)001:1833: 'du byed la sogs gzhan rnams kyang //
NK113(e)001:1834: lugs ldog srid pa'i rtsa ba chad //
NK113(e)001:1836: mtshan nyid mthong ba'i skyes bu yis //
NK113(e)001:1837: sdug bsngal shes shing kun 'byung spong //
NK113(e)001:1838: 'gog pa mngon gyur lam mchog mthong //
NK113(e)001:1839: de ltar snang ba skye med du //
NK113(e)001:1840: bsam pas gtan la phab pa de'i //
NK113(e)001:1841: rang bzhin shes pa'i chos nyid la //
NK113(e)001:1842: sgom pa'i shes rab ces su grags //
NK113(e)001:1843: nam mkha' rnam par dag pa'i dbyings //
NK113(e)001:1844: sgom pa'i don dang ro gcig pa //
NK113(e)001:1845: de la gzugs sogs phung po lnga //
NK113(e)001:1846: tshogs brgyad kun kyang yod ma yin //
NK113(e)001:1847: med ces blo yis bkag pa na //
NK113(e)001:1848: shes rab nyid dang lhag par 'gal //
NK113(e)001:1849: cang med chad pa nyid ma yin //
NK113(e)001:1850: sku dang ye shes kun gyi mdzod //
NK113(e)001:1851: rang bzhin nyid du rnam dag pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1852: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK113(e)001:1853: blta zhes bya ba'ang kun rdzob ste //
NK113(e)001:1854: ngang las ma g.yos sgom pa'i mchog /
NK113(e)001:1855: de yi mdun na blo dang ni //
NK113(e)001:1856: yid byed thams cad gnas pa min //
NK113(e)001:1857: shes rab de 'drar yongs shes na //
NK113(e)001:1858: thabs kyis rnam par grol bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1859: shes rab med pa'i thabs kyis ni //
NK113(e)001:1860: bcings pa nyid las grol ba med //
NK113(e)001:1861: gang du stong nyid snying rje gnyis //
NK113(e)001:1862: rgyud la bsten pa tshogs lam che //
NK113(e)001:1863: sbyor lam chos mchog man chad du //
NK113(e)001:1864: mnyam rjes stong dang snying rjer 'char //
NK113(e)001:1865: mthong lam thob nas gnyis po ni //
NK113(e)001:1867: rab tu dga' ba dang po'i sar //
NK113(e)001:1868: chos nyid bden pa mngon sum mthong //
NK113(e)001:1869: de nas 'phags pa'i sgom lam du //
NK113(e)001:1870: sa bcu rgyun gyi mtha' ma la //
NK113(e)001:1871: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK113(e)001:1872: shes sgrib bcom nas mngon byang chub //
NK113(e)001:1873: mnyam par ma gzhag med pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:1874: rgyal ba'i ma 'dres chos bco brgyad //
NK113(e)001:1875: stobs bcu dang ni mi 'jigs bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1876: mtha' dag mngon gyur sangs rgyas yin //
NK113(e)001:1877: 'di ltar pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK113(e)001:1878: rgyal ba kun gyi gzhung lam ste //
NK113(e)001:1879: lta bas ma rmongs spyod pa'ang //
NK113(e)001:1881: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:1882: smon 'jug gi bslab bya bstan pa'i tshoms te le'u dgu pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:1883: byang chub sems dpa' sngags kyi theg pa la //
NK113(e)001:1884: 'bras bu'am ni rdo rje'i theg pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1885: thabs kyi theg pa rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK113(e)001:1886: sde snod ces grags rgyu las khyad par 'phags //
NK113(e)001:1887: rgyun chags ngos nas gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud //
NK113(e)001:1888: rim gnyis la brten thabs dang shes rab 'brel //
NK113(e)001:1889: dka' thub mthu yis mi gdung 'jug sgo yangs //
NK113(e)001:1890: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas brtul zhugs myur //
NK113(e)001:1891: dus la dgongs pa rdzogs ldan gsum ldan dang /
NK113(e)001:1892: gnyis ldan dang ni rtsod par ldan pa bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1893: rigs la dgongs pa bram ze rje'u rigs //
NK113(e)001:1894: rgyal po dang ni dmangs sam gdol pa'o //
NK113(e)001:1895: dbang por dgongs pa rtul 'bring rnon dang mchog /
NK113(e)001:1896: chos ni bya spyod rnal 'byor bla na med //
NK113(e)001:1897: dang po gsum ni gsang sngags phyi pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1898: thub pas dngos gsungs mtshan nyid theg pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1899: gtsang sbra sdom pa'i kun spyod phal cher mtshungs //
NK113(e)001:1900: rtsod pa'i dus dang 'gal ba'i 'dod chags kyis //
NK113(e)001:1901: kun spyod lam byed lha yang zung 'brel min //
NK113(e)001:1902: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la longs mi spyod //
NK113(e)001:1903: dbye na bya ba dang ni spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK113(e)001:1904: sems dpa' sems ma rig sngags gzungs sngags lha //
NK113(e)001:1905: bya bas rje khol spyod pas spun grogs tshul //
NK113(e)001:1906: bya bas rje khol rnam par bsgrub pa la'ang //
NK113(e)001:1907: bdag bskyed med par rang nyid dman par bzhag /
NK113(e)001:1908: la lar yod de gtso bor mdun bskyed ston //
NK113(e)001:1909: phyi yi bya ba khrus dang gtsang sbra gtso //
NK113(e)001:1910: mchog dman tshul du bsgrubs nas dngos grub 'dod //
NK113(e)001:1911: bya ba'i thabs dang nang gi rnal 'byor la //
NK113(e)001:1912: cha mnyam spyod pas spyod pa'i rgyud du grags //
NK113(e)001:1913: rang nyid dam tshig sems dpa'i mdun bzhugs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:1914: ye shes lha la spun ltar dngos grub len //
NK113(e)001:1915: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi gru chad man chad la //
NK113(e)001:1916: bkod pa chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:1917: bstan yang zung 'brel ma yin bskyed dang rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:1918: thabs dang shes rab rim can so so ba //
NK113(e)001:1919: rnal 'byor gtsor spyod lus ngag grogs su ston //
NK113(e)001:1920: ye shes dgug bstim phyag rgya bzhi yis bcing //
NK113(e)001:1921: dam ye gcig pa'i ngang nas dngos grub blang //
NK113(e)001:1922: bzlas pa'i mtha' la gshegs gsol bya ba'o //
NK113(e)001:1923: bla na med pa gsang sngags nang pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1924: bskyed dang rdzogs dang zung du 'jug pa las //
NK113(e)001:1925: pha rgyud ma rgyud gnyis med rgyud du bzhag /
NK113(e)001:1926: lha ni 'khril sbyor dam rdzas khyad par spyod //
NK113(e)001:1927: gtsang brtsog spong len med pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK113(e)001:1928: rnal 'byor chen po pha rgyud thabs kyi lam //
NK113(e)001:1929: bskyed rim gtsor byas rlung lnga dag par byed //
NK113(e)001:1930: rjes su rnal 'byor ma rgyud shes rab lam //
NK113(e)001:1931: rdzogs rim gtsor byed khams las zhu bde bskyed //
NK113(e)001:1932: shin tu rnal 'byor gnyis med ye shes lam //
NK113(e)001:1933: gcig dang du bral 'od gsal chen por sbyor //
NK113(e)001:1934: kun gyi gnad du khams drug ldan pa'i lus //
NK113(e)001:1935: phung po khams dang kye mched rtsa thig rlung //
NK113(e)001:1936: las su rung las bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gsum //
NK113(e)001:1937: yon tan kun bskyed rdo rje theg pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:1938: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor chen po ru /
NK113(e)001:1939: lta bas thag bcad sgom pas nyams su blangs //
NK113(e)001:1940: spyod pas la dor 'bras bus don gnyis bsgrub //
NK113(e)001:1941: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud la yang dag bsten //
NK113(e)001:1942: 'jug pa'i sgo ni smin par byed pa'i dbang //
NK113(e)001:1943: grol bar byed pa bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gnyis //
NK113(e)001:1944: mthun pa'i grogs su dam tshig spyod pa gsum //
NK113(e)001:1945: sngags kyi lam mchog rnal mar nges pa las //
NK113(e)001:1946: dang po dbang bskur ma thob dngos grub med //
NK113(e)001:1947: bye ma btsir las zhun mar 'dod pa bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1948: 'chad nyan sgom la brtson kyang dmyal bar 'gro //
NK113(e)001:1949: dbang thob skyes bu rgyal ba'i sras su 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:1950: dkyil 'khor mthong bas sdig las rnam par grol //
NK113(e)001:1951: gtsang ma'i rigs skye skye ba bdun dag na //
NK113(e)001:1952: nges par 'grub cing sa bcu thob par bshad //
NK113(e)001:1953: dbang bskur slob dpon rim gnyis gding dang bral //
NK113(e)001:1954: bsti gnas dkor spyod ma bsdams khyim la chags //
NK113(e)001:1955: snying rje chung dang rtog ges zil non des //
NK113(e)001:1956: dbang bskur byas kyang be sprel g.yang sar lhung //
NK113(e)001:1957: phyi nang gsang ba'i de nyid rnam pa bcu //
NK113(e)001:1958: rig cing rang nyid grol ba'i bla ma yis //
NK113(e)001:1959: dad dang ngo tsha shes pa'i slob ma'i rgyud //
NK113(e)001:1960: brtags la dbang bskur rim pas sbyin par bya //
NK113(e)001:1961: bsnyen pa dang ni sa yi cho ga dang //
NK113(e)001:1962: sta gon dang ni slob ma 'jug cing smin //
NK113(e)001:1963: mngon rtogs bzhi po re re nyid la yang //
NK113(e)001:1964: bzhi bzhir rdzogs pa'i yan lag ma tshang na //
NK113(e)001:1965: cho ga nyams pas smin par nus ma yin //
NK113(e)001:1966: rgyud sde so so'i dbang ga rigs dbye la //
NK113(e)001:1967: bya ba'i rgyud la chu dang cod pan gnyis //
NK113(e)001:1968: spyod pa'i rgyud la de steng rdo rje ming //
NK113(e)001:1969: rnal 'byor rgyud la rig pa'i dbang lnga dang //
NK113(e)001:1970: gsang ba bka' yi dbang du mtha' rten rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:1971: bla med bum gsang shes rab tshig dbang bzhi //
NK113(e)001:1972: theg pa'i rtse mo'i rim pa bye brag pa //
NK113(e)001:1973: spros dang spros med shin tu rab spros med //
NK113(e)001:1974: spyir na dbang gi dbye bsdu mtha' yas kyang //
NK113(e)001:1975: sa zin 'jog mtshams rnam pa bzhi po yin //
NK113(e)001:1976: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu dbang bzhi ru //
NK113(e)001:1977: gdod nas grub pa rtsa rlung thig le'i rten //
NK113(e)001:1978: rang chas nyid de mtshungs par ldan pa dang //
NK113(e)001:1979: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni rnam gnyis la //
NK113(e)001:1980: snod du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu yi rkyen //
NK113(e)001:1981: lta dgongs ldan pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen //
NK113(e)001:1982: nus pa'i cho ga mkhyen pa dmigs pa'i rkyen //
NK113(e)001:1983: rten cing 'brel 'byung de ma thag pa'i rkyen //
NK113(e)001:1984: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs las dbang bskur 'grub //
NK113(e)001:1985: gnyen po grangs nges sgo nas bzhag pa ni //
NK113(e)001:1986: lus kyi gtso bor gyur pa rtsa yin te //
NK113(e)001:1987: rtsa yi rnam pa yi ge'i gzugs su gnas //
NK113(e)001:1988: de la rlung brten rlung la khams rnams brten //
NK113(e)001:1989: khams la don dam byang chub sems brten bzhin //
NK113(e)001:1990: 'dod pa'i khams kyi gang zag rang rgyud pa //
NK113(e)001:1991: kun la 'dod chags rnam bzhir gnas pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:1992: dag bya dag byed la brten nges pa yang //
NK113(e)001:1993: dang po bltas pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags ni //
NK113(e)001:1994: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed pa la gnas pa ste //
NK113(e)001:1995: rdul tshon dkyil 'khor la brten bum pa'i dbang //
NK113(e)001:1996: bskur bas gtso bor lus kyi sgrib pa 'dag /
NK113(e)001:1997: snod bcud brtan g.yo phung khams skye mched kun //
NK113(e)001:1998: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor gcig tu shar //
NK113(e)001:1999: snang stong zung 'jug ngo bo nyid gsum gyi //
NK113(e)001:2000: grub mtha' 'khor 'das gnyis med chen po la //
NK113(e)001:2001: 'da' ka 'od kyi gong bu sgra yis 'pho //
NK113(e)001:2002: rtsa yi 'gros thim bskyed rim sprul pa'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2003: mkha' khyab sku yi rdo rje 'dus ma byas //
NK113(e)001:2004: b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor la brten gsang dbang bskur //
NK113(e)001:2005: dgod pas tshim la 'phrul dag'i 'dod chags dang //
NK113(e)001:2006: ngag gi sgrib sbyangs bdag byin sloob pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:2007: gtum mos gzung 'dzin ro rkyang dbu mar 'dzud //
NK113(e)001:2008: rang byung ye shes grub mtha' ma 'dres rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2009: 'da' ka dpe yi 'od gsal chen po'i ngang //
NK113(e)001:2010: yi ge'i 'gros thim longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2011: yan lag drug cur rdzogs pa'i gsung rdo rje //
NK113(e)001:2012: gdan gsum mngon rtogs ngom pa'i mdzes ma yi //
NK113(e)001:2013: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten sher dbang gis //
NK113(e)001:2014: lag bcangs tshim pa dga' ldan 'dod chags dag /
NK113(e)001:2015: yid kyi sgrib sbyangs snang mched thob gsum dang //
NK113(e)001:2016: dga' bzhi'i ye shes khams kyi zhu bdes 'grub //
NK113(e)001:2017: grub mtha' bde stong dbyer med nyams su myong //
NK113(e)001:2018: 'da' ka der snang ma grub rdo rje sems //
NK113(e)001:2019: snying ga'i rtsa mdud grol ba dpe'i ye shes //
NK113(e)001:2020: mkha' khyab thugs kyi rdo rje dwangs ma'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2021: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas //
NK113(e)001:2022: gsum pa'i nyams myong tshig gis mtshon pa'i dbang //
NK113(e)001:2023: 'thab bral man chod 'khyud sbyor 'dod chags dang //
NK113(e)001:2024: sgo gsum sgrib dag tha dad 'dzin pa sbyong //
NK113(e)001:2025: stong pa'i thig le rig pa'i snying po can //
NK113(e)001:2026: grub mtha' bsam mi khyab pa'i ye shes te //
NK113(e)001:2027: 'da' ka gsang chen phyag rgya chen po la //
NK113(e)001:2028: 'bras bu mkha' khyab ngo bo nyid sku'o //
NK113(e)001:2029: sgra don sbyar na a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgras //
NK113(e)001:2030: glo bur dri ma gtor dang she ka tas //
NK113(e)001:2031: skal ba blugs pa rnam pa gnyis su grub //
NK113(e)001:2032: dbang mchog rang la gnas pa khams drug gi //
NK113(e)001:2033: rten dang 'byor pa rgyu yi dbang yin te //
NK113(e)001:2034: slob dpon nyid kyi cho gas bskur ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2035: rang gi dmigs pas 'dris pa lam gyi dbang //
NK113(e)001:2036: rgyu dus 'od zer chen po'i dbang bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:2037: rang sems sku bzhir smin pa 'bras bu'i dbang //
NK113(e)001:2038: dbang bzhi rdzogs tshe rig 'dzin sdom pa thob //
NK113(e)001:2039: dbang thob skyes bu tha ba'i skyon sbyangs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2040: zhing sar sa bon bzhag pa ji bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:2041: sgrib pa bzhi dag sku bzhi mngon du byed //
NK113(e)001:2042: gnyis par lam la bskyed rdzogs rnam gnyis las //
NK113(e)001:2043: dang po bskyed rim skye gnas rnam pa bzhi'i //
NK113(e)001:2044: bag chags sbyong phyir de dang mthun par ston //
NK113(e)001:2045: bskyed tshul 'khor ba'i rnam pa dang mthun pas //
NK113(e)001:2046: srid pa gsum po ma lus sbyong zhing dag /
NK113(e)001:2047: mya ngan 'das dang bzhugs tshul mthun pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2048: lha yi rnam pas 'bras bu gzhi la rdzogas //
NK113(e)001:2049: gnyis ka'ang rdzogs pa'i rim pa smin byed du //
NK113(e)001:2050: 'gro ba'i dag rdzogs smin gsum spyi la gces //
NK113(e)001:2051: ji ltar sgong skyes lan gnyis skye ba ltar //
NK113(e)001:2052: bdag sras gzhan sras rnam pa gnyis su bskyed //
NK113(e)001:2053: bdag gi sras su gzhan bya ba la lnga //
NK113(e)001:2054: sa bon las ni gtso bo bskyed pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2055: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bkug nas mkhar bstim dang //
NK113(e)001:2056: sems can bkug nas sgrib pa sbyang ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2057: gnyis su med la che ba bskyed pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2058: mkha' nas bton nas gdan la dgod pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2059: gzhan gyi sras su bdag bya ba la brgyad //
NK113(e)001:2060: sgo nga smin pa de dang der gyur bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2061: gtso bo 'od zhu sa bon gyur pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2062: de las yab yum skye mched rdzogs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2063: yab kyi rtog pa yi ger gyur pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2064: yum las 'od 'phros lha la gsol gdab dang //
NK113(e)001:2065: kun kyang rang bstim nga rgyal bzung ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2066: snyoms par zhugs nas mkha' ru dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NK113(e)001:2067: rtog pa zhe gnyis lhar gsal phyir gdon dang //
NK113(e)001:2068: phyag rgya zhi yis bcings dang rgyas gdab bo //
NK113(e)001:2069: bsdu na thog mar rang nyid lhar gsal bas //
NK113(e)001:2070: mdun mkhar dkyil 'khor gsal btab rgyun bshags bya //
NK113(e)001:2071: gnyis ka mi dmigs ngang nas lha so so'i //
NK113(e)001:2072: dkyil 'khor mngon rtogs ji bzhin sgom pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2073: mngal skyes sbyong phyir mngon byang bzhi'am lnga //
NK113(e)001:2074: dang po khrag 'thung gal po'i dgongs pa ste //
NK113(e)001:2075: 'chi srid bar dor bcas pa stong nyid sems //
NK113(e)001:2076: dri za nye bar len pa'i rnam shes ni //
NK113(e)001:2077: lha yi sa bon gyis sbyong de nyid kyang //
NK113(e)001:2078: khu rdul rlung dang 'dres pa'i mer mer nur //
NK113(e)001:2079: sa bon nyid las phyag mtshan gyur pas sbyong //
NK113(e)001:2080: ltar dang mkhrang gyur phyag mtshan 'od gong gyur //
NK113(e)001:2081: khyab 'jug nya dang rus sbal dbang po rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2082: lha yi rnam par gyur nas sbyong ba'o //
NK113(e)001:2083: phyag rgya sku la yig 'bru gsum rdo rje //
NK113(e)001:2084: thugs ni phyag mtshan nyid du sbyor ba la //
NK113(e)001:2085: rdo rje'i cho ga gsum zhes pha rgyud lugs //
NK113(e)001:2086: bar ma do nas lus 'tshol tshogs kyi lam //
NK113(e)001:2087: mngal du rnam shes 'jug pa sbyor lam ste //
NK113(e)001:2088: lhum zhugs byang chub lnga po mthong sgom dang //
NK113(e)001:2089: zla ba bcu ni sa dang rab sbyar nas //
NK113(e)001:2090: btsal ba mi slob lam gyur sprul pa'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2091: mngon byang dang po zla ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK113(e)001:2092: mngal skyes khu ba drod gsher skyes kyi gsher //
NK113(e)001:2093: sgong skyes pha dang rdzus skyes stong pa'i cha //
NK113(e)001:2094: de bzhin gnyis pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor yang //
NK113(e)001:2095: mngal skyes rdul dang drod gsher skyes kyi drod //
NK113(e)001:2096: sgong skyes ma dang rdzus skyes gsal ba'i cha //
NK113(e)001:2097: mngon byang gsum pa sa bon phyag mtshan bcas //
NK113(e)001:2098: khu rdul gnyis par rnam shes zhugs pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2099: skye gnas bzhi po'i bar do'i rnam shes sbyong //
NK113(e)001:2100: mngon byang bzhi pa rnam gsum gcig tu 'dres //
NK113(e)001:2101: khu rdul sems gsum ro gcig 'dres pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2102: drod gsher skyes kyi drod dang rnam shes dang //
NK113(e)001:2103: rdzus skyes gsal la stong ba'i cha tsam dang //
NK113(e)001:2104: bar srid 'dres pa'i cha rnams sbyong ba yin //
NK113(e)001:2105: mngon byang lnga pa sku ru grub pa ni //
NK113(e)001:2106: skye gnas bzhi po'i skye mched yongs rdzogs nas //
NK113(e)001:2107: reg pa'i yul la dbang po sad pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2108: 'khor ba'i rnam pa cha dang bcas pa sbyong //
NK113(e)001:2109: khams dang phung po rnam par shes pa'i tshogs //
NK113(e)001:2110: gnas su dag pa gdan gsum tshang ba'i lha //
NK113(e)001:2111: mya ngan 'das dang bzhugs tshul mthun pa ni //
NK113(e)001:2112: rgyu las 'bras bu'i he ru ka nyid do //
NK113(e)001:2113: khu rdul rlung gsum sems dang bcas pa'i cha //
NK113(e)001:2114: rnam par dag pas rdzogs rim smin byed 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:2115: drod gsher skyes ni gnyis po 'dus pa la //
NK113(e)001:2116: rnam shes zhugs pas mod la gzugs grub bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2117: lha yi mtshan dang mngon rtogs dran tsam la //
NK113(e)001:2118: phyag rgya rdzogs pa'i bskyed rim tshang bar sgom //
NK113(e)001:2119: rdzus te skye ba skad cig dran rdzogs te //
NK113(e)001:2120: ming dang gzugs la ma brten wal gyi gsal //
NK113(e)001:2121: sgom tshul bzhi po'ang dang po'i las can la //
NK113(e)001:2122: sgong skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim gtso bor sgom //
NK113(e)001:2123: rim bzhin gom pa brtan dang brtan pa che //
NK113(e)001:2124: shin tu brtan pa'i mthu dang mthun par slob //
NK113(e)001:2125: kun kyang de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin //
NK113(e)001:2126: spros pa kun dang bral ba'i shes rab gdangs //
NK113(e)001:2127: kun snang snying rje'i 'phen pas bskyed rim du //
NK113(e)001:2128: shar ba thabs kyi lam mchog ma nor zhing //
NK113(e)001:2129: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin ma grub pa //
NK113(e)001:2130: zab mo snang stong thabs shes 'brel ba'i lam //
NK113(e)001:2131: de las 'gal ba'i dmigs bcas bskyed rim ni //
NK113(e)001:2132: mu stegs byed dang gdon gyi rigs la'ang yod //
NK113(e)001:2133: sngags su byang chub sems dpa'i mthong lam la //
NK113(e)001:2134: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub ces //
NK113(e)001:2135: shin tu grags pa mngon du byed pa'i thabs //
NK113(e)001:2136: snang cha lha skur gsal ba bsod nams tshogs //
NK113(e)001:2137: de la rang bzhin ma grub ye shes te //
NK113(e)001:2138: tshogs gnyis nye rgyur bsten pa'i dbang rnon dang //
NK113(e)001:2139: lam lngar 'brel ba rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'i //
NK113(e)001:2140: them skas nyid las nges pa lnga ldan sogs //
NK113(e)001:2141: sku lnga'i zhing du mig 'phrul lta bur 'gro //
NK113(e)001:2142: gnyis pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa nyid la'ang //
NK113(e)001:2143: pha rgyud rnams las 'byung ba lnga yi rlung //
NK113(e)001:2144: rnam par dag pas gsal stong ye shes bskyed //
NK113(e)001:2145: ma rgyud rnams las khams la zhu bde yi //
NK113(e)001:2146: ye shes bskyed phyir rang lus thabs ldan dang //
NK113(e)001:2147: gzhan lus la brten dga' bzhi'i ye shes bskyed //
NK113(e)001:2148: gnyis med rgyud las gcig dang du bral gyi //
NK113(e)001:2149: thig le chen po'i 'od gsal gtsor byed las //
NK113(e)001:2150: snga ma gnyis ni snang bcas dmigs pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:2151: phyi ma gcig ni snang med 'od gsal te //
NK113(e)001:2152: dang po'i phyogs la gnas pa rtsa dang ni //
NK113(e)001:2153: g.yo ba rlung la bkod pa byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:2154: gsum du gnas pa rdo rje phung po'i grong //
NK113(e)001:2155: mi yi mngal gnas 'dzin pa'i thog ma ru //
NK113(e)001:2156: mig gnyis dang ni lte ba'i rtsa mdud chags //
NK113(e)001:2157: de las lus bskyed dwangs mar gyur pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2158: rtsa gsum ka ba lta bur gnas pa'i nang //
NK113(e)001:2159: phyi ru lus ngag nang du nyon mongs gsum //
NK113(e)001:2160: gsang bar sku gsung thugs kyi rten byed pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2161: yi ge gsum gnas dbu ma'i yas mar sna //
NK113(e)001:2162: tshangs pa'i sgo dang gsang gnas gnyis la zug /
NK113(e)001:2163: g.yas g.yon ro rkyang dkar dang dmar ba nyid //
NK113(e)001:2164: bud med nyid la ldog pas rkyang ma g.yas //
NK113(e)001:2165: dbu ma sngo skyar gnyis pos lug rgyud du //
NK113(e)001:2166: mdud pa nyi shu rtsa gcig byas pa la //
NK113(e)001:2167: rim bzhin sku gsung thugs sam sku bzhi lnga //
NK113(e)001:2168: phyin drug grangs kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab rnams //
NK113(e)001:2169: phri bsnan gyur pa sbyang gzhi sbyong byed tshul //
NK113(e)001:2170: lte bar drug cu rtsa bzhi mgrin pa la //
NK113(e)001:2171: brgyad tshan gnyis dang snying gar rtsa 'dab brgyad //
NK113(e)001:2172: spyi bor sum cu rtsa gnyis bde skyong na //
NK113(e)001:2173: bdun cu rtsa gnyis de bzhin gtsug tor la //
NK113(e)001:2174: nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lo zhes su grags //
NK113(e)001:2175: 'khor lo re dang so so'i bar mtshams su //
NK113(e)001:2176: 'pho ba bcu gnyis rlung gi dus sbyor dang //
NK113(e)001:2177: de bzhin rten zhing 'brel 'byung bcu gnyis gnas //
NK113(e)001:2178: khams la 'pho ba spangs pa'i lugs ldog 'gros //
NK113(e)001:2179: gsang gnas ye shes 'khor lor phyin pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2180: rlung gi 'pho ba gcig dang rten 'brel gcig /'gags nas dang po'i sa yi rtogs pa 'char //
NK113(e)001:2181: rim bzhin nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lo'i bar //
NK113(e)001:2182: rlung dang rten 'brel re re'i cha ldog pas //
NK113(e)001:2183: sa ni bcu gnyis rab tu rdzogs pa'i mthar //
NK113(e)001:2184: thig le nam mkha'i khams dang 'dres pa'i tshe //
NK113(e)001:2185: mngon par 'tshang rgya dang po'i sangs rgyas lugs //
NK113(e)001:2186: de dang rnam grangs mthun pa'i rtsa 'dab la //
NK113(e)001:2187: sbyang gzhir gnas pa'i rigs drug sa bon rnams //
NK113(e)001:2188: sbyong byed rig pa'i skyes bu rnam drug dang //
NK113(e)001:2189: pha rol phyin pa drug gis sbyangs pa las //
NK113(e)001:2190: tha dad pa yi ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK113(e)001:2191: bsam gyis mi khyab gcig dang drug 'thob bo //
NK113(e)001:2192: de bzhin snying ga zhi ba'i 'khor lo dang //
NK113(e)001:2193: spyi gtsug khro bo'i 'khor lo rnam gnyis la //
NK113(e)001:2194: lha dang rnam grangs mnyam pa'i rtsa 'dab dang //
NK113(e)001:2195: thabs grol steng 'og lam gyi sgo gnyis su //
NK113(e)001:2196: 'dod pa rgyud kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrul lugs //
NK113(e)001:2197: g.yo ba rlung la 'gyur ba che chung gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2198: che ba nyin zhag phrugs gcig dag la ni //
NK113(e)001:2199: nyi khri chig stong drug brgya'i grangs su 'gyu //
NK113(e)001:2200: chung ba kun rtog brgyad khri bzhi stong gi //
NK113(e)001:2201: grangs dang mnyam pa'i bzhon pa lta bur gnas //
NK113(e)001:2202: rtsa ba'i rlung ni srog 'dzin me mnyam dang //
NK113(e)001:2203: khyab byed gyen rgyu thur sel lngar gnas pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2204: byed las rim bzhin srog brten me drod bskyed //
NK113(e)001:2205: lus nyams brtas dang dbugs kyi 'gro 'ong dang //
NK113(e)001:2206: 'gro 'dug gshang gci 'phen pa'i bya ba byed //
NK113(e)001:2207: de'ang pho rlung gyen rgyu stod na gnas //
NK113(e)001:2208: mo rlung thur sel smad dang ma ning mnyam //
NK113(e)001:2209: nang gi rlung gi 'byung lnga'i kha dog can //
NK113(e)001:2210: phung po khams dang skye mched gnas pa'i rten //
NK113(e)001:2211: dug lnga dang ni ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK113(e)001:2212: rgyu 'bras lta bur mched pa'i rten byed do //
NK113(e)001:2213: khyad par dwangs ma'i rlung lnga d+hu tir chud //
NK113(e)001:2214: zad par sa chu me rlung nam mkha' yi //
NK113(e)001:2215: ting nge 'dzin dang yon tan rdzu 'phrul 'grub //
NK113(e)001:2216: gsang ba'i rlung ni ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK113(e)001:2217: rags pa'i chos dang rnam par 'gal ba yin //
NK113(e)001:2218: gsum pa bkod pa byang chub sems kyi khams //
NK113(e)001:2219: ro ma las ni zla ba'i bdud rtsi dang //
NK113(e)001:2220: brkyang ma las ni nyi ma'i rdul 'ba' cing //
NK113(e)001:2221: pho yi rkyang ma mo yi ro ma'i sna //
NK113(e)001:2222: mdud par gyur pas khams gnyis 'dzag pa bsrung //
NK113(e)001:2223: de las gzhan du gnyis pa las mched pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2224: rtsa mdud kun na dwangs ma dkar dmar gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2225: dpa' bo dang ni rnal 'byor ma'i tshul du //
NK113(e)001:2226: 'khril zhing sbyor bas bde stong mchod pa len //
NK113(e)001:2227: mdor na gnas pa rtsa ni yur ba 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2228: g.yo ba rlung ni 'gro 'ong kha lo pa //
NK113(e)001:2229: byang chub sems ni chu 'dra khrid sar 'du //
NK113(e)001:2230: 'khor lo drug tu brtsegs pa'i sgra gcan dbyings //
NK113(e)001:2231: srog dang rtsol ba'i shing rtas drangs pa las //
NK113(e)001:2232: dbu ma'i mdud pa gnyis gnyis grol ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2233: rlung dang khams kyi dwangs ma rnam gnyis re //
NK113(e)001:2234: sgra gcan ltor zhugs dang po'i sa nas bzung //
NK113(e)001:2235: sa bcu'i yon tan gong 'phel gtsug tor 'gro //
NK113(e)001:2236: khyad par sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang thig lugs //
NK113(e)001:2237: snod bcud rang la rdzogs pa phung po'i grong //
NK113(e)001:2238: dus gsum lung du ma bstan bde gshegs snying //
NK113(e)001:2239: mtha' dag mngon 'tshang rgya ba rdo rje'i gdan //
NK113(e)001:2240: snying kha dpal gyi be'u'i khong seng na //
NK113(e)001:2241: rtsa yi dwangs ma brgyad du gnas pa las //
NK113(e)001:2242: dbus ma gsum ni sku gsum chos nyid rten //
NK113(e)001:2243: mdun ma gcig ni ye shes 'char ba'i rtsa //
NK113(e)001:2244: rgyab na yon tan rtsa las zhing khams 'char //
NK113(e)001:2245: g.yon na rang rgyud rtsa gsum 'khrul snang rten //
NK113(e)001:2246: so so'i dbus na 'khor 'das yig 'bru ni //
NK113(e)001:2247: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed tshul du gnas pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:2248: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ges dag par byed //
NK113(e)001:2249: kun gyi dbus na dwangs ma'i rtsa dkar po //
NK113(e)001:2250: rta rnga'i bcu cha tsam du phra ba'i nang //
NK113(e)001:2251: rdul dang dbugs kyi dwangs ma 'dres pa'i 'od //
NK113(e)001:2252: kha dog lnga pa shin tu phra ba nyid //
NK113(e)001:2253: rang bzhin 'od gsal byang chub sems kyi rten //
NK113(e)001:2254: kun bzang rigs lnga bzhugs pa'i gzhal med khang //
NK113(e)001:2255: gang du rlung sems dwangs ma 'das pa'i tshe //
NK113(e)001:2256: mya ngan 'das pa'i zhing snang mtha' dag 'char //
NK113(e)001:2257: snang cha'i 'od lnga stong cha'i chos sku gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2258: ro gcig 'dres pas lam gyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2259: 'og min rnam dag stug po bkod pa zhes //
NK113(e)001:2260: gzhan du mi gnas sgrib pa mtha' dag pa //
NK113(e)001:2261: nam zhig spangs pa'i dus der lhun gyis grub //
NK113(e)001:2262: de phyir lus ni ye shes chen po'i rten //
NK113(e)001:2263: 'khor ba nyid na'ang ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul la //
NK113(e)001:2264: nyams dang dman par gyur pa gnyis ka med //
NK113(e)001:2265: 'gyur ba med pa'i don dam byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:2266: til la mar gyi khyab pa ji bzhin no //
NK113(e)001:2267: de ltar rdo rje lus kyi gnas lugs dang //
NK113(e)001:2268: gdod ma gzhi yi bzhugs tshul shes byas nas //
NK113(e)001:2269: gtum mo dang ni sgyu lus nying 'khrul lam //
NK113(e)001:2270: 'od gsal bar do 'pho ba rnam pa drug /
NK113(e)001:2271: skyes bu'i rtsol bas 'grub kyis gzhan rkyen la //
NK113(e)001:2272: rag ma lus phyir rang lus thabs kyi lam //
NK113(e)001:2273: rtsa thig rlung la gnad du song nas slar //
NK113(e)001:2274: bde stong lam du byed pa gzhan lus te //
NK113(e)001:2275: kun kyang lam du 'gro ba thabs kyi lam //
NK113(e)001:2276: gnyis pa snang ba med pa'i rdzogs rim ni //
NK113(e)001:2277: rnam par gyur pa'i bskyed rdzogs gang yin yang //
NK113(e)001:2278: dag pa'i snod bcud brtan g.yor snang ba kun //
NK113(e)001:2279: 'od du zhu nas snying ga'i sa bon rnams //
NK113(e)001:2280: thig ler thim pa de yang mas rim nas //
NK113(e)001:2281: stong bar gyur pa nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK113(e)001:2282: ye shes chen po'i spyod yul nyid la bzhag /
NK113(e)001:2283: bskyed rim gyis ni snang ba'i bden zhen 'gog /
NK113(e)001:2284: rdzogs rim gyis ni sgyu ma'i zhen rtog spong //
NK113(e)001:2285: bde gsal mi rtog lhan skyes ye shes 'char //
NK113(e)001:2286: zab pa'i rdzogs rim bla na med pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:2287: bla med rgyud las 'og mar gsungs pa med //
NK113(e)001:2288: dbang rnon tshe gcig rdo rje 'chang 'gro ba'i //
NK113(e)001:2289: nye lam sbas pa shin tu zab mo yin //
NK113(e)001:2290: gsum pa mthun pa'i grogs gyur dam tshig ni //
NK113(e)001:2291: sngags la zhugs pa'i brtul zhugs mi nyams bsrung //
NK113(e)001:2292: thabs dang gnyen po'i rten 'brel mi 'chol ba //
NK113(e)001:2293: rma bya'i mgrin par btsan dug zhugs ltar spyad //
NK113(e)001:2294: de la dam tshig dang ni sdom pa'i khyad //
NK113(e)001:2295: dam tshig 'da' bar bya ba ma yin la //
NK113(e)001:2296: sdom pa bya dang mi bya'i nges pa ste //
NK113(e)001:2297: ngo bo gcig la ldog chas dbye ba'o //
NK113(e)001:2298: kun gyi spyi don sngags sdom ma thob dang //
NK113(e)001:2299: smyo ba la sogs 'du shes rang bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:2300: mi gnas pa la ltung dang dngos grub med //
NK113(e)001:2301: sngags sdom ldan zhing ma nyams ma btang la //
NK113(e)001:2302: shes pa rang bzhin rnal du gnas pa de //
NK113(e)001:2303: ltung ba dang ni dngos grub gnyis ka'i snod //
NK113(e)001:2304: byang chub sems las gzhan pa'i rtsa ltung la //
NK113(e)001:2305: kun dkris zhes bya da dung bya ba de //
NK113(e)001:2306: byed 'dod ma log de la 'gyod pa med //
NK113(e)001:2307: rang ngor ltos pa'i ngo tsha shes pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2308: gzhan ngor ltos pa'i khrel yod med pa ste //
NK113(e)001:2309: chos gsum tshang ba'i kun slong bya ba'i mthar //
NK113(e)001:2310: gtugs pa de srid rgyun chags yod gyur na //
NK113(e)001:2311: kun dkris tshang ba'i pham par gyur pa yin //
NK113(e)001:2312: dus kyi bar chad rgyun chags med pa'am //
NK113(e)001:2313: chos gsum gang las cig shos ma tshang na //
NK113(e)001:2314: bya ba'i yan lag ma tshogs sbom por 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:2315: de yis shes byas rtsa ba yan lag kun //
NK113(e)001:2316: yid kyis mi spong lus kyis dor mi bya //
NK113(e)001:2317: nyin dang mtshan mo cha drug bgos pa la //
NK113(e)001:2318: cha re'i nang du rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po'i //
NK113(e)001:2319: nyes pa byung ngam ma byung sngo bgrang bya //
NK113(e)001:2320: gos na 'gyod pa bskyed cing phyir 'chos sems //
NK113(e)001:2321: gos pa min na dga' ba sgom zhing bsngo //
NK113(e)001:2322: sngon chad gos sam ma gos gang yin kyang //
NK113(e)001:2323: phyin chad srog la bab kyang nyes byas kyi //
NK113(e)001:2324: gos par mi bya'i sdom sems shin tu bsten //
NK113(e)001:2325: gang tshe cha drug gang yang rung ba'i nang //
NK113(e)001:2326: sngo bgrang byed pa'i 'du shes rmongs gyur na //
NK113(e)001:2327: kha na ma tho sbom po zhes pa 'byung //
NK113(e)001:2328: drug ka 'das na sbom po drug tu 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:2329: zhag de'i khong du phyir bcos ma grub na //
NK113(e)001:2330: phyi ma'i skya rengs dang po 'char ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2331: sbom po bcu gnyis dag tu 'gyur bar bshad //
NK113(e)001:2332: yan lag dam tshig la'ang de yis 'gre //
NK113(e)001:2333: thog mar bla med spyi la gces pa'i chings //
NK113(e)001:2334: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i rab dbye 'di ltar brtag /
NK113(e)001:2335: dang po dbang thob slob dpon smos ci dgos //
NK113(e)001:2336: sngags rgyud tshigs bcad gcig pa yan chad bkral //
NK113(e)001:2337: lam gyi man ngag zab mo ston gsum la //
NK113(e)001:2338: chos kyi 'brel ba'i bsnyen bkur khur bor brnyas //
NK113(e)001:2339: de la sngags kyi dngos grub yod ma yin //
NK113(e)001:2340: gnyis pa sdom pa gsum dang bslab pa'i gnas //
NK113(e)001:2341: bde bar gshegs pa'i gnang bkag mtshams las 'das //
NK113(e)001:2342: de bzhin mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla ma yi //
NK113(e)001:2343: yul dus la dgongs bka' la khyad bsad yin //
NK113(e)001:2344: gsum pa dbang gral gcig tu 'dres pa'i mched //
NK113(e)001:2345: bskur zhing brnyas byas dmigs kyis bsal na'ang //
NK113(e)001:2346: mtha' yas sems can bde gshegs snying po'i spun //
NK113(e)001:2347: yin phyir ring dang nye ba'i mched la'ang mtshungs //
NK113(e)001:2348: bzhi pa sbyor ba rtsub pa'i sems can zhig /
NK113(e)001:2349: mthong ba'i chos la las kyi mnar gyur pa //
NK113(e)001:2350: de la dga' ba bsgoms nas byams pa'i sems //
NK113(e)001:2351: gtong ba byang chub sems dpar rab lci na /
NK113(e)001:2352: gzhan bde bral bar 'dod la smos ci dgos //
NK113(e)001:2353: lnga pa gzhan don gnyer ba'i byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:2354: spangs pa'i mod la smon sems gtong ba'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:2355: kun dkris tshang ba'i pha ma par gyur pa yin //
NK113(e)001:2356: gnang ba'i skabs bdun min par khu ba phyung //
NK113(e)001:2357: drug pa theg pa gsum ltos rgyal ba'i bka' //
NK113(e)001:2358: dpyas shing ston pas ma gsungs zhes smra dang //
NK113(e)001:2359: las dang dngos grub rgyur rung bstan bcos gzhan //
NK113(e)001:2360: rjes gnang byin brlabs bka' ru ma bltas brnyas //
NK113(e)001:2361: bdun pa dbang gi cho ga ma byas dang //
NK113(e)001:2362: ma rdzogs nyams dang snod ngan zab mos skrag /'dul ba'i dus skabs gnas kyi bskal pa la //
NK113(e)001:2363: gsang sngags zab mo'i don dang dgongs spyod bsgrags //
NK113(e)001:2364: dmigs bsal yin gyi rjes gnang bzlas lung yang //
NK113(e)001:2365: gsang sgrog ngos 'dzin 'dir ni snod la brtag /
NK113(e)001:2366: brgyad pa gzugs phung rnam snang la sogs lnga //
NK113(e)001:2367: de bzhin skye mched lha skur mi shes par //
NK113(e)001:2368: sdug bsngal bden par bsgrub pa'i rtog ge'i blos //
NK113(e)001:2369: brnyan dang dka' thub mthu yis lhag par gdung //
NK113(e)001:2370: dgu pa rang bzhin dag pa'i stong nyid don //
NK113(e)001:2371: sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul nyid las gzhan //
NK113(e)001:2372: sems can khams dang 'brel ba ldem dgongs su //
NK113(e)001:2373: the tshom zos nas bkri bar spangs pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2374: bcu pa dkon mchog gsum dang bla ma smod //
NK113(e)001:2375: bstan pa 'jig sogs drag shul cho ga yis //
NK113(e)001:2376: mngon du spyod pa'i yul la sran cing bzod //
NK113(e)001:2377: 'dris shing bshes nas byams par byas pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2378: bcu gcig ming bral chos la tshad mas gzhal //
NK113(e)001:2379: chos kyi bdag med blo dang rdzas 'gal bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2380: phung sogs stong par blta ba mchog 'dzin blos //
NK113(e)001:2381: skye med grub mtha' rtog pas 'jal ba'o //
NK113(e)001:2382: bcu gnyis sngags kyi snod rung gdul bya'am //
NK113(e)001:2383: dad gsum ldan la don gnyer chos mi ston //
NK113(e)001:2384: kun slong ngan pas gzhan sems sun phyung nas //
NK113(e)001:2385: 'dun pa phyin ci log tu skyogs pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2386: bcu gsum spyad bya'i dam rdzas rang rgyud du //
NK113(e)001:2387: bltas nas la la spong zhing la la sred //
NK113(e)001:2388: sngags kyi brtul zhugs ji bzhin nyams 'og tu //
NK113(e)001:2389: ma chud mtha' gnyis mal du 'khyams pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2390: bcu bzhi rnal 'byor ma sogs 'jig rten 'das //
NK113(e)001:2391: ma mo mkha' 'gro la sogs so mtshams 'dzin //
NK113(e)001:2392: 'byung ba lnga yi khams la rang brgyud bltas //
NK113(e)001:2393: dbang gi rten gyur bud med smod pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2394: bcu bzhi'i yan lag sdom pa gtong byad kyi //
NK113(e)001:2395: pham pa min yang dngos grub thob pa la //
NK113(e)001:2396: gegs su che ba'i sbom po brgyad yod de //
NK113(e)001:2397: dbang dang dam tshig sdom pas ma sbyangs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2398: tha mal bud med rig mar bsten pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2399: mtshan nyid 'gal ba'i dran pa'i khron pa nas //
NK113(e)001:2400: cho ga ma yin bzhin pas bdud rtsi len //
NK113(e)001:2401: dbang ma thob dang lhag par dad med la //
NK113(e)001:2402: sku gzugs glengs bam phyag mtshan phyag rgya ston //
NK113(e)001:2403: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus na 'thab rtsod dang //
NK113(e)001:2404: bab col kyal kas brtul zhugs tha mal sbyar //
NK113(e)001:2405: snod ldan dam chos 'dri la shes bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:2406: de las 'gal ba'i bsnyon dor lan du ldon //
NK113(e)001:2407: sngags kyi lta spyod skur zhing nyams sad pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2408: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad //
NK113(e)001:2409: sngags rgyud de nyid cho ga mi shes bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2410: rdo rje 'dzin par nga rgyal rdzun dang 'grogs //
NK113(e)001:2411: dbang bskur thob kyang sngags la mi dad pa'i /
NK113(e)001:2412: the tshom can la slar yang gsang ba 'chad //
NK113(e)001:2413: klu sgrub kyis bsdus de bzhin dpa' bo dang /
NK113(e)001:2414: lak+shim k+aa ras de las don gzhan pa //
NK113(e)001:2415: bsnyen pa dag par ma byas dbang bskur dang //
NK113(e)001:2416: rab gnas sbyin bsreg slob ma bsdu bar rings //
NK113(e)001:2417: tshogs 'khor las gzhan phyi dro'i kha zas sogs //
NK113(e)001:2418: so byang bcas pa dgos med 'da' ba yis //
NK113(e)001:2419: bdag nyid sun 'byin dngos grub 'phrog pa'i rgyur //
NK113(e)001:2420: gsungs pa'i sbom po rnams la'ang brtag par bya //
NK113(e)001:2421: 'di ltar rnal 'byor bla med thun mong gi //
NK113(e)001:2422: rtsa ltung bcu bzhir b+ha wi lhas bsdus pa //
NK113(e)001:2423: kun la khyab cing yongs su grags pa ste //
NK113(e)001:2424: gzhan du rgyud sde bzhi po'i rang lugs kyi //
NK113(e)001:2425: bcu bzhi'i grangs nges dus kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK113(e)001:2426: spyi rgyud mngon byang sogs las gsal por gsungs //
NK113(e)001:2427: rnal 'byor ldan pa 'achi'am srog gtong sla //
NK113(e)001:2428: rtag tu dam tshig bsrung bar ma byas na //
NK113(e)001:2429: sngags la spyod pa'i skyes bu ngan song dang //
NK113(e)001:2430: sangs rgyas gnyis las 'gro sa gsum pa med //
NK113(e)001:2431: de phyir ltung na bdag nyid sun phyung nas //
NK113(e)001:2432: phyir bcos thabs la de ma thag tu 'bad //
NK113(e)001:2433: khyad par rtsa ltung dang po shin tu lci //
NK113(e)001:2434: bla mar bsnyen bkur 'khor gsum yongs dag 'bul //
NK113(e)001:2435: dbang bskur bskyar nas sdom pa gsor gzhug cing //
NK113(e)001:2436: nye bar mi gnas bdag 'jug lan mang blang //
NK113(e)001:2437: de bzhin gzhan la khrel yod ngo tsha'i rten //
NK113(e)001:2438: bla ma med na sngags kyi sdom ldan mdun //
NK113(e)001:2439: phyag dang spyod lam dul bas rang gi ming //
NK113(e)001:2440: smos nas rdo rje theg pa'i 'dul ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2441: 'gal ba'i nongs pa 'di dang 'di byung bas //
NK113(e)001:2442: 'chab na bdag nyid bde bar gnas mi 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:2443: 'chab med legs par gsol nas bshags yul gyis //
NK113(e)001:2444: nyes par mthong ngam rang gis mthong lags brjod //
NK113(e)001:2445: yul gyi phyin chad sdom par byed dam dri //
NK113(e)001:2446: chos bzhin 'dul ba bzhin du spyi bos nod //
NK113(e)001:2447: ces pa lan gsum brjod la thabs legs bya //
NK113(e)001:2448: gal te phyir bcos 'gyangs na zhag re bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2449: gong 'phel 'gro 'gyur de yi gnyen po ru //
NK113(e)001:2450: stobs bzhi tshang ba'i yig brgyas rtag tu bshags //
NK113(e)001:2451: bcu bzhi'i sngo bgrang brjod pa'i bshags tshig gdon //
NK113(e)001:2452: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum ring lugs ni //
NK113(e)001:2453: spyi mdor sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK113(e)001:2454: bsrung dang spyad dang yid 'ong mi 'dor dang //
NK113(e)001:2455: shes bya bsgrub pa'i dbye bas nyi shu brgyad //
NK113(e)001:2456: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga dang //
NK113(e)001:2457: yan lag bcur bshad rtsa ba'i phyogs la ni //
NK113(e)001:2458: rdo rje slob dpon mi spong bkur stis bsnyen //
NK113(e)001:2459: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2460: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams par byed //
NK113(e)001:2461: gsang ba'i don rnams gzhan mi bsgrag pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2462: yan lag dam tshig sde tshan gnyis su bsdu //
NK113(e)001:2463: dang po'i phyogs ni nyon mongs lnga mi spang //
NK113(e)001:2464: rang bzhin shes pa'i nyon mongs de bzhin nyid //
NK113(e)001:2465: thabs kyis zin pa rma byas dug zos 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2466: ye nas rigs lngar shes pas ye shes 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:2467: gnyis pa'i phyogs ni bdud rtsi chen po lnga //
NK113(e)001:2468: blang byar nges pa chos nyid rol par blang //
NK113(e)001:2469: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin nyid du shes par blang //
NK113(e)001:2470: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i dam rdzas yin pas blang //
NK113(e)001:2471: mkha' 'gro 'du zhing dngos grub nye bas blang //
NK113(e)001:2472: sangs rgyas kun gyi brtul zhugs yin pas blang //
NK113(e)001:2473: cha shas dbye ba nyis brgya'i grangs nges ni //
NK113(e)001:2474: nyi shur bsdu ba kun gzigs rong pa'i lugs //
NK113(e)001:2475: sems kyi phyogs la med dang gcig pu dang //
NK113(e)001:2476: phyal ba dang ni lhun grub ces grags pa //
NK113(e)001:2477: bsrung mtshams bral la 'da' bya mi dmigs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2478: ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul dam tshig chings kyis bcings //
NK113(e)001:2479: ye nas nyams med rdo rje rgyal po'i lugs //
NK113(e)001:2480: lam zhugs rnams kyi rang rgyud dag bya'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:2481: nyams na phyir bcos rin chen bum pa bzang //
NK113(e)001:2482: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa'i grub mtha' ni //
NK113(e)001:2483: rtsa ba bla ma'i sku gsung thugs gsum la //
NK113(e)001:2484: phyi nang gsang ba'i dam tshig gsum tshan gsum //
NK113(e)001:2485: srog gcod mi tshangs spyod dang brku ba spang //
NK113(e)001:2486: pha ma spun sring rang lus chos gang smod //
NK113(e)001:2487: bla ma'i grib 'gong yum gtse spun sring brdeg /
NK113(e)001:2488: gsung gi gsum la rdzun phra tshig rtsub spang //
NK113(e)001:2489: chos smra don sems gnas lugs sgom mi bkur //
NK113(e)001:2490: bla ma'i yum dang spun srid tshig mi brnyas //
NK113(e)001:2491: thugs kyi gsum la yid kyi rnam gsum dang //
NK113(e)001:2492: spyod dang sgom dang lta ba log pa spang //
NK113(e)001:2493: bla ma lha mched lta sgom thun kun sems //
NK113(e)001:2494: thabs kyi dbang gyur yan lag nyi shu lnga //
NK113(e)001:2495: tan gan ma byin len rdzun kyal pa'i tshig /
NK113(e)001:2496: spyad bya lnga ni gnang bkag shes pas spyod //
NK113(e)001:2497: 'dod chags zhe sdang la sogs nyon mongs lnga //
NK113(e)001:2498: mi spang lnga ni rang rgyud pa dang dbral //
NK113(e)001:2499: dri chen dri chu m+aam sa rak+ta zil //
NK113(e)001:2500: dang len lnga la gtsang sme'i gnyis rtog 'dral //
NK113(e)001:2501: phung po 'byung yul dbang po kha dog lhar //
NK113(e)001:2502: shes bya lnga ni shes rab stobs kyis spyod //
NK113(e)001:2503: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las de bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2504: bsgrub bya lnga ni rtogs goms mthu yis bsgrub //
NK113(e)001:2505: 'di dag dam tshig gsal bkra'i dgongs pa ste //
NK113(e)001:2506: de bzhin dus 'khor brtul zhugs nyi shu lnga //
NK113(e)001:2507: gsang 'dus sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor zla gsang sogs //
NK113(e)001:2508: sngon dang phyin chad 'gyur ba'i rgyud sde yi //
NK113(e)001:2509: spyi don gyur pa'i rigs lnga'i sdom pa la //
NK113(e)001:2510: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor smon 'jug tshul khrims gsum //
NK113(e)001:2511: mi bskyod rdor dril phyag rgya bla ma gzung //
NK113(e)001:2512: rin 'byung chos nor mi 'jigs byams pa sbyin //
NK113(e)001:2513: snang mtha' theg pa gsum 'dzin chos rnam bshad //
NK113(e)001:2514: don grub mchod bstod phrin las kun la gus //
NK113(e)001:2515: khyad par bla med rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni //
NK113(e)001:2516: rdo rje rigs gyur srog la 'tshe ba yang //
NK113(e)001:2517: zhing bcu las gzhan dbu mar rlung rtogs gsod //
NK113(e)001:2518: rin chen rigs la ma byin blang bya ni //
NK113(e)001:2519: mtshan ldan gzugs dang skal med skye bo'i nor //
NK113(e)001:2520: rdzogs pa'i byang chub rang stobs mthu yis blang //
NK113(e)001:2521: pad+ma'i rigs la ri dwags mig can mchod //
NK113(e)001:2522: stong pa nyid kyi bud med kun tu spyod /
NK113(e)001:2523: las chos dam tshig phyag rgya chen po bsten //
NK113(e)001:2524: las la rdzun tshig sgyu ma lta bur sgrog /'khor lo'i rigs la rdzas dang yul rnams kyi //
NK113(e)001:2525: 'dod pa'i yon tan sgyu ma lta bur spyod //
NK113(e)001:2526: de yi yan lag tshig gis gab pa ni //
NK113(e)001:2527: ma bsgral bsgral sogs byang sa dang thun mong //
NK113(e)001:2528: lha dang lha min gsang ba pa mi brnyas //
NK113(e)001:2529: phyag rgya bzhon pa mtshon cha mtshan ma la //
NK113(e)001:2530: smad par mi bya'i gnyis ni dngos bstan te //
NK113(e)001:2531: gsang ba gnod sbyin phyag rgya sku gzugs rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2532: bzhon pa bla ma'i stan dang chibs la sogs //
NK113(e)001:2533: mtshon cha lha yi ched du byas pa'i rigs //
NK113(e)001:2534: mtshan ma phyag mtshan lha dang bla ma dang //
NK113(e)001:2535: mchod rten grib ma 'gom la smad pa'i sgra //
NK113(e)001:2536: de bzhin mchod rdzas rnyings la dman mar grags //
NK113(e)001:2537: phyag mtshan rnam pa'ang bza' bar bkag pa yin //
NK113(e)001:2538: khyad par gsod dang ma byin len pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:2539: dngos bstan nyid dang dgongs pa lung ston gyi //
NK113(e)001:2540: rnam dbye ma phyed sngags pa thur la ltung //
NK113(e)001:2541: mdor na gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par //
NK113(e)001:2542: spas pa'i gsang bar mngon 'chel kun la gzur //
NK113(e)001:2543: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod dang mtshams med spyod //
NK113(e)001:2544: sngags sdom skye ba'i rten du rung bas na //
NK113(e)001:2545: gsang sngags thabs kyis che ba smos ci dgos //
