NK113(e)001:2546: ltung mtshams mi shes bla mar mi gus dang //
NK113(e)001:2547: bag med la goms nyon mongs mthu che bzhi //
NK113(e)001:2548: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi de'i steng du //
NK113(e)001:2549: brjed ngas che dang dran pa mi gsal ba //
NK113(e)001:2550: bsnan pa dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu drug yin //
NK113(e)001:2551: de bas dran dang shes bzhin gnyen po yi //
NK113(e)001:2552: long ba dbye ba'i gnas skabs thob pa'i bag /
NK113(e)001:2553: bsrung ba ji bzhin nyin mtshan thun drug tu //
NK113(e)001:2554: spang blang gnas la bsgrims shing bsgrims shing dpyad //
NK113(e)001:2555: nyams na gso ba'ang 'og ma las 'phags te //
NK113(e)001:2556: nyan thos sdom khrims 'chab sems ma skyes na //
NK113(e)001:2557: lan bdun gsor yod 'chab bcas lan gcig kyang //
NK113(e)001:2558: gso ba'i yul med rdza be'u chag pa bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2559: byang sdom rin chen nyer spyad chag dang 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2560: gzhan rkyen dge ba'i bshes la bsten nas gso //
NK113(e)001:2561: gsang sngags sdom pa rin cen snod zhom ltar //
NK113(e)001:2562: rang stobs mthu yis gso ru byar yod pas //
NK113(e)001:2563: bla ma spun brnyas 'phral du mnyes byas bskang //
NK113(e)001:2564: gsung gi tha tshig nyams na rdo rje chos //
NK113(e)001:2565: bsgoms la snying po'am yig brgya 'bu ma ther 'don //
NK113(e)001:2566: thugs las nyams na lo gsum smra ba bcad //
NK113(e)001:2567: gcig tu mnyam par bzhag pa gso ba'i thabs //
NK113(e)001:2568: drug cha las thal thun tshod 'da' ba'i mtshams //
NK113(e)001:2569: 'gal dang nyams dang 'das dang ral ba zhes //
NK113(e)001:2570: zhag dang zla ba lo gcig lo gnyis 'das //
NK113(e)001:2571: gso bar rung ste phyi ma phyi mar lci //
NK113(e)001:2572: lo gsum 'das na gso bar rung ma yin //
NK113(e)001:2573: 'gal na tshogs 'khor nyams na bdog dgus bskang //
NK113(e)001:2574: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK113(e)001:2575: ral na srog gis gso ba'i rnam bzhag rnams //
NK113(e)001:2576: rdo rje nyi ma rnam par bkod las gsungs //
NK113(e)001:2577: gzhan yang dbang bzhi bskyar dang bdag 'jug blang //
NK113(e)001:2578: bskyed rdzogs bzlas brjod 'pho med tshul khrims dang //
NK113(e)001:2579: thig le'i rnal 'byor sbyin sreg gtor ma gtong //
NK113(e)001:2580: dral ba'i sngags rgya bkru dang gtum mos bsreg /
NK113(e)001:2581: tshogs sam rten gyi drung du nyes pa bsgrag /
NK113(e)001:2582: srog bslu gsung rab bklag dang yig brgya bzla //
NK113(e)001:2583: man+dala yan lag bdun dang mchod rten bzhengs //
NK113(e)001:2584: la sogs thabs kyis gtugs pa ma yin la //
NK113(e)001:2585: khyad par dong sprugs bshags pas mi 'dag med //
NK113(e)001:2586: dmigs bcas kun la 'gyod sems lhag par gces //
NK113(e)001:2587: ma bshags tshe 'dir bde legs yon tan 'grib //
NK113(e)001:2588: do zla med pa'i rdo rje'i dmyal bar ltung //
NK113(e)001:2589: dam tshig ldan pa skye ba bcu drug gam //
NK113(e)001:2590: myur na 'adi'am 'chi kha bar ma dor //
NK113(e)001:2591: grub pa brgyad dang dbang bcu phyi nang gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2592: dbang phyug brgyad dang rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi //
NK113(e)001:2593: mchog gi dngos grub kha sbyor yan lag bdun //
NK113(e)001:2594: sku lnga'i zhing 'gro don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK113(e)001:2595: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:2596: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod bstan pa'i tshoms te le'u bcu pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:2597: rgyal bas 'khor lo bar par rnam thar gsum //
NK113(e)001:2598: bstan bya'i ngo bo so so rang rig nyid //
NK113(e)001:2599: sems can khams la bde gshegs snying po ru //
NK113(e)001:2600: rang bzhin bzhugs la rdzogs pa chen por grags //
NK113(e)001:2601: gang du rgya cha 'i lam bzang dam pa'i don //
NK113(e)001:2602: mtha' dag blo yi byi dor kho na'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:2603: sdom pa gsum dang phyin drug bskyed rdzogs sogs //
NK113(e)001:2604: kun kyang rdzogs pa chen po'i lam stegs yin //
NK113(e)001:2605: 'dir ni 'khor dang mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK113(e)001:2606: dbyings las ma g.yos gzhan du gyur ba med //
NK113(e)001:2607: 'khor 'das ma grub gzhi yi chos nyid kyang //
NK113(e)001:2608: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum du rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2609: de nyid ngang na dag pa sangs rgyas dang //
NK113(e)001:2610: ma dag sems can 'khor 'das gnyis kyi cha //
NK113(e)001:2611: gnyis kyi ngang na rmi lam mi g.yo bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2612: gang nas ma 'ongs gzhan du 'pho ba'ang med //
NK113(e)001:2613: re zhig gzhi yi bzhugs tshul grub pa'i mtha' //
NK113(e)001:2614: ka dag lhun grub ma nges nges pa don //
NK113(e)001:2615: cir yang btub dang cir yang khas blang btub //
NK113(e)001:2616: sna tshogs 'dod pa'i gzhi bdun thams cad kyang //
NK113(e)001:2617: ngo bo ka dag gcig pu'i phyogs re la //
NK113(e)001:2618: so sor btags pa'i rang gzhung 'dzin pa gzhan //
NK113(e)001:2619: khong long bdun gyis glang po'i skye mched dang //
NK113(e)001:2620: ngang pa'i kha dog brjod pa ji bzhin no //
NK113(e)001:2621: 'dir ni ngo bo ka nas dag pa la //
NK113(e)001:2622: yon tan lhun grub gcig dang tha dad min //
NK113(e)001:2623: dngos mtshan spros pa bral bas ka dag la //
NK113(e)001:2624: gting gsal 'gag pa med pas lhun grub bo //
NK113(e)001:2625: gzhi gcig rdzas su 'gal ba'ang ma yin te //
NK113(e)001:2626: gnyid du phyogs dang gnyid dus shes pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:2627: ngo bo ka dag yin pas 'khor ma myong //
NK113(e)001:2628: lhun grub rtsal la rol pa cir yang snang //
NK113(e)001:2629: ji ltar beed+aur+ya yi rang 'od ni //
NK113(e)001:2630: gting gsal rkyen gyis ma bskyed phyir mi snang //
NK113(e)001:2631: de bzhin ka dag dngos mtshan spangs pa'i gdangs //
NK113(e)001:2632: lhun grub phyi rgya ma ral bum pa'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2633: ngo bos stong la gdangs kyis ma 'gags pas //
NK113(e)001:2634: snang ba kun gyi 'char gzhir de bzhugs kyang //
NK113(e)001:2635: gzhi las g.yos pa med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:2636: mtshan ma ris chad can du phyir mi gsal //
NK113(e)001:2637: de ni sangs rgyas ma yin sems can min //
NK113(e)001:2638: gcig dang tha dad ma yin mtha' dbus min //
NK113(e)001:2639: stong pa phyang chad ma yin dngos po min //
NK113(e)001:2640: skye med snang ba gsum dang thabs gcig go //
NK113(e)001:2641: de nyid ngang las rig pa'i bdag nyid can //
NK113(e)001:2642: rlung lnga'i snying po gdangs kyi phyir 'phags pas //
NK113(e)001:2643: nang gsal gzhon nu bum pa'i rgya ral nas //
NK113(e)001:2644: gzhan las g.yos pa med bzhin gzhi snang shar //
NK113(e)001:2645: gang tshe thugs rje'i rigs gdangs rnam pa'i yul //
NK113(e)001:2646: dpyod byed shes par shar ba rig pa la //
NK113(e)001:2647: ltos pa'i ma rig can gyi cha bzung bas //
NK113(e)001:2648: sprin bral mkha' bzhin dwangs pa'i ka dag las //
NK113(e)001:2649: lhun grub g.yo ba 'char tshul brgyad du shar //
NK113(e)001:2651: theg rtse shin tu rnal 'byor rgyud sde dang //
NK113(e)001:2652: man ngag lde mig gangs ldan ri yi ljongs //
NK113(e)001:2653: dri med 'od zer stong ldan gcig gis phye //
NK113(e)001:2654: de tshe gzhi snang mthong ba'i skad cig mar //
NK113(e)001:2655: dang po'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po des //
NK113(e)001:2656: snang ba 'khrul par ma mched rang snang du //
NK113(e)001:2657: rig pas lung ma bstan gyi gzhi las 'phags //
NK113(e)001:2658: gzhi nyid 'bras bu smin pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK113(e)001:2659: skad cig gcig la bye brag rab tu phyed //
NK113(e)001:2660: phyed thog shes rab nyid kyang skur smin pa //
NK113(e)001:2661: gzhan byung rkyen la ma ltos rang sar gnas //
NK113(e)001:2662: sku dang ye shes rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid du //
NK113(e)001:2663: skad cig gcig la mngon par sangs rgyas so //
NK113(e)001:2664: gang tshe chos sku'i dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2665: rnam grol yon tan rgyas pa'i lhun grub sgo //
NK113(e)001:2666: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru snang byas nas //
NK113(e)001:2667: de yi rtsal las tshangs chen bskal pa bkod //
NK113(e)001:2668: dag pa rang bzhin sprul sku'i snang ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2669: ma dag 'khor ba'i sgo las sems can gyi //
NK113(e)001:2670: snang ba nyid dang mthun pa'i ston pa yis //
NK113(e)001:2671: 'khor ba stongs pa'i phrin las zad mi shes //
NK113(e)001:2672: zag med rang ngo shes pa'i dge tshogs kyi //
NK113(e)001:2673: mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i ston pa chen po de'i //
NK113(e)001:2674: zhing dang mdzad pa chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam //
NK113(e)001:2675: sangs rgyas nyid kyi snang ba de tsam mo //
NK113(e)001:2676: de la gnyis su 'dzin pa yod min pas //
NK113(e)001:2677: gdul bya 'dul byed rnam par mi rtog kyang //
NK113(e)001:2678: nor bu mchog dang dpag bsam shing chen ltar //
NK113(e)001:2679: rtsol ba med pa'i thugs rje gzhan ngor snang //
NK113(e)001:2680: de nyid ma rig khams gsum sems can rnams //
NK113(e)001:2681: thog ma'i gzhi la 'khrul pa ma mchis kyang //
NK113(e)001:2682: gzhi snang shar ba'i rnam pa ma rig pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2683: glo bur rkyen ni bdag nyid gcig pa ste //
NK113(e)001:2684: de nyid thur song lhan cig skyes pa la //
NK113(e)001:2685: ming don bdag rtog kun tu brtags pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2686: ma rig gsum las 'khrul ba'i rkyen bzhi mched //
NK113(e)001:2687: gzhi nyid khyim ltar gnas pa rgyu yi rkyen //
NK113(e)001:2688: de la rtog dpyod shar ba bdag po'i rkyen //
NK113(e)001:2689: de las yul dang yul can dmigs pa'i rkyen //
NK113(e)001:2690: gsum po dus mtshungs de ma thag pa'i rkyen //
NK113(e)001:2691: tshogs las rim bzhin 'khrul ba stobs gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:2692: nyon mongs tshogs 'phel 'khor ba'i gnas rigs grub //
NK113(e)001:2693: rten 'brel bcu gnyis shing rta'i 'phang lo bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2694: 'di ltar rigs drug skye gnas bzhi po'ang //
NK113(e)001:2695: med snang sgyu ma'i rang gzugs snang dus nas //
NK113(e)001:2696: yod ma myong ba'i stong gzugs thog ma la //
NK113(e)001:2697: dpyod byed yid drug langs nas tshogs drug shar //
NK113(e)001:2698: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa'i 'ching ba ni //
NK113(e)001:2699: rab tu mthu che sems nyid nam mkha'i khams //
NK113(e)001:2700: ngo bo nyid med 'di yang rab bcings nas //
NK113(e)001:2701: bdag yod la zhen mgal me'i 'khor lo bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2702: srid na la la'i snang ba la la'i mun //
NK113(e)001:2703: la la'i bdud rtsi la la'i chu dang me //
NK113(e)001:2704: kun nas rnam par 'gal ba'i 'du shes rnams //
NK113(e)001:2705: bag chags rjes 'gro nges pa 'ga' yang med //
NK113(e)001:2706: de lta na'ang snang yul sems ma yin //
NK113(e)001:2707: bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan me long nang zhugs kyang //
NK113(e)001:2708: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i rkyen tsam las //
NK113(e)001:2709: bzhin dang me long nam yang 'dres ma myong //
NK113(e)001:2710: med bzhin snang la der 'dzin 'khrul pa'i sems //
NK113(e)001:2711: thag khra mthong tshe sprul du 'dzin byed kyi //
NK113(e)001:2712: shes pa dang po gzung ba'i chos yin la //
NK113(e)001:2713: rjes la rtog dpyod zhugs pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK113(e)001:2714: gal te sbrul du snang ba gzung ba la //
NK113(e)001:2715: 'dzin pa bdag po'i shes par smra byed na //
NK113(e)001:2716: snang dang snang yul ma phyed skyes bu yang //
NK113(e)001:2717: snang ba nyid dang lhan cig yod med byed //
NK113(e)001:2718: gang du'ang ma rig gang 'dzin glo bur rkyen //
NK113(e)001:2719: srid pa'i bdag po nga dang nga yi bar //
NK113(e)001:2720: med bzhin 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba chod gyur na //
NK113(e)001:2721: kun byed rgyal po rang byung rang la thim //
NK113(e)001:2722: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:2723: gzhi'i bzhugs tshul bstan pa'i tshoms te le'u bcu gcig pa'o ////
NK113(e)001:2724: gang zhig slob pa min pa'i zung 'jug la //
NK113(e)001:2725: dkri ba'i lam chen phyin drug yon tan kun //
NK113(e)001:2726: shes rab pha rol phyin la yang dag bsten //
NK113(e)001:2727: lam de nam yang gzhan gyi rgyur mi 'gyur //
NK113(e)001:2728: 'di ltar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK113(e)001:2729: stong pa nyid la mtshan nyid mi gnas shing //
NK113(e)001:2730: mtha' bral don la dbu mar gzung ba'ang med //
NK113(e)001:2731: ngo bo nyid spangs rdzogs pa chen por grub //
NK113(e)001:2732: rtsod pa mngon par 'phel ba'i rtog ge ni //
NK113(e)001:2733: brtags shing rjes su dpag pa'i phyi bzhin 'brang //
NK113(e)001:2734: don dam yul ni de dang 'gal ba can //
NK113(e)001:2735: so so rang rig brjod pa'i yul las 'das //
NK113(e)001:2736: dngos por smra ba grub matha'i rtog ge dang //
NK113(e)001:2737: sa mtshams dman pa so skye'i rtog ge yi //
NK113(e)001:2738: rtog dpyod las 'das rgyal ba'i ye shes ni //
NK113(e)001:2739: gdod nas grol ba rdzogs pa chen po'i lam //
NK113(e)001:2740: shes bya snang bas ma bcings stong pa'i dngos //
NK113(e)001:2741: stong pa rang bzhin gsal ba'i snying po ni //
NK113(e)001:2742: rig par bzhugs pa'i sku dang ye shes khams //
NK113(e)001:2743: 'du 'bral med pa nyi ma'i snying po bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2744: gang la blo yi rim pas 'jal lugs gsum //
NK113(e)001:2745: sems kyi sde ni rol pa'i rtsal du shar //
NK113(e)001:2746: klong gi sde ni rang snang bkod pa'i rgyan //
NK113(e)001:2747: man ngag sde ni med snang stong pa'i gzugs //
NK113(e)001:2748: kun kyang dgrol gzhi med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK113(e)001:2749: gang gi 'grol ba spangs pa'i ngang gsal gdangs //
NK113(e)001:2750: gzhi dang rtsa ba med pa'i klong na gsal //
NK113(e)001:2751: byas shing bcos pa med pas ye grol yin //
NK113(e)001:2752: rang gi rang grol rkyen la rag ma lus //
NK113(e)001:2753: cer grol yin pas ltos gzhi kun dang bral //
NK113(e)001:2754: gcig dang du mar gdags pa'i mtha' las grol //
NK113(e)001:2755: gcig po rig par grol bas mtshan nyid med //
NK113(e)001:2756: gang dag sems las 'das pa'i rig pa ni //
NK113(e)001:2757: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i khyad chos yin //
NK113(e)001:2758: rtogs pa rnams ni gzhi las rig par grol //
NK113(e)001:2759: ma rtogs sems can de nyid ngang du 'khor //
NK113(e)001:2760: rnam pas dbye na chu dang chu lbur bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2761: rtog med tsam du sems rig mtshungs na'ang //
NK113(e)001:2762: rig pa rang bzhin med par zang thal la //
NK113(e)001:2763: sems ni lteng ka lta bur 'khyil zhing rmongs //
NK113(e)001:2764: rig pa gnam stong zla ba gting gsal 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2765: sems ni bco lnga'i zla ba yul 'dres mtshungs //
NK113(e)001:2766: dwangs la yul med rig pa'i yon tan te //
NK113(e)001:2767: yul dang kun nas 'dres pa sems kyi khyad //
NK113(e)001:2768: de bzhin rig pa rang gnas shes rab ste //
NK113(e)001:2769: bsam gtan thabs la ma ltos bying rgod bral //
NK113(e)001:2770: sems ni gzung 'dzin cha dang bcas pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2771: rnam rtog nye bar len pa'i phyogs dang 'dres //
NK113(e)001:2772: rig pa yul la shar kyang snang ba yid //
NK113(e)001:2773: zil gyis mi non dngul chu sar lhung 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2774: sems ni gzung 'dzin cha dang bcas pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2775: rnam rtog nye bar len pa'i phyogs dang 'dres //
NK113(e)001:2776: rig pas sems nyid gzhan du ma spangs kyang //
NK113(e)001:2777: sems dang rig pa lhan cig mi 'du bas //
NK113(e)001:2778: yul dang rnam par rang dang rdzas gcig pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2779: nyon mongs rnams kyang lhan cig sbran nas bros //
NK113(e)001:2780: de ltar bros pas nyon mongs btson ra las //
NK113(e)001:2781: nges par 'byin pa man ngag sde ba yi //
NK113(e)001:2782: khyad par chos te gzhan du nyon mongs tshogs //
NK113(e)001:2783: nyan rang spong zhing byang sems gnyen pos 'dul //
NK113(e)001:2784: sngags spyir lam gtong sems sder gshes thog grol //
NK113(e)001:2785: klong sder chos nyid gcig tu dag byed pa //
NK113(e)001:2786: rig pa'i klong na rang tshugs zhig pa mtshar //
NK113(e)001:2787: de bzhin kun gzhi dang ni chos sku gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2788: dbyings su gcig kyang chos sku rgya mtsho 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2789: kun gzhi'i rnam shes de yi sgrib cha ste //
NK113(e)001:2790: gru pa bzhin du 'khor 'das gnyis kar lding //
NK113(e)001:2791: gzhi de nyid nas 'khrul grol chos nyid kyang //
NK113(e)001:2792: gnyid du song dang de las sad pa bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2793: 'khrul pa dbang po nyams pa'i gnyid stug bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2794: grol ba de las sad pa'i gnas skabs 'dra //
NK113(e)001:2795: thog ma'i nges med gzhi yi lhun grub dang //
NK113(e)001:2796: mthar gyi grol sa'i ka dag dri bral gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2797: rdzas su gcig kyang slad kyi 'khrul pa'i gzhi //
NK113(e)001:2798: byed dang mi byed khyad par shes pa gces //
NK113(e)001:2799: de bzhin dbyings kyi grol sa ka dag dang //
NK113(e)001:2800: da lta'i lam gyi rig pa ka dag gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2801: rgya chad phyogs lhung med par mnyam na'ang //
NK113(e)001:2802: grol sa nyid ni rlung sems cha dang bcas //
NK113(e)001:2803: rnam par byang ba'i 'khor 'das ka dag ste //
NK113(e)001:2804: lam dus rlung sems ma dag rkye dbang dang //
NK113(e)001:2805: 'grogs shing sems dang sems byung dri ma'i chas //
NK113(e)001:2806: bslad cing khur bas dngos gnas res 'ga' tsam //
NK113(e)001:2807: de bzhin chos nyid bar do'i rig gdangs dang //
NK113(e)001:2808: rtog bcas goms pa'i lha yi sgyu lus gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2809: lha skur mtshungs kyang snang ba zhing khams su //
NK113(e)001:2810: shar zhing shes thog grol dang mi grol khyad //
NK113(e)001:2811: khyad par lam 'dir zhugs pa'i dam tshig can //
NK113(e)001:2812: sa bcu'i snang bas bsdus pa'i longs sku la //
NK113(e)001:2813: 'thogs pa ma yin de yi dpe byad ni //
NK113(e)001:2814: rang bzhin sprul par bkod la myur du 'gro //
NK113(e)001:2815: de phyir 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog ste //
NK113(e)001:2816: gdod nas grol ba'i rig pa ka dag ni //
NK113(e)001:2817: stong pa ngo bo nyid med bsam brjod 'das //
NK113(e)001:2818: mtshan nyid blo yis brjod pas thug pa spangs //
NK113(e)001:2819: smon pa med la rig pa'i yon tan rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2820: rig pa'ang shes bya'i yul la mi gnas pas //
NK113(e)001:2821: nga dang nga yir 'dzin pa'i chos dang bral //
NK113(e)001:2822: de la sgom dang sgom par bya ba med //
NK113(e)001:2823: ma bcos rnal mar bzhag na rjen par mthong //
NK113(e)001:2824: rang gi ngo bo bzhan du mi 'gyur na //
NK113(e)001:2825: ma rig 'dzin pas srid par 'khrid mi nus //
NK113(e)001:2826: phyi rol yul dang bdag tu zhen pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:2827: byed pos ma byas sems rtog brtas las grub //
NK113(e)001:2828: gzhi dang rtsa ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK113(e)001:2829: skyes tsam nyid las skye ba med par rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:2830: de las gzhan pa'i rtogs pa yod mi dgos //
NK113(e)001:2831: klog dang 'dzin dang sgom dang bstan bcos sems //
NK113(e)001:2832: mtha' dag blo yi grub mtha' zhig gyur na //
NK113(e)001:2833: yid smon med pa'i sangs rgyas de nyid do //
NK113(e)001:2834: khyad par bla na med pa'i thod rgal ni //
NK113(e)001:2835: rig gdangs mngon sum mthong ba'i gol sa nyung //
NK113(e)001:2836: phyi 'byung sa rdo ri brag yul snang gi //
NK113(e)001:2837: rdos bcas dri ma zad pa'i 'byung chen gyi //
NK113(e)001:2838: ye shes 'od gsal chen por dwangs pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:2839: mngon du byed pas nang 'byung khregs chod kyis //
NK113(e)001:2840: rdul phran nyid las dwangs par ma nus pa'ang //
NK113(e)001:2841: 'pho ba chen po rdo rje'i skur smin nas //
NK113(e)001:2842: gzhan don 'khor ba ma stongs bar du mdzad //
NK113(e)001:2843: de phyir rang gi sde pas yid dpyod kyi //
NK113(e)001:2844: lta sgom spyod 'bras kun dang khyad zhugs pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2845: mtshan nyid legs par phyed pa man ngag yin //
NK113(e)001:2846: de lta mod kyi bdag 'dzin glo bur rkyen //
NK113(e)001:2847: chos dbyings dag pa'i klong du ma nub par //
NK113(e)001:2848: glo bur rkyen gyis bslu ba'i rtog tshogs chos //
NK113(e)001:2849: tha mal rang lugs srid pa'i bdag po yis //
NK113(e)001:2850: dang po'i las can rnams la sgrib pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:2851: zhi gnas lhag mthong ngo bo gcig pa dang //
NK113(e)001:2852: so so ba yi 'khrid tshul rnam gnyis las //
NK113(e)001:2853: dang po'i phyogs la gnas cha'i bsam gtan dang //
NK113(e)001:2854: gsal cha'i shes rab zhi lhag zung 'brel las //
NK113(e)001:2855: gnyis pa min pa'i mtha' bral don la bzhag /
NK113(e)001:2856: gnyis pa'i phyogs la'ang dbye ba gnyis grub ste //
NK113(e)001:2857: shes rab las dang gdams ngag las byung ngo //
NK113(e)001:2858: shes rab las byung sgra yi rjes mthun pa //
NK113(e)001:2859: thos pa'i don la rtse gcig zhi ba dang //
NK113(e)001:2860: de las don rtogs lhag mthong mtshan nyid do //
NK113(e)001:2861: man ngag las byung don gyi rjes su 'gro //
NK113(e)001:2862: sems ni g.yo ba med pa zhi gnas la //
NK113(e)001:2863: de yi rang bzhin shes pa lhag mthong ste //
NK113(e)001:2864: mdor na rab kyis ngan rtog chos skur lhongs //
NK113(e)001:2865: bzang ngan mnyam na gnyen po bsten mi dgos //
NK113(e)001:2866: 'bring gi ngang dwangs zung 'brel lam goms pas //
NK113(e)001:2867: bzang ngan rtog pa mtha' dag dbyings su nub //
NK113(e)001:2868: tha mas thog mar zhi gnas 'bab zhig btsal //
NK113(e)001:2869: gang dmigs brtan pa thob nas lhag mthong gi //
NK113(e)001:2870: ye shes so sor rtog pa la goms na //
NK113(e)001:2871: mthar gyis gser gling sa rdo ma rnyed bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2872: sems dang sems byung rtog pa gang skyes kyang //
NK113(e)001:2873: snang sems dbyer med gzhi grol chen por 'char //
NK113(e)001:2874: thabs kyi mchog tu rtog pa gang shar yang //
NK113(e)001:2875: dgag par mi bya bsgrub par bya ba med //
NK113(e)001:2876: rjes su mi 'brang ngang las ma g.yos na //
NK113(e)001:2877: lha yi mig dang spyan dang mngon shes sogs //
NK113(e)001:2878: dbang po dwangs pa'i yon tan mtha' dag 'thob //
NK113(e)001:2879: rtog pa yul dang 'brel na tha mal te //
NK113(e)001:2880: me long lta bur dwangs pa'i shes pa la //
NK113(e)001:2881: snang yul ma 'gags gza' skar bzhin bkra yang //
NK113(e)001:2882: rnam pa'i blo yis gos par ma gyur na //
NK113(e)001:2883: gzung ba'i yul dang 'dzin sems 'brel chad pas //
NK113(e)001:2884: so so rang rig rnam par mi rtog pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2885: ye shes bla ma'i sa la da lta phyin //
NK113(e)001:2886: mdor na dbyings kyi lam ni chos nyid gcig /
NK113(e)001:2887: rig pa'i lam ni shes rab khyad par can //
NK113(e)001:2888: 'od gsal lam ni sgron ma rnam pa gnyis //
NK113(e)001:2889: khregs chod lam ni shar grol dus mnyam ste //
NK113(e)001:2890: thod sgal lam ni dbyings dang rig pa yin //
NK113(e)001:2891: 'di dag rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK113(e)001:2892: thun mong ma yin lam lngar mkhyen 'tshal nas //
NK113(e)001:2893: ma rig grogs dang 'khrul pa'i bslu brid kyis //
NK113(e)001:2894: mtha' med 'khor ba'i 'brog dgon 'jigs rung bar //
NK113(e)001:2895: las dang nyon mongs 'du byed lcags sgrog gis //
NK113(e)001:2896: de ring phan chad bcings la skyo ba'i sems //
NK113(e)001:2897: bskyed nas zhi ba dam pa'i grong khyer du //
NK113(e)001:2898: mya ngan 'das pa'i lam mchog bsnyen par mdzod //
NK113(e)001:2899: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
NK113(e)001:2900: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam thun mong ma
NK113(e)001:2901: yin pa bstan pa'i tshoms te le'u bcu nyis pa'o
NK113(e)001:2902: //// de ltar gzhi lam mtshan nyid legs rtogs nas //
NK113(e)001:2903: mthar phyin 'bras bu sku dang ye shes ni //
NK113(e)001:2904: gzhan las ma byung kun gzhi'i rnyogs pa dwangs //
NK113(e)001:2905: sems dang sems byung chos dbyings zhi ba yin //
NK113(e)001:2906: gang du gzhi las gzhi snang g.yos pa yi //
NK113(e)001:2907: bdag 'dzin bdag chags shes bya'i cha 'dzin pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2908: tshogs brgyad nyer len sprin dang 'dra ba rnams //
NK113(e)001:2909: rnam par dag pa'i ye shes nyi ma ni //
NK113(e)001:2910: sgrib pa med par rang bzhin 'od du gsal //
NK113(e)001:2911: glo bur dri ma cha dang bcas spangs pa //
NK113(e)001:2912: dag pa gnyis ldan byang chub mchog gi dngos //
NK113(e)001:2913: gdod mi sangs rgyas smon pa med pa'i dbyings //
NK113(e)001:2914: nya rgyas zla ba spros pa phyir gsal can //
NK113(e)001:2915: stong gi cha la dbyings su nub pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:2916: kun tu mi rtog chos nyid 'pho 'gyur med //
NK113(e)001:2917: dbyings kyi rtag pa mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2918: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan zhi ba'i dbyings //
NK113(e)001:2919: stobs sogs yon tan rgya mtsho kun chub kyang //
NK113(e)001:2920: snang cha ngo bor ma 'dres spangs rtogs kyi //
NK113(e)001:2921: cha nas gzhal ba mngon par byang chub sku //
NK113(e)001:2922: shes bya'i yul la blo yi 'jug pa zhi //
NK113(e)001:2923: shes byed blo la 'dzin pa'i kun rdzob spangs //
NK113(e)001:2924: so so rang rig rtag chad mthar ma lhung //
NK113(e)001:2925: thim la ma rmugs phra ba'i ye shes ni //
NK113(e)001:2926: mkhyen cha 'gag med sku dang ye shes rten //
NK113(e)001:2927: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa rnams kyis mthong //
NK113(e)001:2928: gang la zhi ba chos kyi sku zhes brjod //
NK113(e)001:2929: so so rang gi rig bya rgyal ba'i khams //
NK113(e)001:2930: gcig dang du mar ma yin dngos po dang //
NK113(e)001:2931: dngos med las 'das mkha' ltar rnam mi rtog /
NK113(e)001:2932: gos pa med cing rnam 'gyur spros pa zhi //
NK113(e)001:2933: ngag gi yul 'das don dam bden pas bsdus //
NK113(e)001:2934: rtog dpyod tha snyad gtan tshigs kyis mi mtshon //
NK113(e)001:2935: blo dang snyam byed dpe dang 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:2936: sa bcu'i dbang phyug gi yang spyod yul min //
NK113(e)001:2937: 'dren pa rnams la mngon sum gyur pa'i gnas //
NK113(e)001:2938: zab zhi gzhon nu bum pa'i khang mdzes nang //
NK113(e)001:2939: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams ni rtag bzhugs kyang //
NK113(e)001:2940: rnam pa'i cha nas gcig gis gcig mi gzigs //
NK113(e)001:2941: rang bzhin spros bral dbyings na dgongs klong gcig /
NK113(e)001:2942: mkhyen cha 'gag pa med pa'i rang gdangs las //
NK113(e)001:2943: thugs rje phyir gsal longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK113(e)001:2944: gnas dang dus dang ston pa chos dang 'khor //
NK113(e)001:2945: nges pa lnga ldan sku dang zhing khams dang //
NK113(e)001:2946: mtshan dpe yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid can //
NK113(e)001:2947: gnas ni lhun rdzogs 'og min stug po bkod //
NK113(e)001:2948: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer gsal 'tsher 'bar //
NK113(e)001:2949: mkha' dbyings dbang po'i mtshon chas bkab pa bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2950: mnan na nem zhing btegs na 'phar ba lta'i //
NK113(e)001:2951: gzhal med khang mdzes sgo 'phar rnam bzhir ldan //
NK113(e)001:2952: rta rkang brgyad ldan ye shes lnga'i rtsig pa //
NK113(e)001:2953: pha gu d+r+wa phyed mda' yab pu shu can //
NK113(e)001:2954: snam bur 'dod pa'i yon tan mig yangs ma //
NK113(e)001:2955: bde stong mchod sprin rtse dga' g.yo ba can //
NK113(e)001:2956: rnga yab 'phan gdugs rgyal mtshan nor bu'i tog /
NK113(e)001:2957: bla bre zar tshags gtsang khang phyur bur mdzes //
NK113(e)001:2958: chu zheng srid du mi mngon gang bltas gang //
NK113(e)001:2959: grangs kyis mi gtugs mkha' dbyings snod gyur bzhin //
NK113(e)001:2960: rten gzhi gzhal med khang pa re re'i nang //
NK113(e)001:2961: brten pa'i gtso bo lnga yi gdan khri ni //
NK113(e)001:2962: 'phrog byed gnyis 'thung cang shes zlos gar can //
NK113(e)001:2963: shang shang te'u chu skyes nyi zla'i steng //
NK113(e)001:2964: dus gsum gzhir rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i dus //
NK113(e)001:2965: 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i mtshan rdzogs ston pa lnga //
NK113(e)001:2966: rnam snang mi bskyod rdo rje rin chen 'byung //
NK113(e)001:2967: 'od mtshan stong 'bar don yod grub pa ni //
NK113(e)001:2968: rang rang rigs kyi yum dang bcas pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:2969: kha sbyor bdun gyi bdag nyid chen por bzhugs //
NK113(e)001:2970: rang las mi gzhan sems dpa' sems ma'i 'khor //
NK113(e)001:2971: sgo ba bzhi dang de bzhin so so'i yum //
NK113(e)001:2972: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i chos 'khor ni //
NK113(e)001:2973: sgra tshig mtshan ma'i yul las 'das par bskor //
NK113(e)001:2974: steng khang zhi ba byang chub snying po'i gnas //
NK113(e)001:2975: dbang mdzad zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las //
NK113(e)001:2976: dam pa'i stangs dpyal gnyis ni sprul gzhi ste //
NK113(e)001:2977: kun la khyab par brdal bas chos kyi sku //
NK113(e)001:2978: 'gro drug so so'i gnas su don mdzad pa'i //
NK113(e)001:2979: rig pa'i skyes bu drug ni sprul par shar //
NK113(e)001:2980: rang snang longs sku'i zhing na sum cu bzhi //
NK113(e)001:2981: gtso bo bcu la nyer bzhi 'khor gyi tshul //
NK113(e)001:2982: phung khams skye mched gnas su dag pa'i lha //
NK113(e)001:2983: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po yin //
NK113(e)001:2984: 'di dag sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mnyam sbyor sogs //
NK113(e)001:2985: bla med rgyud las lus grub dkyil 'khor ni //
NK113(e)001:2986: ji snyed bstan dang rnam dag mtshungs pa yin //
NK113(e)001:2987: 'og khang tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK113(e)001:2988: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas phyi nang rim pa dgu //
NK113(e)001:2989: sgo khyams dgu pa'i phyi mar rgyu 'bras kyis //
NK113(e)001:2990: rta babs gnyis ldan pho brang dbus ma'i nang //
NK113(e)001:2991: rdo rje'i brag chen pad+ma stong brdal la //
NK113(e)001:2992: thabs shes nyi zla dbang phyug khyo shug ni //
NK113(e)001:2993: nyi shu rtsa bzhi steng du dpa' gtum stag /'jigs byed seng ge gdug pa gzig dang ni //
NK113(e)001:2994: gtum pa dom dang stobs chen glang po dang //
NK113(e)001:2995: brjid pa'i ma he 'dzin pa'i chu srin dang //
NK113(e)001:2996: zhe sdang lto 'gro byol song gtso brgyad res //
NK113(e)001:2997: dregs pa pho mo bzung zhing bardzisa pa'i steng //
NK113(e)001:2998: 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi dpal bcom ldan 'das //
NK113(e)001:2999: che ba'i che mchog in+d+ra n+ai la'i mdangs //
NK113(e)001:3000: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od ldan bdun gsum zhal //
NK113(e)001:3001: zhabs brgyad phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK113(e)001:3002: zhi ba'i lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bsnams //
NK113(e)001:3003: gnam zhal yul mchog dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad //
NK113(e)001:3004: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis rdo rje dung khrag 'dzin //
NK113(e)001:3005: lhag ma gnas yul ma mo phra men bsnams //
NK113(e)001:3006: yab yum khro mkhar tshul lam mnyam par sbyor //
NK113(e)001:3007: srid dang zhi ba'i chos khams ma lus pa //
NK113(e)001:3008: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs kyi gdan khri nas //
NK113(e)001:3009: dbu rgyan 'khor lo'i bar la rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:3010: dbang mchog dang ni he ru ka dpal dgu //
NK113(e)001:3011: glo 'bur bzhi dang gru chad rnam bzhi la //
NK113(e)001:3012: rnam shes tshogs dag goo r+ai la sogs brgyad //
NK113(e)001:3013: dkyil 'khor dang po'i khyams la phra men brgyad //
NK113(e)001:3014: gnyis pa'i khyams la spor ma rnams pa brgyad //
NK113(e)001:3015: gsum pa'i khyams la dbang mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK113(e)001:3016: kun la rang rang sgo ma bzhi bzhir ldan //
NK113(e)001:3017: 'bar ba'i rnam rol gar dgu'i nyams kyis brjid //
NK113(e)001:3018: 'di dag rang snang longs sku'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK113(e)001:3019: gzhi snang lhun grub don gyi 'og min yin //
NK113(e)001:3020: bzhi pa'i khyams la mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis //
NK113(e)001:3021: lnga pa'i khyams la ma bdun sring mo bzhi //
NK113(e)001:3022: drug pa'i khyams la ging chen drug tshan gsum //
NK113(e)001:3023: bdun par khro bo yab yum bcu phrag drug /
NK113(e)001:3024: brgyad par pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu ste //
NK113(e)001:3025: dgu pa'i khyams la ma mo drug cu rnams //
NK113(e)001:3026: log 'dren 'dul phyir sprul pas bsdus pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:3027: bgegs sogs gdul bya so so'i rang ngor snang //
NK113(e)001:3028: de phyir rang snang 'og min dkyil 'khor min //
NK113(e)001:3029: chos sku'i ye shes phyi ru gsal ba'i mdangs //
NK113(e)001:3030: phun tshogs lnga ldan longs spyod rdzogs pa'i gnas //
NK113(e)001:3031: gang du sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs gyur pa'i //
NK113(e)001:3032: sangs rgyas kho na'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa yi //
NK113(e)001:3033: rol pa nyid phyir gtso 'khor mchog dman mnyam //
NK113(e)001:3034: kun gyi thugs kyang rnam par mi rtog cing //
NK113(e)001:3035: gsung ni brjod bral sku ni mtshan dper rdzogs //
NK113(e)001:3036: rang snang ye shes mthong ba dag pa'i spyan //
NK113(e)001:3037: gcig gis gcig gzigs nam yang sgrib pa med //
NK113(e)001:3038: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi spyod yul ni //
NK113(e)001:3039: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma bsdus phyir //
NK113(e)001:3040: dag pa'i sems can chen po rnams kyis kyang //
NK113(e)001:3041: mthong bar mi nus rgyal ba'i ye shes dang //
NK113(e)001:3042: 'gal ba'i sgrib chas da dung ma spangs phyir //
NK113(e)001:3043: 'das dang ma 'ongs da lta dus gsum gyi //
NK113(e)001:3044: nges pa las 'das 'og min chen po na //
NK113(e)001:3045: bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dus bzhi'i bdag nyid can //
NK113(e)001:3046: gtso 'khor ngo bo mthun pa'i rang snang ngo //
NK113(e)001:3047: de nyid ngang las sems can gdul ba'i phyir /
NK113(e)001:3048: 'dul byed ston pa gsum du bkod pa ni //
NK113(e)001:3049: rang bzhin sprul pa 'gro 'dul sprul pa dang //
NK113(e)001:3050: sna tshogs sprul pa gsum las rang bzhin ni //
NK113(e)001:3051: rgyal ba'i ye shes snang ba 'og min gyis //
NK113(e)001:3052: dbyings snang longs sku'i dpe byad dwangs shel nang //
NK113(e)001:3053: 'phos lta'i gzugs brnyan phyed sprul longs sku'i gnas //
NK113(e)001:3054: dbus na 'og min shar na mngon par dga' //
NK113(e)001:3055: lho na dpal ldan nub na pad+ma brtsegs //
NK113(e)001:3056: byang na las rab grub pa rnam pa lnga //
NK113(e)001:3057: gzugs kyi rgyal po la sogs ston mchog lnga //
NK113(e)001:3058: mtshan dpe yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid can //
NK113(e)001:3059: zhi dang khro ba'i rnam 'gyur dpag med cing //
NK113(e)001:3060: ye shes rnam pa lnga po re re la'ang //
NK113(e)001:3061: bzhi bzhi'i 'khor dang bcas pas nyi shu lnga //
NK113(e)001:3062: chos dbyings ye shes g.yo ba med pa ni //
NK113(e)001:3063: nam mkha'i gzugs bzhin shes bya'i mtha' las 'das //
NK113(e)001:3064: me long ye shes gzung 'dzin rdul bral ni //
NK113(e)001:3065: mngon par 'du byed med bzhin mched pa'i gzhi //
NK113(e)001:3066: mnyam nyid ye shes chos kun mtshan nyid med //
NK113(e)001:3067: srid zhi dbyer med zhi ba'i dbyings su zhugs //
NK113(e)001:3068: sor rtog ye shes chos nyid ji lta dang //
NK113(e)001:3069: chos can shes bya ji snyed rtag thogs med //
NK113(e)001:3070: bya grub ye shes phrin las gzhan phan can //
NK113(e)001:3071: chags thogs spangs pa'i mdzad pa lhun gyis grub //
NK113(e)001:3072: 'khor ni sa bcu'i byang sems 'ba' zhig la //
NK113(e)001:3073: sku yis chos rnams 'jal ba'i 'od bkye bas //
NK113(e)001:3074: byad kyi dri ma me long nang gsal ltar //
NK113(e)001:3075: da dung bdag dang ston pa'i khyad mthong nas //
NK113(e)001:3076: byang chub sgrib pa gting dpag dka' ba dag /
NK113(e)001:3077: sbyangs nas bcu gcig kun tu 'od la 'gro //
NK113(e)001:3078: dus ni sa bcu'i dbang phyug chen po rnams //
NK113(e)001:3079: 'jig rten mgon po ngo bo med pa'i dbyings //
NK113(e)001:3080: mi zad rgyan 'khor sku gsung thugs kyi ngang //
NK113(e)001:3081: ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig tu ma gyur bar //
NK113(e)001:3082: 'chi ba'i bdud bcom 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK113(e)001:3083: gdul bya'i gti mug la sogs nyon mongs lnga //
NK113(e)001:3084: gang gi gnyen por che ba'i zhing khams dang //
NK113(e)001:3085: ston par bstan pa'i sku lnga chos rab lnga //
NK113(e)001:3086: gnas 'gyur ye shes rnam pa lnga po yang //
NK113(e)001:3087: mthong lam nas bzung sa bcu rgyun matha'i bar //
NK113(e)001:3088: rim rdzogs rdzogs pa'i byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK113(e)001:3089: zhing 'di sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' las //
NK113(e)001:3090: gzhan gyi spyod pa'i yul du snang min zhing //
NK113(e)001:3091: de bzhin ston pa longs spyod rdzogs na yang //
NK113(e)001:3092: 'khor sogs rang snang ma yin rgyud gzhan pas //
NK113(e)001:3093: bsdus phyir phyed snang rang bzhin sprul pa zhes //
NK113(e)001:3094: nyi zla kha sbyor chen po'i rgyud kyis bstan //
NK113(e)001:3095: khyad par rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK113(e)001:3096: rang snang ye shes dkyil 'khor dam pa ru //
NK113(e)001:3097: mchog gzigs bla mas dbang bskur ma nyams la //
NK113(e)001:3098: nyin dus rang snang mngon sum 'od gsal dang //
NK113(e)001:3099: mtshan mo snying kha'i 'od gdangs goms pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:3100: rtogs pa'i rang bzhin tshad du ma phyin yang //
NK113(e)001:3101: chos nyid bden pa bla ma'i byin rlabs kyi //
NK113(e)001:3102: sa thob rnams dang skal pa mtshungs gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:3103: gzhi snang lhun grub phyogs bcu sprul par 'gro //
NK113(e)001:3104: khyad par rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa lnga //
NK113(e)001:3105: shar nas rim bzhin shes dang su war+na //
NK113(e)001:3106: pad r+aag in+d+ra n+ai la'i gzhal med khang //
NK113(e)001:3107: sgo khyams rta babs snang byed ba glang mig /
NK113(e)001:3108: zur bzhir mu tig mchod rten dril bu dang //
NK113(e)001:3109: g.yer khas sbrel ba'i dpyang thag rlung bskyod sgra //
NK113(e)001:3110: rnam thar gsum ldan chos dbyangs dar dir sgrog /
NK113(e)001:3111: phyogs bzhir spos sprin g.yo ba'i ba dan bzhi //
NK113(e)001:3112: phyi rim yan lag brgyad ldan rdzing bu'i 'gram //
NK113(e)001:3113: t+aa la'i ljon pa d+r+wa phyed 'phyang 'phrul can //
NK113(e)001:3114: shar shang te'u rma bya ka ta ri //
NK113(e)001:3115: ne tso mi skad 'byin dang ngang pa gzhon //
NK113(e)001:3116: ri skegs zer mo sbab dang kang+ka ri //
NK113(e)001:3117: lha'i bya dril bu'i sgra can khu byug dang //
NK113(e)001:3118: gser gyi rdo rje'i gzugs can kri ti pa //
NK113(e)001:3119: g.yu dang byi ru in+d+ra n+ai la dang /
NK113(e)001:3120: dung ltar kha dog phyed pa'i bya tshogs kyis //
NK113(e)001:3121: snyan sgrog mgrin pa'i rgyud mang kun tu 'khrol //
NK113(e)001:3122: de na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK113(e)001:3123: nyon mongs gnod pa zhi ba'i chu klung la //
NK113(e)001:3124: spyad pa tsam gyis 'du ba'i nad mi 'byung //
NK113(e)001:3125: yid la ci bsam dran pa'i mod la 'byung //
NK113(e)001:3126: sum cu rtsa gsum lha dang longs spyod mnyam //
NK113(e)001:3127: phyi rim rin chen sna bdun pha gu can //
NK113(e)001:3128: zhing mchog de na rigs bzhi'i ston pa yis //
NK113(e)001:3129: dus bzhir chos kyi sgra sgrog rgyun mi chad //
NK113(e)001:3130: kun gyi bar snang he ru ka dpal zhing //
NK113(e)001:3131: dur khrod chen po me ri 'bar ba na //
NK113(e)001:3132: ston pa gzhon nu dpa' bo bcom ldan 'das //
NK113(e)001:3133: lag na rdo rje la sogs dpa' bo dang //
NK113(e)001:3134: mkha' 'gro'i sprin phung 'phro ba'i dbus nyid na //
NK113(e)001:3135: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i chos 'khor bskor //
NK113(e)001:3136: pad+ma las skyes rgyal sras dpag tu med //
NK113(e)001:3137: kun kyang lha dang lha mo khye'u dang //
NK113(e)001:3138: bu mo'i rnam pa drang srong grub pa can //
NK113(e)001:3139: rnam par rtog pa med cing sems gsum med //
NK113(e)001:3140: yid drug dang ni nyon mongs drug kyang med //
NK113(e)001:3141: ma rig pa med rkyen bzhi yod ma yin //
NK113(e)001:3142: de dang mtshungs par ldan pa rnams kyang med //
NK113(e)001:3143: ston pa rdo rje 'chang gi byin rlabs las //
NK113(e)001:3144: rang bzhin nyid du bkod phyir rang bzhin ni //
NK113(e)001:3145: sprul pa'i zhing zhes rgyal sras rnams la grags //
NK113(e)001:3146: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gsang lam du //
NK113(e)001:3147: rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud las bstan //
NK113(e)001:3148: gzhan du bde chen mkha' la spyod pa dang //
NK113(e)001:3149: sa spyod ces grags don gyi 'od gsal la //
NK113(e)001:3150: dbang thob lhan gcig skyes ma'i d+aa ki dang //
NK113(e)001:3151: yul chen nyer bzhir spyod pa'i zhing skyes ma //
NK113(e)001:3152: la sogs dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma tshogs dang //
NK113(e)001:3153: skal ba mnyam pa'i rig 'dzin gral gong du //
NK113(e)001:3154: lam gyi 'phro sbyong rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK113(e)001:3155: rdo rje'i bla ma rnams ni rab bzhugs nas //
NK113(e)001:3156: sngags kyi lta spyod rlabs po che la spyod //
NK113(e)001:3157: 'di dag rang snang dge ba'i sa bon dang //
NK113(e)001:3158: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i brtul zhugs mthar son pa'i //
NK113(e)001:3159: gsang sngags grub pa rnams la snang ba las //
NK113(e)001:3160: rtog 'dod can gyi phyin du yod pa yi //
NK113(e)001:3161: ris chad can du bsam par mi bya'o //
NK113(e)001:3162: de nyid ngang las longs spyod rdzogs pa yi //
NK113(e)001:3163: yi ge'i sprin gyi 'od zer rab 'phros pas //
NK113(e)001:3164: 'jig rten 'dul byed sprul pa'i sku mchog ni //
NK113(e)001:3165: gnas rigs drug gi gdul bya'i snang ba la //
NK113(e)001:3166: rang rang ming gi mngon brjod rjes 'gro ba'i //
NK113(e)001:3167: 'dul byed rigs pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK113(e)001:3168: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med stong gsum gyi //
NK113(e)001:3169: stong chen snyed dang mnyam par rab sprul nas //
NK113(e)001:3170: gdul ba bzhi yi 'gro don bsam mi khyab //
NK113(e)001:3171: de yang bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba ni //
NK113(e)001:3172: sku yi mdzad pa chen po bcu gnyis yin //
NK113(e)001:3173: gsum gi mdzad pa theg pa gsum mam gcig /
NK113(e)001:3174: gang yang 'du shes rjes 'gro sems can gyi //
NK113(e)001:3175: nyon mongs gnyen por dgongs te gsungs pa la //
NK113(e)001:3176: chos kyi sgo 'phar brgyad khri bzhi stong grangs //
NK113(e)001:3177: gsum ltar snang yang sgra tshig rang mtshan pa //
NK113(e)001:3178: ma yin sems can khams la byin brlabs mthus /
NK113(e)001:3179: rnam par rig pa nyid dang mthun par shar //
NK113(e)001:3180: thugs kyis 'dul ba dus gsum mkhyen cing gzigs //
NK113(e)001:3181: dus kyang so sor mi rtog dus med dus //
NK113(e)001:3182: rang bzhin gdod ma'i gnas skabs kun tu bzang //
NK113(e)001:3183: gzhan gyi sems rgyud mkhyen dang de bzhin du //
NK113(e)001:3184: rdzu 'phrul chen po'i spyan dang snyan la sogs //
NK113(e)001:3185: mngon shes drug po dus las yol ba med //
NK113(e)001:3186: phrin las 'dul ba kun tu sku dang zhing //
NK113(e)001:3187: kun tu thugs dang de bzhin kun tu zhal //
NK113(e)001:3188: kun tu gsung gi gsang ba bsam mi khyab //
NK113(e)001:3189: sku gsung thugs kyis dngos su don mdzad la //
NK113(e)001:3190: phrin las kyis ni dngos rgyud kun tu mdzad //
NK113(e)001:3191: de ltar dbyings las sprul pa'i skur mchog rnams //
NK113(e)001:3192: chos nyid la ltos ji lta'i ye shes dang //
NK113(e)001:3193: chos can la ltos ji snyed mkhyen pa yi //
NK113(e)001:3194: ye shes gnyis kyis gdul bya'i rgyud 'grol zhing //
NK113(e)001:3195: nye bar zhi dang ma 'dres chos tshul ston //
NK113(e)001:3196: de las yang sprul rnam pa brjod mi lang //
NK113(e)001:3197: 'gro ba drug gi gnas rigs de snyed du //
NK113(e)001:3198: lha rnams 'dul byed tshangs dbang bde 'byung sogs //
NK113(e)001:3199: mi la nyan rang byang sems 'khor los sgyur //
NK113(e)001:3200: de bzhin lha ma yin la thags bzang ris //
NK113(e)001:3201: bya la shing rta mo dang ri dwags phyir //
NK113(e)001:3202: seng ge'i rgyal po yi dam brtan pa sogs //
NK113(e)001:3203: mdor na dmyal ba yi dwags gang dang gang //
NK113(e)001:3204: 'dul byed de dang de 'dra'i gzugs sprul nas //
NK113(e)001:3205: sems can don la nam yang g.yel ba med //
NK113(e)001:3206: 'di ni 'jig rten drug gi zhing rnams su //
NK113(e)001:3207: las dang bag chags dge sdig rgyu 'bras kyi //
NK113(e)001:3208: gnas rigs bde sdug mtho dman ltar snang ba'i //
NK113(e)001:3209: rang snang mthun pa'i ston pas don mdzad cing //
NK113(e)001:3210: chos kyang ma nges gdul bya'i blo rtog ltar //
NK113(e)001:3211: dus kyang rang rang skal pa'i rjes 'gro ba //
NK113(e)001:3212: ma dag zhing gi 'gro la de ltar snang //
NK113(e)001:3213: gang zhig rmi lam nang du sangs rgyas mthong //
NK113(e)001:3214: rmi lam lta bur sprul pa'i chos bstan yang //
NK113(e)001:3215: ngo bo nyid med rang bzhin ma grub la //
NK113(e)001:3216: bdag med stong pa gsog tu rig bya zhes //
NK113(e)001:3217: zab mo'i mdo sde dag las gsungs pas na //
NK113(e)001:3218: 'khor 'das rmi lam lta bu'i rol pa la //
NK113(e)001:3219: snang ba'i sangs rgyas ngo bo dag na'ang //
NK113(e)001:3220: sprul pa gdul bya nyid ltar snang ba'i phyir //
NK113(e)001:3221: ma dag thugs rje rol pa'i sprul pa yang //
NK113(e)001:3222: ji srid 'khor ba'i rjes 'gro rgyun mi 'chad //
NK113(e)001:3223: de nyid ngang las sna tshogs sprul pa ni //
NK113(e)001:3224: rang bzhin byon dang 'du byed las byung ba //
NK113(e)001:3225: 'bur du byas dang ris su bris pa dang //
NK113(e)001:3226: gan+d+ho la dang khang bzang skyed mos tshal //
NK113(e)001:3227: mya ngam thang la sprul pa'i grong khyer dang //
NK113(e)001:3228: pad+ma dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin nor //
NK113(e)001:3229: gru gzings zam pa shing rta zab gos sogs //
NK113(e)001:3230: sems med bem po'i tshul du snang ba dang //
NK113(e)001:3231: skye ba mu ge'i tshe na nya bo che //
NK113(e)001:3232: nad kyi gdungs la srog chags des pa dang //
NK113(e)001:3233: srid mo'i gling du cang shes ba la ha //
NK113(e)001:3234: mi gtsang 'dam du gser gyi bung ba sogs //
NK113(e)001:3235: sprul pa sna tshogs rnam kun bde ba'i gzhir //
NK113(e)001:3236: rtog pa med cing g.yo ba med pa ltas //
NK113(e)001:3237: don chen gyis ni dpal du nye bar gnas //
NK113(e)001:3238: gal te gdul bar bya ba'i dus yol na //
NK113(e)001:3239: 'dul byed dbyings su nub pa'i mtshon dpe ni //
NK113(e)001:3240: ji ltar chu snod med tshe chu zla'i gzugs //
NK113(e)001:3241: sprul gzhi'i zla ba nyid la thim pa ltar //
NK113(e)001:3242: gdul bya'i snang bas bsdus pa'i sprul pa rnams //
NK113(e)001:3243: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbyings su thim //
NK113(e)001:3244: de'ang gnam stong zla ba gcig shos nas //
NK113(e)001:3245: gcig tu thim pa med kyang phyir gsal gdangs //
NK113(e)001:3246: nang dbyings spros pa med pa'i ngang thim ltar //
NK113(e)001:3247: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rang snang chos kyi sku'i //
NK113(e)001:3248: ye shes chen por 'khyil ba de nyid la //
NK113(e)001:3249: dbum pa rnams 'jug pa chos dbyings su //
NK113(e)001:3250: zhi ba'i 'gog pa dam pa zhes 'dod la //
NK113(e)001:3251: 'dir ni so so rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK113(e)001:3252: phra ba'i ye shes nang gsal chos kyi dbyings //
NK113(e)001:3253: thim la ma rmugs gzhon nu bum pa'i sku //
NK113(e)001:3254: gang du gdul bya snang ba'i mod nyid la //
NK113(e)001:3255: 'gag med thugs rje'i ye shes mched pa'i gzhi //
NK113(e)001:3256: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK113(e)001:3257: 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i go 'phang yin //
NK113(e)001:3258: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las //
NK113(e)001:3259: mthar phyin 'bras bu sku dang ye shes bstan pa'i tshoms te le'u bcu gsum pas rdzogs so ////
NK113(e)001:3260: bdag brgyud snod kyi dpyad pa rdzogs gyur nas //
NK113(e)001:3261: 'jig rten mgon po dri med 'od zer gyi //
NK113(e)001:3262: zhal mthong thugs rje'i dbugs 'byin ma thob na //
NK113(e)001:3263: lam min g.yang sar dal rten stong log byas //
NK113(e)001:3264: de phyir 'di la legs par bshad pa'i cha //
NK113(e)001:3265: bla ma'i byin rlabs sgom byung shes rab las //
NK113(e)001:3266: thos bsam rtog ge'i rig pas ma bskyed pas //
NK113(e)001:3267: rang rang 'dod gzhung phyogs dang 'gal na 'chags //
NK113(e)001:3268: chos tshul rgya mtsho gting dpag dka' ba'i don //
NK113(e)001:3269: mnyam par bzhag pa kho na'i khyad chos las //
NK113(e)001:3270: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnas //
NK113(e)001:3271: yang dag mthong la nam yang bslu ba med //
NK113(e)001:3272: dge ba 'di yis bdag dang sems can rnams //
NK113(e)001:3273: rgyal ba'i ring lugs nor ba med pa'i lam //
NK113(e)001:3274: sgrib gnyis rnyog pa dwangs pa'i gzings zhugs nas //
NK113(e)001:3275: byang chub zhi ba rin cen gling phyin shog /
NK113(e)001:3276: nags mthongs ri dwags dkyu ba'i sman ljongs na //
NK113(e)001:3277: dus bzhi'i mngon rtogs ngom pa'i ljon pa ni //
NK113(e)001:3278: drang srong rnams la mi snyan sgrog mi byed //
NK113(e)001:3279: snying la 'bab par smra ba'i bya tshogs kyang //
NK113(e)001:3280: sbrul gdug 'khri shing lta bu'i 'khor ba 'dir //
NK113(e)001:3281: skyo ba'i nges 'byung shing rtas yid 'dren pa'i //
NK113(e)001:3282: ca co shin tu zhi ba sgrog thos nas //
NK113(e)001:3283: dbang po nye bar zhi ba'i dpal thob shog /
NK113(e)001:3284: lta ba yid byed rlung gis ma dkrugs la //
NK113(e)001:3285: spyod pa rgyal sras dam pa'i rjes 'gro bas //
NK113(e)001:3286: nam yang gzhan gyi khur du mi 'gro zhing //
NK113(e)001:3287: rlabs chen phrin las 'gro ba'i dpal du shog //
NK113(e)001:3288: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya //
NK113(e)001:3289: la stod pa chos rje brag phug pas bskul ba'i ngor //
NK113(e)001:3290: sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+ma sam+b+ha wa'i zhabs rdul la
NK113(e)001:3291: spyi bos reg pa'i rdzogs chen pa rang byung rdo
NK113(e)001:3292: rje mkhyen brtse 'od zer gyis dpal ldan pad+ma 'od
